tagline: A brand new way to preview Framer designs natively on iOS
text_content: [{u'description': u'Framer Preview is a companion app to Framer for Mac, a code-based prototyping tool for designers. Download Framer on any iOS device to interact with your UI designs at the level of a fully functional native app. Simply connect your iPhone or iPad to the same WiFi network as your Mac and watch your code come to life. No toolbar distractions or constant refreshing, just a beautiful visual display that reacts to your changes in real-time. Other features: - Powerful gesture support allows you to pinch, swipe or tap to test your transitions and animations live. - Download any Project for offline use and showcase your prototype in its full functional glory. - One-click sharing capability and automatic in-app viewing of any Framer link sent to you - Enhanced security features ensure you‚Äôre safeguarded on any network, big or small Download Framer for Mac at http://framerjs.com/', u'title': u'Framer Preview'}, {u'description': u'Design interactive high-fidelity prototypes for iOS, Android, desktop or the web. Invent new animations and interactions. Integrates with Sketch and Photoshop.', u'title': u'Introducing Framer for iOS - Framer'}]

tagline: Check your health insurance for free (California)
text_content:
[{u'description': u'*Currently available in San Francisco, and Silicon Valley* Your doctor comes to your home or work. You can do just about everything you could do in an old school doctor's office. Build an ongoing relationship with your board-certified physician. Your physician and care team work together to keep you at optimal health. Pay just your standard copay. Scan your insurance card and we'll take care of the rest. What you can do: ‚Ä¢ Annual physicals/Wellness exams ‚Ä¢ Chronic disease management ‚Ä¢ Sexual health consultations and screenings ‚Ä¢ Sickness or injury visits ‚Ä¢ Blood tests ‚Ä¢ Prescriptions ‚Ä¢ Referrals Insurance we accept: ‚Ä¢ Aetna ‚Ä¢ Anthem Blue Cross ‚Ä¢ Blue Shield of California ‚Ä¢ Cigna ‚Ä¢ Health Net ‚Ä¢ UnitedHealthcare Disclaimer: All medical services are provided by independent physician groups.', u'title': u'Circle Medical - Doctor house calls paid for by your insurance'}, {u'body': u' *Currently available in San Francisco*Your doctor comes to your home or work. You can do just about everything you could do in an old school doctor's office. Build an ongoing relationship with your board-certified physician. Your physician and care team work together to keep you at optimal health. Pay just your standard copay. Scan your insurance card and we'll take care of the rest.What you can do:
‚Ä¢ Annual physicals/Wellness exams
‚Ä¢ Chronic disease management
‚Ä¢ Sexual health consultations and screenings
‚Ä¢ Sickness or injury visits
‚Ä¢ Blood tests
‚Ä¢ Prescriptions
‚Ä¢ ReferralsInsurance we accept:
‚Ä¢ Aetna
‚Ä¢ Anthem Blue Cross
‚Ä¢ Blue Shield of California
‚Ä¢ Cigna
‚Ä¢ Health Net
‚Ä¢ UnitedHealthcareDisclaimer: All medical services are provided by independent physician groups.   ', u'description': u'The family doctor that comes to your home or work.', u'title': u'Circle Medical - House Doctors - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': None, u'title': u'Circle Medical - San Francisco housecall doctors that take insurance'}]

tagline: Run your entire financial life from your phone
text_content:
[{u'body': u' More than 160.000 users already love the mobile banking experience with NUMBER26. Now the bank account for your smartphone is also one of the best apps in 2015 in the Play Store.NUMBER26 - Europe‚Äôs most modern bank accountFree checking account, free MasterCard, convenient overdraft access‚úì MoneyBeam: Send money via SMS or Email
‚úì International money transfers powered by TransferWise
‚úì Full control and everything in realtime
‚úì Convenient and free bank account
‚úì Protected by the German deposit insurance
‚úì Overdraft: Money with one click (available in Germany) 
‚úì CASH26: Cash without bank branches (available in Germany)
‚úì Account switching service (available in Germany)As featured in:
TechCrunch | WIRED | Financial TimesJoin 160.000+ NUMBER26 users. Just download the app and open your account for free in 8 minutes.Learn more about NUMBER26: https://number26.eu/
About¬∑ Full-featured current account
¬∑ Intuitive mobile banking app
¬∑ Innovative online banking
¬∑ NUMBER26 MasterCard¬Æ
¬∑ NUMBER26 Maestro debit card (available in Germany and Austria)
¬∑ Open your an account in just 8 minutes (100% online ‚Äì You don‚Äôt have to fill any documents ‚Äì  your identity will be verified via a video conference call)
NUMBER26 is completely secure¬∑ Your deposits are protected through the German deposit-protection scheme
¬∑ Your data is protected, in line with German data-protection requirements
¬∑ Your account activity is completely transparent and fully under your control due to push notifications for every transaction.Your individual security settings offer you full control and 100% freedom.
¬∑ We make use of latest encryption technology (e.g. HTTPS, RSA)
Features of the mobile app¬∑ Receive a push notification on your Android smartphone for every transaction on your account
¬∑ Have the best overview of your transactions at every time
¬∑ Automated categorizing of your spending
¬∑ Smart statistics, give you an even better overview 
¬∑ Transactions which are logically connected to each other are linked automatically
¬∑ Send money to your friends via e-mail and text message without using IBAN & BIC
¬∑ Send money in 9 currencies (USD, GBP, CAD, AUD, SEK, INR, HUF, CHF, PLN) with the real exchange rate, powered by TransferWise. (Feature not yet available to residents of Spain or Italy)
¬∑ Block and unblock your card with just one click
¬∑ Report your card as stolen and you will receive a new one
¬∑ Decide how and where your account and your card can be used: Abroad? Online? At the ATM?
¬∑ Change your card limits for card payments and ATM withdrawals
¬∑ Transfer money conveniently
¬∑ Bank transfers are designed to be very user-friendly and a history of already used transfer contacts will make future transfers even more convenient
¬∑ Filter and search for past transactions
Your free bank account
¬∑ You can withdraw money from most ATMs worldwide for free
¬∑ You don‚Äôt have to pay an account maintenance charge
¬∑ You receive the NUMBER26 MasterCard¬Æ and Maestro card (available in Germany)   ', u'description': u'Chosen as one of the best apps in 2015: The bank account for your smartphone.', u'title': u'N26 Mobile Bank Account - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': u'NUMBER26 - Europe's most modern bank account Free basic checking account, free MasterCard, convenient overdraft access. Join 160.000+ users - open your account in the app for free in 8 minutes. - MoneyBeam: Send money via SMS or email - International money transfers powered by TransferWise - Control your account right on your mobile device in real time - Protected by the German deposit insurance - PULSE26: Gives you insights into your NUMBER26 account - Overdraft: Money with one click (available in Germany) - CASH26: Cash without bank branches (available in Germany) - Convenient fingerprint login with TouchID As featured in: TechCrunch | WIRED | Financial Times With NUMBER26‚Äôs free basic bank account for your smartphone, we offer you the most advanced banking experience in Europe: - Receive push notifications for each transaction - Send money to your friends without IBAN & BIC - Control your spending with intelligent statistics - Custom security settings easily with your iPhone - Overdraft facility - CASH26: withdraw or deposit cash at over 6000 retail stores ‚ñ∂ ABOUT NUMBER26 - Intuitive mobile banking app - Innovative online banking experience - Full-featured current account - NUMBER26 MasterCard¬Æ + Maestro debit card - Open your account, in just 8 minutes (completely online with identity verification via video call) ‚ñ∂ NUMBER26‚Äôs EXCEPTIONAL SECURITY STANDARDS - Your money is protected by the German Deposit Protection Fund - Your data is secured according to the German data protection requirements - You enjoy full transparency and control regarding your account, thanks to real-time push notifications for any transaction related to your account ‚ñ∂ FUNCTIONS OF THE MOBILE APP - With our handy statistics and categorization you can easily manage your spendings - Transactions which are logically connected to each other are linked automatically - You can easily transfer money to your friends via email or text message without inserting their IBAN or BIC - Send money in 15 currencies (USD, GBP, CAD, SEK, INR, AUD, HUF, CHF, PLN, BGN, DKK, GEL, NOK, RON, CZK) with the real exchange rate, powered by TransferWise. - Execute money transfers using only an IBAN. The BIC is no longer necessary - Account activity list now indicates which card (MasterCard or Maestro) was used for a card transaction - You can block or unblock your card with a simple click - You can report your card as stolen and we will send you a new one - You decide when and where your bank account and your MasterCard should work (i.e. abroad, online, at the ATM) - You can change your card limits for card payments and atm withdrawals - Transfer money conveniently - All your account connections of previous recipients are automatically saved for future money transfers - Filter transactions or search for specific transactions - Our new and updated Support Center is now also available on mobile ‚ñ∂ THE BASIC NUMBER26 CURRENT ACCOUNT HAS NO MAINTENANCE FEES - You can withdraw money from almost every ATM worldwide - No service charge when you use your NUMBER26 MasterCard¬Æ and Maestro debit card - There are no hidden costs - We earn a small fee with every card transaction, paid by the merchant - We earn money on optional features - We earn money from financial partners that we integrate into our service', u'title': u'NUMBER26'}]

tagline: Discover and meet people nearby
text_content:
[{u'body': u' VoyageUp ‚Äì Make Real World Connections with people nearbyA Discovery platform to find other people, businesses, offers and
events around you. It shows you 2 circles of users:1> People connected to the same Wi-Fi as you are
2> People in a 200m radius around you. It uses location services to show this.People can network, catch up for common interests or help each other.
The offers / events / business info is based on the Wi-Fi or location.VoyageUp lets you make new connections, without having to send or receive invites. You can network with these people at hotels, airports, events, stadiums, colleges, malls and other public places. Or someone nearby who is just looking out for help.Using location services will increase battery usageIt you want you can meet them up for a drink, meal or just hang out with them by just tapping on the icon, without having to send or receive invites. Download now and make new connections.WHY USE VOYAGEUP:¬†DISCOVER PEOPLE AROUND YOU:¬†Discover and connect with other VoyageUp users who are physically near you. Who are on the same WiFi network as you. FIND OR PROVIDE HELP:¬†Need an iPhone charger or want to know the best public transport from the airport? You can find help or help out a fellow VoyageUp user with just a tapEASY OPTION TO CONNECT:¬†Join the same Wi-Fi network as other VoyageUp users and chat without having to send and receive invites.MEET UP:¬†Meet up with other VoyageUp users, who share similar interests like you.PRIVACY:¬†All VoyageUp users and chat messages are erased within 10 min after you disconnect/leave the Wi-Fi network. You can always block or report a userEASILY SHARE THE APP:¬†We make it easy to share our VoyageUp app through Facebook the more people that have VoyageUp the better it is  HOW IT WORKS  Step 1: Join the same WiFi network as other VoyageUp users. If you allow location services then you will also see VoyageUp users who have not joined the same Wi-Fi but are close by. Step 2: Discover VoyageUp users on the ‚ÄòPeople Nearby‚Äô screen. Check their interests and chat with anyone you want to meet up with. Download now and find new friends! 
_____________________________

tagline: Everything you love about Scrivener writing, now on iOS
text_content: [{u'description': u'‚ÄúThe biggest software advance for writers since the word processor.‚Äù ‚ÄîMichael Marshall Smith, bestselling author Typewriter. Ring-binder. Scrapbook. Scrivener combines all the writing tools you need to craft your first draft, from nascent notion to final full stop. Tailor-made for creating long manuscripts, Scrivener banishes page fright by allowing you to compose your text in any order, in sections as large or small as you like. Got a great idea but don‚Äôt know where it fits? Write when inspiration strikes and find its place later. Grow your manuscript organically, idea by idea. Whether you plan or plunge, Scrivener works your way: meticulously outline every last detail first, or hammer out a complete draft and restructure later. Or do a bit of both. All text sections in Scrivener are fully integrated with its outlining tools, so working with an overview of your manuscript is only ever a tap away, and turning Chapter Four into Chapter One is as simple as drag and drop. Need to refer to research? In Scrivener, your background material is always at hand. Write a description based on a photograph. Reference a video or PDF. Check for consistency with an earlier chapter. On the iPad, open two documents side-by-side; on the iPhone, flip between research and writing with just two taps. Once you‚Äôre ready to share your work with the world, simply compile everything into a single document for printing, or export to popular formats such as Word, PDF, Final Draft or plain text. You can even share using different formatting, so that you can write in your favorite font and still keep your editor happy. FEATURES Get Started ‚Ä¢ Interactive tutorial project ‚Ä¢ Keep each manuscript and supporting materials in a self-contained project ‚Ä¢ Import Word, RTF, Final Draft and plain text files ‚Ä¢ Easily split imported text into separate sections Get Writing ‚Ä¢ Write your manuscript in sections of any size ‚Ä¢ View all sections as a single text using the ‚ÄúDraft Navigator‚Äù (iPad only) ‚Ä¢ Quickly navigate sections using the ‚Äúbinder‚Äù sidebar ‚Ä¢ Format with fonts and presets ‚Ä¢ Comments, footnotes, links and highlights ‚Ä¢ Simple bullets and lists ‚Ä¢ Insert images ‚Ä¢ Pinch-zoom to resize text ‚Ä¢ Full-screen mode (iPad only) ‚Ä¢ Typewriter scrolling mode keeps typed text center-screen (iPad only) ‚Ä¢ Write a screenplay using scriptwriting mode ‚Ä¢ Live word and character counts ‚Ä¢ Set word and character count targets ‚Ä¢ Find and replace ‚Ä¢ Customizable keyboard row provides quick-access buttons for formatting, navigation and punctuation ‚Ä¢ Comprehensive keyboard shortcuts for external keyboard users Find Your Structure ‚Ä¢ Write in any order and reorganize later ‚Ä¢ Write a synopsis for any text section and see it in the outline ‚Ä¢ Expand, collapse and drill down into sections of your project ‚Ä¢ Rearrange sections as index cards on the corkboard (iPad only) ‚Ä¢ Project-wide search ‚Ä¢ Track ideas using labels and status ‚Ä¢ Apply custom icons to your sections Refer to Research ‚Ä¢ Import research material such as image, PDF and media flies ‚Ä¢ View research files or other sections right alongside your writing (iPad only) ‚Ä¢ Every section has its own notes area for jotting down ideas ‚Ä¢ Supports multi-tasking split screen mode (supported devices only) Share Your Work ‚Ä¢ Compile to a single document for sharing or printing ‚Ä¢ Use different formatting in your exported or printed document ‚Ä¢ Export to Word, RTF, Final Draft, PDF or plain text ‚Ä¢ Convert rich text to Markdown for sharing with Markdown apps ‚Ä¢ Create and email zipped backups of your projects Work Anywhere ‚Ä¢ Use Dropbox to sync between devices and with the macOS and Windows versions of Scrivener* ‚Ä¢ Copy projects between devices via iTunes * Requires a Dropbox account. Scrivener is not compatible with iCloud. tagline: Turn your data into beautiful, interactive graphs on iOS.
text_content: [{u'description': u'Vizable is the best app for exploring your data on iOS. Pinch, tap, and swipe to answer questions, and watch your spreadsheets come to life with beautiful animations. Just download data from Fitbit, Mint, Dropbox, Google Drive, and more - and find out what insights are hiding in that Excel or CSV attachment. Stop staring at rows of numbers: It‚Äôs time to reach out and touch your data. Visualize Anything Let intuitive design guide you to data revelations. Don‚Äôt be confined to canned dashboards or templates. With Vizable, the only limitation is the number of questions you can ask! How are sales doing? Is my incentive plan working? How can I better align my inventory this month? Go ahead and ask why profit is down, or whether to invest in that new product. Create and Share Design a viz that makes your data pop. Then share with others, who can pick up right where you left off and discover their own insights. Rich visual analytics have never been this fun, and our users agree: ‚ÄúBeing able to show the data to the whole team is really powerful. Seeing the data convinced the team to invest in a project that could easily grow into a million-dollar business in a few years.‚Äù -Ryan Fry, co-owner of Sudwerk ‚ÄúWith thoughtful visuals, simple functionality and seemingly unlimited data viewing options that encourage users to interact and explore, it's certainly a lot more fun than sifting through an clunky Excel spreadsheet.‚Äù -Fast Company Get Going When we developed Vizable, we obsessed about one thing: making sure this is the best app for finding insights in your data. So there are no configuration screens, wizards, or chart builders. Just open your data in Vizable to see what it has to say. With Vizable, you can: ‚Ä¢ Transform data into interactive graphs and charts. ‚Ä¢ Spot patterns and relationships with the help of beautiful animations. ‚Ä¢ Pan and zoom through data stored in Excel and CSV files. ‚Ä¢ Connect to data from Fitbit, Mint, Amazon, and more. ‚Ä¢ Import data from Google Drive, iCloud, Dropbox, and more. ‚Ä¢ Analyze trends and explore data over time. ‚Ä¢ Share your data stories with a static image or an interactive Viz file. "Vizable provides a sleek interface and smooth animations that allow your data to come alive nicely. The pinching and other controls are responsive which make using the app quite simple. So, brighten up those drab spreadsheets by giving Vizable for iPad a try.‚Äù - Sandy Stachowiak, AppAdvice ‚ÄúBelieve me, in the few months I have been using Vizable, I have learned more about my family‚Äôs business than I probably have in the last five years. ‚Ä¶ It‚Äôs like a Rubik‚Äôs cube that you can change, rotate, and see the data in different ways with minimal effort. So if you have a question, you can answer it immediately.‚Äù -Alejandro Palaez, consultant for American Rubber ‚Äú‚Ä¶the possible use cases for an app like Vizable are virtually limitless. Personal finances, fitness data from something like the Nike Band, Amazon shopping habits are just some of the things that can be visualized.‚Äù - Mike Wheatley, SiliconANGLE ‚ÄúSeeing the data spurred me to act. I might have eventually figured it out with Excel, but it would‚Äôve been a lot more difficult.‚Äù -Dave Belt, owner of Seafoam Lavender', u'title': u'Vizable - Explore Your Data'}]

tagline: Track your purchases. Manage your expenses. Earn cashback.
text_content: [{u'description': u'Manage your expenses with quality services that are free, easy- to- use and rewarding. LIFE IS A CONSTANT FUSION OF BUSINESS AND PLEASURE SPENT let‚Äôs you track all your card spending, manage expenses and earn cashback on travel bookings and purchases, that way you always know what you bought, where you bought it, and of course, how much you spent. Start managing your expenses right now and earn rewards with your purchases. FORGET CREDIT CARD STATEMENTS AND CRUMPLED RECEIPTS NEVER MISPLACE ANOTHER FINANCIAL RECORD. CONTROL YOUR RECEIPTS AND EXPENSES. SPENT keeps your receipts and makes your life organized with convenient, easy-to-use folders, so you can view your purchases and expense history anywhere. IT‚ÄôS NEVER BEEN SO REWARDING TO SPEND AND MANAGE YOUR EXPENSES SPENT is the only app that rewards you for spending. Partnering with thousands of merchants, hotels and airline companies we can offer cashback up to 20% on your spending. SPENT App also let‚Äôs you organize your receipts and track all expenses. Whether you‚Äôre picking up the tab for your business lunch or purchasing school supplies for your kids, every purchase tracked counts toward earning cashback. SAFETY AND SECURITY SAFEGUARD - Here at SPENT, keeping your personal information safe and secure is our top priority. When you register with us, rest assured that the following measures and safeguards are always in place. ENCRYPTION - SPENT guarantees a secure experience by encrypting data storage and transports, so you never have to worry about prying eyes. PRIVACY PROTECTION - Your data is safe. SPENT will never sell your data to 3rd parties. PCI COMPLIANCE - SPENT is compliant with all requirements administered by the Payment Card Industry Security Standards Council. SECURE BANK CONNECTIONS - SPENT only maintains bank connections through trusted financial API (Application Programming Interface) partners.', u'title': u'Spent ‚Äì Track your purchases. Manage your expenses. Earn cashback.'}]

tagline: Universal remote control for all of your smart home devices
text_content: [{u'description': u'myHome Plus controls entire home in one app, full-feature supporting all HomeKit accessories, Nest Thermostat, Nest Protect, Nest Cam, WeMo Switch, WeMo Insight, WeMo Light Switch, and WeMo Motion; and makes the days of switching apps to control different products over. No additional hardware required. #Support All HomeKit Features: Scenes Group actions into a scene to represent a state of your home, so that you can run the actions together automatically thru triggers or manually to implement home automation. Triggers Create timer and event triggers to control action sets/scenes at specific times when you get to locations, or when an accessory is in a specific status. e.g. an event trigger turns off the lights when you leave the office after sunset only if they are still on. Multiple Users Share the control of your home with your family members or even a guest with an iCloud account with different control levels. Remote Access Enjoy accessing your HomeKit accessories remotely by enabling Remote Access in iOS Settings > HomeKit and by having a 3rd+ generation Apple TV connected to your local network. Rooms and Zones Assign accessories to rooms and organize rooms into a zone. Service Groups Organize services in a custom way. e.g. add a subset of lights in the living room to control without controlling all lights in the living room. Favorites Set your most important accessories as favorites, which can be quickly controlled from Today View and Apple Watch. Today View Today View lets you glance and control favorite properties of accessories quickly. #Nest Features (Thru In-app Purchase): Support all Nest products Support all Nest products including Nest Thermostat, Nest Learning Thermostat, Nest Protect, and Nest Cam. Remote Access Remotely control Nest products thru Nest cloud. Home/Away state settings Set your state and let the app control home automatically and accordingly. Alert for alarms Get alerts immediately when there is an alarm detected by Nest Protect. #WeMo Features (Thru In-app Purchase): Support WeMo Switch, WeMo Insight, WeMo Light Switch, and WeMo Motion with full control like changing friendly names, resetting settings, and restoring to factory default. #What is Next? Let us know what manufacturer you want us to support next at support@vicinno.com. We will work hard to add it in as soon as we can. Note: Currently, it works with all HomeKit compatible accessories, WeMo and Nest devices like Nest Thermostat, Nest Protect, Nest Cam, WeMo Switch, WeMo Insight, WeMo Light Switch, and WeMo Motion. We will support more soon.', u'title': u'myHome Plus - Control for Nest, WeMo, and HomeKit'}]

stemmed_keyphrases: [hanger, ipad, ipod, iphon, ad, app, hand, imag, love, nine, quot, text, word, motiv, share, author, closet, featur, inspir, packag, search, aesthet, qualiti, categori, distract, platform, quantiti]
tagline: Read and share motivational and inspirational quotes
text_content: [{u'description': u'Read, Share and Hang Quotes. Quote Hanger is an all new app for your daily inspiration and motivation. It comes in a clean user-friendly package, with hand picked quotes. Key Features: * Nine incredible categories focusing on quality over quantity, providing you pure inspiration. * Hang the quotes you love to your iPhone, in a closet just for you. * Sharing quotes has never been this easy, you can share as image or text to all social platforms. * You can search specific words or authors. * The app is for distraction free browsing with minimal aesthetics. * This app is ad free and will always be like that.', u'title': u'Quote Hanger'}]

tagline: Choose one out of four potential matches for a date
text_content: [{u'description': u'ooOo‚Ñ¢ shows you four potential local matches at the same time. You choose the one you like the most. If they also choose you then it's a match and you can start chatting all within the app. To make it more exciting, each time you're shown four people you can see how many liked you. You also get two special options, 'Show' lets you see who said yes. 'Skip' lets you bypass all four potential matches. But remember, these special options can only be used a limited number of times per day so use them at the right time, with the right people. Behind the scenes there's lots of technical stuff going on! ooOo‚Ñ¢ works offline, so if you have a poor connection or no connection at all you can still use the app. We also work very hard to protect your privacy. Passwords are encrypted in such a way it could take up to 7,000 years to hack. The personal details we ask from you by design, are very limited. If you want to try something different, something that doesn't use swiping, something that's reliable then download ooOo‚Ñ¢ now and within 60 seconds you can be choosing your favourite matches. ooOo‚Ñ¢ yes!', u'title': u'ooOo‚Ñ¢ - Find a date or connect with new friends'}]

text_content: [{u'description': u'Memorize anything while playing a game! Tinycards is a brand new app created by the team behind Duolingo, the most downloaded education app in the world. Tinycards. Big fun. _ Have fun unlocking new levels and keeping your memory strength bar full while you learn. Memorize anything quickly. _ Tinycards uses spaced repetition and other smart learning techniques to help you remember new material. Choose from thousands of topics or make your own. _ Learn almost anything with delightful, animated decks. Create your own decks and share them with friends, or pick from a variety of ready-made collections. You‚Äôll find country capitals, vocabulary in different languages, history, constellations, hat styles, you name it! Always wanted to learn Chinese on Duolingo? Now you can exclusively access Chineasy‚Äôs lessons in the form of beautiful flashcards. Simple and free. _ Easy to use, 100% free. Love Duolingo? text_content: [{u'description': u'Edit photos, create beautiful designs and professional graphics with Canva. Get started in seconds with more than hundreds of professional templates and tweak them to suit your need. Use your own photos or choose from more than one million layouts, stock photographs and illustrations. Search for the best fonts, photo filters, graphics, stickers and shapes, then use Canva‚Äôs simple drag and drop tool to create a design. Share your design to your favourite social media, email or text. BEAUTIFUL LAYOUTS Choose from hundreds of professionally designed layouts for - - Greeting cards - Thank you cards - Photo cards - Birthday invitations & cards - Party Invitations - Wedding & Engagement Invitations - Inspirational posts - Music posts - Travel posts - Sale posters & flyers - Event posters & flyers - Business presentation - Sales presentation - Facebook cover - Social Media graphics and much more being added soon... ONE MILLION IMAGES Choose from our library of more than 1 million premium images or design with hundreds of free elements and fonts. Use images from your Camera roll in your designs, or take photos on the go. PHOTO EDITING Take your photos to the next level with Canva‚Äôs stunningly simple photo editor. Present a consistent look and feel on social media and in your marketing materials. You can edit your photos using preset filters or get advanced with photo editing tools like brightness, contrast, saturation, tint, blur, x-process and vignette. With more than six quadrillion options, you‚Äôll never be stuck for choice. SHARE AND PUBLISH - Share directly to your favourite social media including Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest, Instagram and Google + - Or, save your design to phone and share via email, text, messaging apps and more. GET IN TOUCH Got questions or comments? Get in touch by emailing appsupport@canva.com. We're here to help!', u'title': u'Canva - Graphic Design & Photo Editing'}]

[{u'description': u'We‚Äôve been grinding in NYC for the last 4 months working on the latest iteration of our product.', u'title': u'Introducing ‚Äî Lawnmower: Bitcoin & Blockchain Investing, News & Market Data ‚Äî Tales of a Lawnmower'}, {u'body': u' Lawnmower makes it easy to start learning about & investing in blockchain assets. Start tracking assets and reading news with no account required. Begin investing with a bank account in less than 2 minutes for as little as $5. Access curated asset research as well as advanced trading analytics all from your pocket.- Real-time Price Quotes -
Crypto-markets never sleep ‚Äì our asset price data is updated real-time & 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, and all quoted in USD.- Flexible Trading -
Easily set up fixed recurring purchases to "dollar-cost-average" over time, or buy and sell instantly. Trading amounts are flexible with minimums as low as $5.- Account Analytics -
Simplified analytics on your performance over time are available free to all users, while premium users can request more advanced reports highlighting detailed trade data.- Asset Resources -
Each of our blockchain asset pages features fundamental data including market caps, supply, historical prices, trading volume, key resources like technology whitepapers, and in-depth proprietary research.- Performance Benchmarks -
Gauge how your portfolio & trades have performed versus traditional assets & indexes like the S&P 500, Gold, & Oil and our own ‚ÄúLawnmower Blockchain Index‚Äù.- Industry News -
In addition to our own content, we proudly feature top industry news in our app to help keep you up to date on developments in the space.Lawnmower is the perfect tool for diversifying a traditional portfolio of assets like stocks, bonds, and mutual funds. tagline: The exact training methods of the world's top athletes
text_content: [{u'description': u'Join Fitplan's community & use the exact training routines of the world‚Äôs best athletes to become the best version of you. Workout and follow exclusive Fitplans from Michelle Lewin, Jeff Seid, Sergi Constance, and other elite athletes. Choose from a variety of workout styles to lose weight, build muscle, burn fat or get a shredded physique. Here‚Äôs what you can do with Fitplan: - Follow the daily workout routines of the athletes that inspire you. - FREE single-day workouts (always under workout tab) - Automate your results. Workout, follow instructions, watch yourself change - New athletes and plans added monthly - Get detailed sets, reps, rest times and tips that the athletes use to gain the extra edge. - Watch each athlete perform exercise demonstrations in high definition video. - See your weekly workout schedule at a glance and track your progress. We believe that fitness lays the foundation for achieving your goals in all areas of your life. By following the exact training methods of top athletes, you can elevate your performance in the gym and achieve any fitness goal that you set for yourself. Start your Fitplan and transform your mind and body today! Our roster of athletes includes global industry leading fitness phenomenon Michelle Lewin, the youngest IFBB Pro Jeff Seid, 3x Miss Bikini Olympia champion Ashley Kaltwasser, and creator of Vega nutrition and professional Ironman triathlete Brendan Brazier. Our app includes an optional monthly subscription that lets you access our athletes' multi-day plans. The subscription includes a free 7-day trial that becomes a $9.99 USD / month subscription. The billing starts after your 7-day trial completes, and continues on a monthly basis. You can cancel at any time from the Settings screen in the app. If you cancel 24 hours before the 7-day trial is over then you will not be charged. If you cancel during the month period for which you've already paid (up to 24 hours before the next period starts), your subscription will continue until the end of that period. If you do choose to cancel your subscription, or do not subscribe at all, one day workouts with your favorite athletes will still be available to you! Elevate Effort, Exercise Fit, Emerge You. Welcome to Fitplan.', u'title': u'Fitplan: Workout, Burn Fat & Build Muscle with Athletes'}]

text_content: [{u'body': u' The best single messaging experience.Reply is a conversational one-on-one messaging app for Android and iOS that displays your messages in fullscreen.You and your friend can tap anywhere on the screen to start replying. It‚Äôs a new, creative and fun way to stay in touch with the people around you!Combine your text messages with a photo, a video, a link or get creative by using the drawing tools.It‚Äôs the best single messaging experience. In Reply 3 we‚Äôve introduced the ability for you to send a single fullscreen message to multiple people at once, without creating a group conversation.Use it for having a conversation, to share an announcement with your network or to notify people around you about what‚Äôs up!Enjoy!   ', u'description': u'The best single messaging experience. text_content: [{u'description': None, u'title': u'Relationup | Live Online Relationship Advice'}, {u'description': u'This is the only app with live chat 24/7 that matches you to professional Advisors for instant, private, and affordable help on relationship and dating issues. A Relationup Advisor can offer far more valuable and relevant advice for your situation than friends or forums, and is far cheaper and more convenient than looking for a therapist. ‚ÄúRelationship guidance from someone more qualified than your friends but less expensive and time-consuming than a therapist‚Äù --Glamour IMMEDIATE RELATIONSHIP ADVICE ANYTIME Connect with an Advisor in our easy to use private messaging interface. Sign up for free and answer just a few questions about yourself and your situation, and you can be chatting with an Advisor in just a few minutes. Instantly chat with an Advisor any time of day on your iOS device. Each Advisor has their own office hours you can check in case you want to keep chatting with the same one later. No appointments, no commitments - just access them on demand. LARGE NETWORK OF PROFESSIONAL ADVISORS PERSONALIZED JUST FOR YOU Advisors are qualified professionals who hold Master‚Äôs degrees or higher in related fields such as Marriage & Family Therapy, Social Work, Psychology, and Counseling to ensure guidance is competent and appropriate. They are hand-picked for their ability to get at the heart of your issue right away. Every Relationup Advisor has passed a background check and is continually monitored for quality. Relationup‚Äôs unique Match system instantly matches you to available Advisors based on your personal profile and situation for a personalized and meaningful chat. You choose the Advisor you wish for each chat. PRIVATE AND ANONYMOUS Chats are kept private and confidential. No other users can see you are in the app except Advisors you request to chat with. You can choose to create an anonymous profile to hide your name even from your Advisor. Even if not, only your first name is shared. CHAT FOR AS LONG AS YOU NEED AT A SIMPLE, AFFORDABLE PRICE You have the option to keep talking for as long as you need in 15-minute increments. A single 15-minute chat with an Advisor can be purchased for $12. WHAT USERS ARE SAYING What a fantastic, easy to use app! Excellent relationship advice on demand and at a fraction of what I've paid therapists over the years. A combo of empathetic listening yet firm, real, and actionable suggestions. Wow! --Bronty‚Äôsbuddy', u'title': u'Relationup - Get Live Help From a Professional For Relationship Advice Via Chat'}]

tagline: Discover the location of any Pokemon
text_content: [{u'description': u'Poke Radar for Pokemon GO is an assistant app for discovering the location of any Pokemon that's been found by other players. Using Poke Radar for Pokemon GO is extremely simple. You can view all of the nearby Pokemon in your area that have been discovered by your self and other players on the map, along with the times of day they were found. If you're trying to find a specific Pokemon's location, you can quickly use the "Filter" feature to find the nearest one. Since Poke Radar for Pokemon GO is driven by it's community, it's possible that there may not yet be Pokemon locations in your area when you first download the app. If this is the case, you can go out and mark the locations of Pokemon you've found to help other players in your area. When others view the location of the Pokemon locations you've marked, your trainer name will also be associated to aid your local trainer reputation. Everyone's gotta catch'em all - so why not work together? All Pokemon location submissions have the ability to be "Upvoted" or "Downvoted" by others. If a submission receives too many "Downvotes" it will be automatically removed from the map. Highly "Upvoted" locations will receive display priority on the map. Don't forget to check out our website www.PokeRadar.io FEATURES COMING WITHIN 2 DAYS - Remove your own pins. (If you need to remove a pin of yours now, simply downvote it) - Earlier iOS version support (iOS 8+). - Greatly improved UI. Want to use our app from a computer? Check out: http://www.pokeradar.io/ DISCLAIMER: Poke Radar for Pokemon GO is in no way affiliate with or endorsed by the Pokemon brand, Niantic or Nintendo. This app has been built by fans, for fans who love the Pokemon GO game and wanted to create this separate assistant app to support it's community.', u'title': u'Poke Radar for Pokemon GO'}]

tagline: Canvas for drawing in real-time with others around the world
text_content: [{u'description': u'Lotus is a creative canvas for drawing in real-time with others around the world. The real-time nature of a Lotus canvas allows you to interact with others in new and creative ways. Build on each other's work, draw in different colors, and explore new ideas like never before. Lotus recreates the experience of being in the same room, huddled around the same whiteboard. Lotus supports iPad Air and iPad Pro, all running iOS 9.1 and above. Lotus supports drawing with Apple Pencil and other common styluses. IN-APP SUBSCRIPTION REQUIRED A subscription fee of $1.99/month per unique iTunes Account is required to use Lotus. You will be asked once inside the app to buy a subscription. The first month is free and you will not be charged during that period. Following the first month, you will be charged $1.99 for a month‚Äôs worth of use. Payment will be charged to your iTunes Account at confirmation of the purchase. Your subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current month. Auto-renewal may be turned off by going to your iTunes Account Settings after purchase. Lotus Terms of Use: http://getlot.us/terms Lotus Privacy Policy: http://getlot.us/privacy', u'title': u'Lotus - Draw Together in Real-Time'}]

tagline: Pro Markdown writing, note taking and static blog generator
text_content: [{u'description': u'## Pro Markdown writing * Minimal UI, Dark Mode, optimized lists indent,five editor themes. * Markdown syntax and massive Markdown extensions Supported: Table, TOC, MathJax, Fenced code block and code syntax highlight, Task lists, Sequence & Flow chart, Footnote and more. * Typewriter Scrolling: `View` - `Typewriter Scrolling` * Publish/Update to Wordpress, Metaweblog API services, Wordpress.com, Evernote, Âç∞Ë±°Á¨îËÆ∞, Blogger, Medium, Tumblr. `Preferences` - `Publishing` to add publishing services. Click top-right corner `Share Button` for publishing. * Support six live preview themes. Easy to custom preview theme. All themes can export to HTML or PDF. To open live preview window, please press `CMD + R` or `CMD + 4`. * Export to RTF, Docx. * Support Outline view. ## External Mode and Library Mode 1. External Mode (CMD + E): This mode design for create, open external Markdown document. You can add external folder to this mode. 2. Library Mode (CMD + L): This mode design for note taking and static blog/website generator. Shortcuts `CMD + E` or `View` - `Open External` to open External Mode. Shortcuts `CMD + L` or `View` - `Open Library` to open Library Mode. External's folder and Library documents are supported **Full Text Search**, drag & drop or paste photos to the editor and display. `CMD + V` paste to JPG pictrue, `CMD + Shift + V` paste to PNG pictrue. ## Library Mode for note taking Library Mode use categories tree to organize documents, support drag & drop or paste insert pictrue and display immediately. Support import external Markdown or txt document to the library, export a category or documents to HTML, PDF or Markdown. More info, please check this post: [Introducing documents library](http://www.mweb.im/mweb-document-library.html) ## Library Mode for static blog generator You can build static blog **One Click**! Now has two blog themes, it's easy to custom you owner blog theme. you can add [AddThis](http://www.addthis.com/) and [Disqus](http://www.disqus.com) code for share and comment support to you blog. You can enable MathJax and Sequence & Flow chart support in category setting. More info, please check this post: [Introducing static blog generator](http://www.mweb.im/mweb-static-blog-generator.html)', u'title': u'MWeb - Pro Markdown writing, note taking and static blog generator App on the Mac App Store'}]

tagline: Swap shifts, share schedules, and message coworkers
text_content:
[{u'description': u'Swap shifts, share schedules, and message coworkers instantly with Shyft! Please email support@myshyft.com if you have any feedback or need support, we're always happy to help! ***Check Out These Awesome 100% FREE Features*** ***Are you a manager? Scroll down for Admin Features*** Shift Swaps ‚Äì Post your shift to your location‚Äôs private feed, with the date, time, location and note. Your team will be alerted that there is a shift available instantly, and you will get notified instantly when your shift gets covered. Boom. Regional Shift Swaps - Custom regional networks can be created for brands that allow shift swapping from store to store in a given region. Email us to request a free regional channel: support@myshyft.com Shift Approvals - Finally! No more phone calls and texts to your manager. When a team member covers your shift, your manager will be notified on Shyft and can approve or deny the swap request! View Schedules - Snap a quick photo of the weekly schedule, and send it as a push notification instantly to your team (ie."New schedule has been posted" in their notifications). The image will be high resolution. Comprende? Nice. Store Newsfeed - Post pics, give shoutouts, send links, and share jokes memes with your team on a private Instagram style feed for your store. Private Groups - Got departments? Front of house & back of house? Create customized feeds/channels for different employee groups within your location to swap shifts or to better organize your app. The ‚ÄòDM‚Äô - Keep your phone number private while direct messaging or group chatting with other contacts from your workplace. Feel like we don't need to describe that any further. Multiple Work Locations - If you hustle hard and work multiple jobs you can have a channel and store feed for shift swapping at each job. Manager Admins - Gain free admin status on Shyft through the app, and enable shift swap approvals, special posting privileges, read receipts on posts, location privatization, the ability to remove users, and the ability to curate content and posts. Honestly nobody said work was supposed to be easy, but Shyft makes it easy-er! #Shyftlife #GetShyft', u'title': u'Shyft - Shift Swapping Made Easy'}, {u'body': u' Swap shifts, share schedules, and message coworkers instantly with Shyft!Please email support@myshyft.com if you have any feedback or need support, we're always happy to help!***Check Out These Awesome 100% FREE Features***
***Are you a manager? Scroll down for Admin Features***Shift Swaps ‚Äì Post your shift to your location‚Äôs private feed, with the date, time, and note. Your team will be alerted that there is a shift available instantly, and you will get notified instantly when your shift gets covered. Boom.Shift Approvals - Finally! No more phone calls and texts to your manager. When a team member covers your shift, your manager will be notified on Shyft and can approve or deny the shift swap request! Regional Shift Swaps - Custom regional networks can be created for brands that allow shift swapping from store to store in a given region. Email us to request a free regional channel: support@myshyft.comView Schedules - Snap a quick photo of the weekly schedule, and send it as a push notification instantly to your team (ie."New schedule has been posted" in their notifications). The image will be high resolution. Comprende? Nice.Store Newsfeed - Post photos, post shifts, give shout-outs, send links, and share jokes memes with your team on a private Instagram style feed for your store. Private Groups - Got departments? Front of house & back of house? Create customized feeds/channels for different employee groups within your location to swap shifts or to better organize your app.The ‚ÄòDM‚Äô - Keep your phone number private while direct messaging or group chatting with other contacts from your workplace about shifts. Feel like we don't need to describe that any further.Multiple Work Locations - If you hustle hard and work multiple jobs you can have a channel and store feed for shift swapping at each job. Manager Admins - Gain free admin status on Shyft through the app, and enable shift swap approvals, special posting privileges, read receipts on posts, location privatization, the ability to remove users, and the ability to curate content and posts. Honestly nobody said work was supposed to be easy, but Shyft makes it easy-er!

tagline: Search printed documents, with your camera!
text_content:
[{u'body': u' Stop tracing your finger through long documents - CTRL-F allows you to quickly search all types of printed texts: Books, magazines, user manuals, and everything else you can think of! 
To search a document, simply scan the page using your device's camera. The app then analyses the document and you'll be able to search within it after a few seconds, just like you would with a digital document and CTRL-F on a PC!
Features:
* Search any printed document!
* Export as a fully searchable PDF
* Searches texts in over 50 languages
* Free and without ads
For best results, please make sure the document is well-lit. Use the flash, if possible. Keep the camera steady - if the image turns out blurry, taking a new picture is often quicker than using the blurry image.
Please note: CTRL-F doesn't work with handwritten notes and can occasionally be stumped by very strange fonts. Please let us know via e-mail if you've got feedback or questions!   ', u'description': u'Search, for the real world', u'title': u'CTRL-F - Search the real world - Android Apps on Google Play'}]

tagline: Send encrypted emails using your current email provider
text_content:
[{u'description': u'Meet Inky, the groundbreaking new app that makes exchanging encrypted mail with your existing Exchange and IMAP email account as easy as sending a text. Just install Inky and enter your email address and password (or use oAuth for Gmail accounts), and you're good to go! Inky will verify your account within 60 seconds, after which you can exchange encrypted email with any other Inky user! There are no keys, certificates, or fingerprints to manage: encrypted email with Inky works exactly like legacy insecure mail -- the only difference is that only the intended recipients can read the emails you send. Inky's encryption technology is based on the S/MIME standard. The difference is that Inky handles all the key and certificate management for you -- so you don't have to be a crypto expert to send secure mail. It just works. Inky encrypts emails with AES-256, deemed suitable for classified communications at the Top Secret level by the US Government. Your private keys are kept secret, and nobody but you has access to them -- not our employees, your email host, or anybody else. Complete details of our algorithms and operational procedures are available for public review at http://inky.com/secure. Of course, Inky offers all the email and calendar features you'd expect from a modern email client -- you can even search your inbox with hashtags like #pdf and #package with results returned instantly, as you type. Give Inky a try, and let us know what you think by dropping a line to hi@inky.com.', u'title': u'Secure Email - Inky for Office 365, Exchange, GMail, iCloud, and IMAP mail accounts'}, {u'body': u' End-to-End Encrypted Email that is a Delight to UseInky is a drop-in replacement for your email client that secures your email. Every message sent with Inky is digitally signed to prevent tampering and forgery. Simply tap the padlock icon when you compose an email message and Inky will also automatically encrypt it for any recipients who use Inky. With Inky there are no certificates to install or keys to remember.Inky is Easy ‚Äî Setup is a breeze ‚Äî add your existing email accounts in just a few steps, no technical expertise needed. After setting up Inky once, you can take advantage of Inky's time-saving features on your iOS, Mac or Windows desktop computer, too. Everything remains synchronized ‚Äî yet secure from prying eyes.Inky is Smart ‚Äî Inky understands what your messages are about, Inky downloads and analyzes your mail directly on your device, where it automatically sorts and filters messages into meaningful categories like Personal, Subscriptions, and Notes. Instantly search by keyword, contact, or even tags like #package or #pdf to find what you need fast! You can use hashtags for messages and senders, and even save searches.Inky is Safe ‚Äî Inky boasts state-of-the-art encryption and security with Zero Knowledge Proof cryptography so that your information stays safe. Unlike most email apps, Inky stores your email only on your device and your existing email servers, not Inky servers.Inky's playful-yet-refined design makes email enjoyable again. Who says secure email can't be smart, simple and safe?   ', u'description': u'Secure Email - Inky for Office 365, Exchange, GMail, iCloud, IMAP, EWS, Calendar', u'title': u'Inky Secure Mail - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': u'Inky makes exchanging encrypted and digitally signed email a breeze. It's 
as simple as regular email and works with any type of email account.', u'title': u'Inky'}]

tagline: Secure, permanent deletion of files and folders for your Mac
text_content: [{u'description': u'A beautiful file shredder for your Mac. 3 reliable and secure methods to erase sensitive data.', u'title': u'Shredo - Securely Erase Files and Folders / MyMixApps'}, {u'description': u'Shredo is a beautiful and functional file shredding utility. It permanently shreds files, folders and external volumes' contents to keep information secure and impossible for anyone to retrieve. Depending on security level and data erase speed, you have 3 shredding methods at your disposal: 1-pass Offers good security and quickest erase of data. It deletes access information to your files and writes random bytes over the data ONCE. 7-pass Slower speed, but better security than 1-pass. Writes over data 7 times, based on US Department of Defence (DoD) 5220-20 M standard algorithms. 35-pass Slowest, but offers best security. Erases file access info and writes over the data 35 times, based on the Gutmann method for deletion. Shredo supports external volumes and flash drives, but depending on their size and method selected, shredding time many vary. Should you have any questions, please contact us - support@mymixapps.com', u'title': u'Shredo - Securely and Permanently Erase Sensitive Files and Folders on the Mac App Store'}]

tagline: Prompts you to look up from your phone at intersections.
text_content:
[{u'body': u' Look Up is a participatory public art app that prompts New Yorkers to look away from their phones and into the street intersections to embrace the diversity and engage in the serendipity of the city. Whether it's strangers making eye contact and saying hello or friends hugging, Look Up hopes to tear down the digital walls we build up, opening us to seeing, acknowledging and valuing the people and city around us.
 
Look Up runs in the background and uses GPS to detect when participants are near an intersection. It prompts them to look up by vibrating and showing a notification if they‚Äôre in an app or showing eyeball animations in the background if they‚Äôre on their home screens. Look Up uses crash injuries and fatalities data to create a 1‚Äì5 energy score reminding participants why our streets need their energy, eyes, and ‚Äúhellos‚Äù. The higher the score, the more crashes, and the more energy participants should put back into those intersections. Participants can feel the energy score through the number of vibrations and see it in the number of iris rings in the eyeball animations. 
Look Up was made with Processing and support from Google Creative Lab‚Äôs Android Experiments. It‚Äôs free and open source. The iOS app as well as other cities will be available soon. So please email us or tweet with #lookupnyc if you think your city is starting to feel like a smartphone zombie apocalypse too!Read more at http://look-up.nyc.   ', u'description': u'Prompts New Yorkers to look up from their phones at street intersections.', u'title': u'Look Up - Android Apps on Google Play'}]

tagline: Book a last minute room with locals, in seconds.
text_content: [{u'description': u'WHAT WE DO Overnight is for quickly and easily booking a room for tonight. Save an average of 50% vs booking a hotel room in that same area by booking with a local on Overnight. Be spontaneous and know Overnight is there for last-minute stays. HOW IT WORKS ‚Ä¢ Request a place to stay tonight ‚Äî for up to 5 nights. ‚Ä¢ Hosts have 10 minutes to respond. ‚Ä¢ Pay safely through the app. ‚Ä¢ Rest easy. ‚Ä¢ Review your host and be on with your travels. :) Dozens of Trust and Safety Features including: ‚Ä¢ Facebook verification ‚Ä¢ Phone number Verification ‚Ä¢ Government ID Verification ‚Ä¢ Ratings and reviews ‚Ä¢ Mutual friends ‚Ä¢ 24 hour customer support with ‚Äãreal, nice and happy people. ‚Ä¢ tons more! BECOME A HOST ON OVERNIGHT ‚Ä¢ RENT YOUR EXTRA BEDROOMS & MORE - Turn any extra space you have into extra cash. ‚Ä¢ LIGHT + FAST - it takes two minutes to list your space. ‚Ä¢ NO CALENDARS - You decide in the moment when you feel like hosting someone. ‚Ä¢ PRIVACY - Turn private hosting on to remove your image and name from your listing. ‚Ä¢ List your extra bedrooms, apartment, hexi-yurts, futons, airstreams, mansions, beds in boats or bean bags. ‚Ä¢ Sync your calendar with other home-sharing platforms. Whether you‚Äôre staying across town, going on a weekend excursion or traveling for business, we have you covered. Check featured destinations every week for awesome destinations for push-button staycation ideas and book directly in the app. Explore, romance, adventure, all at your finger-tips. Use it to stay across town, across state lines, or across borders. From our living room to yours, The Overnight Team --- In Spontaneity We Trust. Instagram: @Overnight - Get inspired Twitter: @OvernightApp - let us know what you think Email our CEO: asher@joinovernight.com', u'title': u'Overnight - Book Last-minute Stays with Local Hosts'}, {u'description': u'Get the app ‚Äì Live on your own schedule and book same-day stays with local hosts', u'title': u'OVERNIGHT - Book Last-Minute Stays With Local Hosts'}]

tagline: Measure UI elements directly on your screenshots
text_content: [{u'description': u'The app that allows you to conveniently measure UI elements directly on your screenshots. Simply select a screenshot from your camera roll and measure the following with a few simple taps: DISTANCES - Measure distances and angles to double-check the alignment of your UI elements. - Measure the width and height or gutters and spacing of your UI elements. COLORS - Get HEX color codes directly from your screenshots. GUIDES - Show guidelines of screen halves, thirds or the iOS defaults. Great for app designers to double-check prototypes and make sure the layout is pixel perfect.', u'title': u'UI Check'}]

tagline: Take a picture of homework, and learn what you need
text_content: [{u'description': u'Point the camera at your homework question, and Socratic will teach you how to answer it! The Socratic app combines cutting-edge Artificial Intelligence (AI) with‚Ä¶', u'title': u'Socratic: Homework done in a snap on Vimeo'}, {u'description': u'Take a PHOTO of your homework question and get explanations and videos instantly. Supports SCIENCE, HISTORY, ENGLISH, ECONOMICS and more. This is homework app you‚Äôve been waiting for. (Math equations are not supported). ‚Ä¢ Fast - Take a photo, get instant results, no waiting ‚Ä¢ Explainers - Teaches you exactly what you need to learn ‚Ä¢ Videos - The best Youtube videos for your question ‚Ä¢ Powerful - Better than Google for homework help ‚Ä¢ Free - Free to use and always will be ~~ Students LOVE this 5 star app ~~ *Amazing* ‚ÄúWhenever I don't get homework I use this and it is helpful and useful. Usually apps either don't give you what you want or just give you the answer straight up. This app actually shows you the site the whole paragraph they found it in and more it's not like cheating‚Äù *Wow!!* ‚ÄúI only got this today, and it's already been a lifesaver. I've had apps that only helped with one subject or were too difficult to operate, but this one is so easy! I love it!‚Äù * ‚ÄúIt's way easier to search up things for hw instead of typing I really love the camera. I like how the whole system works!!! It helps me learn how to go search and get the answers for myself.‚Äù ~~ How it works ~~ Socratic is a homework app that combines cutting-edge Artificial Intelligence (AI) with amazing learning content to make learning on your phone easy. Take a picture of a homework question and our AI instantly figures out which concepts you need to learn in order to answer it, and shows you simple, high-quality content designed to make learning easy. Socratic‚Äôs AI combines cutting-edge computer vision technologies, which read questions from images, with machine learning classifiers built using millions of sample homework questions, to accurately predict which concepts will help you solve your question. Socratic‚Äôs team of educators is creating highly-visual, jargon-free content to teach every important high school curriculum concept, and is curating the best online videos from sources like Khan Academy, Crash Course, and others. Together, the Socratic app represents a huge improvement in how students learn on the Internet.', u'title': u'Socratic - Scan homework, get answers and explanations'}]

tagline: Cards Against Humanity meets GIFs
text_content: [{u'description': u'YIX is the most fun you will have with your friends all day and is the game you have been waiting for. Play with multiple friends or strangers by responding to a phrase with an expressive animated GIF supplied within the game or upload a GIF of your choice. Laugh and repeat for endless, addicting fun. YIX follows the same popular game playing format that you would find in Cards Against Humanity or Apples to Apples‚Ä¶ but with GIFs! How to play - Invite 3 or more friends to play with or play a game with strangers - Start a game by choosing between 3 phrases or customize your own question - Your friends will be given 10 GIFs to choose from to respond to your phrase - Once all your friends have played, you choose the winner - Next player in line becomes the new judge and starts a new round - After all players have been the judge a winner is chosen and the game is over Features - Tens of thousands of funny and entertaining GIFs with more added daily for endless comedy and fun - Discover hilarious and shocking GIFs that are difficult to find elsewhere - Search and invite friends using your contacts, Facebook and other social networks - Start playing by connecting with Facebook or by creating an account using email - Play with multiple friends and strangers in multiple games - Follow all of your games in one unified feed - Favorite any GIF and store for future creative plays - Upload your own GIFs and play them in the game or add them to your favorites - Share your plays and the plays of your friends to Facebook, Twitter, SMS and more - Nudge a group of players in a game to encourage them to play - Play YIX extra evil as a party drinking game', u'title': u'YIX: The Funny GIF Game To Play Against Your Friends'}]

text_content:
[{u'description': u'FamilyInSafe is an app for family and friends communication. It‚Äôs much more then messenger, location tracker or to-do list. This is family online - perfect way to stay close to people that really matter. WHAT IS HUB? Hub is a standalone community where people can share their private information. No one can join the hub without special invitation from one of it‚Äôs members. Invitation can be sent via email or Facebook Messenger. LOCATION TRACKING Battery-friendly, accurate and informative - it‚Äôs all about FamilyInSafe location tracking features. Real-time mode works like family finder. It shows you where your hub mates are and their smartphones battery charge level. Smart check-ins provide you with info about places that your family members visited and time they spent in each of them. Check-ins - perfect way to share something special with your loved ones. Geofencing. Be instantly notified when all or some of your hub mates enter or leave some specific places or areas. Continued use of GPS running in background can dramatically decrease battery life. FamilyInSafe app use smart location tracking technology that is very accurate and battery-friendly. So, you don't need to worry that your phone will turn off when you need it most. TO-DO LIST It‚Äôs all about collaboration. Create tasks, categorize and share them. Get things done with your family‚Äôs help. Set up smart reminders based on time and location to not forget about things that really matter. FAMILY BUDGETING See how much money you or your family members have spent on shopping, traveling or some other stuff. Find out who is the biggest money spender and optimize your monthly expenses. Easy! MESSAGING Communicate with your loved ones! Privately! No spam, no ads, no strangers! FamilyInSafe is a messenger, tasks list, location tracker and personal money management tool. Imagine perfect app for you family communication and collaboration. Install FamilyInSafe, try it‚Äôs awesome features. Give it a shot and you'll love it! tagline: Turn photos into production ready assets
text_content:
[{u'body': u' Quickly capture, edit and share uniquely crafted design assets ‚Äî including brushes, colors, filters, patterns and shapes ‚Äî to use in apps like Adobe Photoshop CC and Illustrator CC. It‚Äôs Brush CC, Color CC and Shape CC, all in one place.
COLORS
Extract color themes from photos and the world around you. Play with presets based on color theory ‚Äî optionally make changes with HSB and RGB sliders.Use with: After Effects CC, Dreamweaver, Animate CC (formerly Flash Professional CC), Illustrator CC, Illustrator Draw, InDesign CC, Muse, Photoshop CC
SHAPES
Instantly convert what you see, or have drawn, into vector graphics. Use the slider to adjust the level of detail, and tap specific details to keep/remove them.Use with: After Effects CC, Dreamweaver, Animate CC (formerly Flash Professional CC), Illustrator CC, Illustrator Draw, InDesign CC, Muse, Photoshop CC
BRUSHES
Turn inspiring photos or graphics into high-quality ribbon-, scatter- or vector-type brushes. Refine them with color, size and repetition adjustments.Use with: Dreamweaver, Animate CC (formerly Flash Professional CC), Illustrator CC, Muse, Photoshop CC 
LOOKS
Pull color and light from your favorite moments to make video-enhancing filters. A 3D histogram and intensity slider let you visualize and fine-tune your Looks.
 
Use with: After Effects CC, Dreamweaver, Animate CC (formerly Flash Professional CC), Muse, Premiere Pro CC
PATTERNS
Use an existing photo or take a new one and turn it into a pattern. Pick from several pattern grids and go from ordinary to extraordinary. Name and save that new asset to your CC Library then use it in a final design. Use with: Photoshop CC
ADOBE STOCK
Adobe Stock subscribers can search for and license high-res, royalty-free images from inside the app. Use your favorite photos to craft your assets.CREATIVE CLOUD LIBRARIES
Your library of assets automatically syncs to your Creative Cloud account ‚Äî so the assets you create in Capture CC are immediately accessible in compatible applications.POWERED BY CREATIVESYNC
Adobe CreativeSync ensures that your files, fonts, design assets, settings and more all instantly appear in your workflow wherever you need them. Start your creative work on any device and seamlessly pick it up on another.   ', u'description': u'Quickly capture, edit and share brushes, colors, filters, patterns and shapes', u'title': u'Adobe Capture CC - Android Apps on Google Play'}]

tagline: Book recommendations from people you trust
text_content: [{u'description': u'We believe that the best book recommendations come from people you trust. Reco is a simple way to share, discover, capture, and discuss the books you love with friends and trusted experts. Join the Reco community to: SHARE: Quickly share your favourite books (physical books, ebooks, audiobooks) with any friend, anywhere. Simpler and more inspiring than an email or a text. DISCOVER: Find great books personalized to your interests, curated for you by friends and trusted experts. Follow book lists from popular influencers. CAPTURE: Keep track of the books you want to read in a simple reading list. Gone are the days of spreadsheets, notepads, and self-emails. Buy books in any format. DISCUSS: Have thoughtful discussions about the stories you love with the people you trust.', u'title': u'Reco - Great books from real people'}]

tagline: Social photo printing
text_content: [{u'description': u'1st social photo printing app in Indonesia. Chaterpress gives you a fresh, neat and simple photo book you would love to show off. It‚Äôs affordable, lightweight and its 15x15 cm size means your beautiful photos can be enjoyed/viewed with ease. Ideal for life snapshots, photo journal, business, projects and even gifts for special events. Our app is designed with simplicity and convenience in mind. With a Chat feature, you can easily share photos and collaborate with your family and friends to create a joint book wherever they are. *Instagram Private Edition - Create photo books of your own Instagram feeds - Allows for up to 4 Instagram accounts - Filter your Instagram photos using hashtags - 60 pages of thick matte quality paper finished with perfect binding - Choose between Basic, Minimal and Creative book layouts *Collective Edition - Photos from multiple sources (Instagram, Facebook and your device) *Auto Happiness Your photobook volume will automatically be updated for every photo you have uploaded into Instagram. Once it is ready we will let you know for you to order, so you can sit back and we take care of the rest. *Gift card - A great way to introduce someone to Chaterpress photo books, or for that last minute gift. All books are IDR 150,000. Free shipping to major cities (only Indonesia). We use "Wallet" as our payment method - a secured payment system where you can top up your Chaterpress account credit balance through bank transfer. Therefore, you are not required to provide your bank account or credit card details.', u'title': u'Chaterpress'}]

tagline: Turn anything into art in two taps
text_content:
[{u'body': u' The one and only original ‚Äì the best styling app on the market. Use ANY STYLE IN THE WORLD to turn your photos into incredible artwork!You've seen watered down apps like Prisma that only let you use a few styles. Pikazo is the original and best art app. Any artwork you can find on the web can be used as your own style!From one of the grandmasters of digital art comes an explosion of the most interesting images the world's ever seen. Turn any photo into compelling, lasting visual art. Using next generation neural networks, Pikazo works the way your brain does to rip apart and assemble image details into something new and extraordinary.Created by the image scientist behind landmark visuals seen in the Myst games, The Matrix films, 300, and Second Life, Pikazo lets anyone create and share beautiful artwork.
Pikazo is at the very bleeding edge of neural network software. It really, truly, actually works by simulating the way your brain sees images. This is incredibly computationally intensive, and even on a cloud of the fastest computers, it takes a few minutes to process each image.Sometimes Pikazo paints masterpieces; amazing images that take the air out of the room. Sometimes it doesn't.Sometimes, it doesn't work at all.To be honest, we're not yet sure why it works. That's why we need your help ‚Äì to discover what types of images are successful and what aren't.We would like to sincerely thank the following genius digital neurosurgeons who made Pikazo possible: Leon Gatys, Alexander Ecker, and Matthias Bethge at Bethge Lab at University of T√ºbingen; Justin Johnson and Kai Sheng Tai at Stanford University; Karen Simonyan and Andrew Zisserman at the Visual Geometry Group at University of Oxford; Alexander Mordvintsev, Chris Olah, and Mike Tyka at Google.   ', u'description': u'Turn photos into art with *ANY* style you find! Show off your taste with art!', u'title': u'Pikazo - Make anything  art - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': u'How to make anything art in just two taps: 1. Start with any image in the universe 2. Choose a style image of anything that ever has, will, or can exist 3. Repeat! REMEMBER ART CLASS? Tables speckled with the bright drops of yellow, red, and blue paint that never made it to a student‚Äôs canvas. The faint smell of clay from misshapen forms left to dry on a shelf, waiting for the kiln. The feel of charcoal between finger and thumb, strangely warm and imprecise. We believe that art is a universal birthright, and we created Pikazo to help you claim it. Pikazo doesn‚Äôt care if you‚Äôre Bob Ross or can‚Äôt even doodle. Unlike oils or acrylics, the neural algorithms it uses obey an accountant or athlete as precisely as a master painter. Pikazo in hand, the world is now yours. Make it art. Maybe you‚Äôre a professional artist now and you‚Äôre adding Pikazo images to a toolkit alongside brushes and turpentine. Or maybe the charcoal seemed to disobey you intentionally, you swore the paint preferred the table, and your sculpture was mistaken for discarded clay and never made it to the kiln. And maybe, ever since that art class, you‚Äôve believed that art was something other people did - special, privileged people who could take anything in the world and magically make it art. JOIN THE ART WORLD, NO BERET NEEDED. As a Pikazo artist, you are cordially invited to exhibit your work in the exclusive Salon, a gathering where like-minded creatives praise and critique each other‚Äôs art while, we assume, sipping espresso and wearing black. FRESH, PREMIUM STYLES EVERY WEEK. From the paintings of Pablo Picasso himself to the masonry of Angkor Wat, the world we see is packed with beautiful art that can be applied to any photo using Pikazo. Every week, we seek out the style images that deliver the most beautiful results and deliver them with a dose of creative inspiration. TO AN ARTIST, ART IS EVERYTHING. TO PIKAZO, EVERYTHING IS ART. Pikazo is a collaboration between human, machine, and our concept of art. It is an experiment to see what emerges when anyone can create a masterpiece. It is yoga for the brain. Brain for the yoga. For for the the. It is a universal art machine that paints any image in the style of any other, producing sometimes-beautiful, sometimes-disturbing, always-surprising artworks. We encourage you to play. We can't wait to see what you make with it!', u'title': u'Pikazo ‚Äî Make anything art in just two taps.'}]

tagline: The first virtual assistant in personal finance.
text_content: [{u'description': u'THE FIRST VIRTUAL ASSISTANT IN PERSONAL FINANCE XOBI gives you instant knowledge and control over your spending ‚Äî immediately improving the quality of your life. ASK XOBI anything in your own words! Enjoy XOBI‚Äôs beautiful visualization of your financial transactions all in a secure environment that uses bank level encryption, tokenization, and touch ID. ASK XOBI ANYTHING Using cutting edge artificial intelligence, you can talk to XOBI in plain language. XOBI can answer anything you want to know and will suggest questions too‚Ä¶ ‚ÄúHow much did I spend on eating out last month?‚Äù ‚ÄúHow much is my average water bill?‚Äù ‚ÄúHow much did I spend on my trip to Spain?‚Äù XOBI can tell you ‚Äî instantly. XOBI gives you the knowledge to make smarter decisions about your life ‚Äî and knowledge is power. XOBI puts the power directly into your hands ‚Äî where it belongs. XOBI IS BEAUTIFUL XOBI attaches visual images to all your transactions automatically. You can add your own photos, notations, receipts ‚Äî anything you‚Äôd like to enrich your personal financial library. But even without doing anything, XOBI will organize every financial transaction in your life. XOBI operates under the simple principle that in this modern age you should have the best information of all. All in one place. Wrapped inside a single elegant secure app that takes the anxiety out of spending money, allowing you total control over your financial life. At XOBI, knowledge is not only power ‚Äî knowledge is also happiness. XOBI IS SECURE Secured first with AES-128 encryption and secondly with SSL/TS Multi-factor authentication, Automatic logouts, Ensured with your 4-digit pin and touch ID. XOBI links your banking and credit card accounts. You will need your username and password for your financial institution to establish a secure and encrypted connection. We use this information once and immediately discard it. We never store your credentials. XOBI KEY FEATURES ENRICHES AND CURATES YOUR TRANSACTIONS XOBI adds a category assignment, logo, image and other key information when available. ALLOWS FURTHER PERSONALIZATION WITH NOTES, RECEIPTS, and PHOTOS Annotate your transactions with things you need to remember such as ‚Äútax related,‚Äù or a photo of a birthday present. ACCESS YOUR LIBRARY USING NATURAL LANGUAGE OR VOICE RECOGNITION Not an accountant? Just ask in your own words, ‚ÄúWhere does my money go?‚Äù GROUP TRANSACTIONS INTO LIFE EVENTS AND SHARE CURATED FEEDS After XOBI enriches your your data and you personalize it, group transactions by tapping to create a LIFE Event. Great for sharing recommendations from a vacation or a business trip. Choose to share with or without dollar amounts. AUTOMATED RECEIPT MATCHING Upload or email a receipt and XOBI will automatically attach your receipt to the appropriate transaction. tagline: Scans your hand & lets you try-on rings
text_content: [{u'description': u'Want to try on dozens of trendy engagement and wedding rings on your hand without even leaving your room - Say Yes! app makes it possible! Download this app now and ‚Äúfeel that the future is already here‚Äù, as Digital Trends described it. It is a new iOS app that uses hand recognition to scan your hand, and augmented reality technology to virtually put a ring on it. After trying it on, you can click the price button to order the ring and get it delivered. Find a matching engagement ring for your special occasion, present to the one you love and would like to impress - just using your iPhone. You can easily move the gorgeous wedding ring to any other finger. Just press the ring and drag it to the other finger; to zoom in and move tap the ring twice. Another useful feature of the app is ability to share the final look of your hand with a ring digitally added atop on Instagram, Facebook, Pinterest or via e-mail. You don't have to ask for a gift, but you do need to drop a hint. This mobile jewelry store connects to your iPhones built-in camera to scan and take a photo of your hand, and then augmented reality technology places the ring accurately where it belongs. Regular catalogs, either printed or digital, show us images of wedding and engagement rings, bracelets and necklaces on models or alone. They may look amazing on the pictures, but even most vivid imagination will not guarantee it will look good on you. Jewelry market leaders know about this problem, and introduce this app with augmented reality technology as a solution to it. No more blind online orders, no more disappointment afterwards, just choose a ring with a design you would like to try on, click the ‚ÄúTry On Screen‚Äù button and see how exactly that piece of jewelry will look on your hand. Our try on app helps both customers and vendors to make a step towards each other: it encourages vendors to connect their e-shops and enrich variety of choice, while helping customers to move forward on their decision-making path.', u'title': u'Say Yes! - find and try on engagement rings by top brands of gold, silver, diamond jewelry'}, {u'description': u'If you are just about to make a proposal or looking for wedding inspiration, virtually try on our collection of engagement rings in the Say Yes! app. Marketing engagement rings online has never been easier - feature your items on our wedding jewellery mar', u'title': u'AR jewellery mobile apps for wedding marketing - business plans and ideas'}]
