tagline: Emoji to celebrate women
text_content: [{u'description': u'Attention girls, ladies, sisters, mothers, daughters, women of all shapes, sizes and nationalities. Do you like to run, play ball, or do yoga? Are you a doctor, dancer, or student? Do you have red hair or brown skin? Well, now you can express yourself ‚Äì with She-Moji! This first release Starter Pack grants you access to over 400 new emoji representing female diversity, from Indian karate masters and red-headed chefs, to latina weightlifters and blonde astronauts. The app also includes a set of phrases, from ‚ÄúSlay All Day‚Äù to ‚ÄòOm Shanti‚Äô. Or if you just want to express your mood, style or give a shout out to your BFF, we have that too! Installing the She-Moji keyboard lets you easily add these unique characters to your messages via text, Facebook Messenger, Twitter, WhatsApp, Slack and SnapChat (chat only). Created by DLS Studios Developer: Devin Ross - devinross.com Animations: Blair Burke - blairburke.com FOLLOW US: Want to request a specific She-Moji? We know we haven‚Äôt represented all women in this starter pack, but next we'll be growing the She-Moji girl gang with characters requested by you! So download today and then use #makemyshemoji to let us know what you want to see in future app updates: Twitter: @shemojiapp Instagram: @she.moji Email: hello@she-moji.com INSTRUCTIONS: After downloading the app, go to iOS Settings and add "She-Moji Keyboard" from third-party keyboards. Make sure to turn on ‚ÄúAllow Full Access‚Äù. Please rest assured that She-Moji will never collect any personal information or transmit what you type over any network. Turning on ‚ÄúAllow Full Access‚Äù is simply an iOS requirement for third party keyboards. Allowing full access does not give us access to any of your other keyboards, only to the She-Moji keyboard. We take your privacy very seriously. DISCLAIMERS: She-Moji, its designs, all assets & artwork are the sole property of DLS Studios and it's partners. Despite the warning by Apple regarding installing third-party keyboards, we do not gain access to any private information and we do not monitor your keystrokes. It is currently not possible for app developers to create new emoji keyboards that work like the ones installed on your phone. The process to create and release emojis is highly restricted, so until those rules change, we've come up with the next best thing. She-Mojis are sent as images that you need to copy and paste. Therefore additional MMS and data rates may apply. There is no qwerty keyboard included in She-Moji - it‚Äôs nearly impossible to build one better than your regular keyboard, so just use the globe and ‚ÄòABC‚Äô icons in the bottom left of your keyboards to switch between Apple and She-Moji. It‚Äôs as easy as that!', u'title': u'She‚ÄìMoji'}]

tagline: UK‚Äôs most influential music blogs streamed as playlists
text_content: [{u'description': u'Playlist Everything you find in Lost. Listen to our selection of the UK‚Äôs most influential music blogs & magazines streamed as playlists, featuring all the music they‚Äôre talking about. Import your playlists from YouTube, SoundCloud, Apple Music & Spotify. Search and create playlists across services, our curators and your collection, without anything getting in your way. The Lost Curators ‚Äì the music and video they‚Äôre talking about, updated daily. LOST‚Äôs official curators are: FACT, VICE‚Äôs music channels Noisey & Thump UK, Mahogany, UKF, i-D, The Line of Best Fit, Dummy, The 405, Complex UK, Clash Magazine, Data Transmission, Rockfeedback, Gold Flake Paint, The Ransom Note, Inverted Audio, Stamp the Wax, Hyponik, Harder Blogger Faster, Get Into This and Fortitude Magazine. Every track our curators review we match to artists catalogues in Spotify and Apple Music - so if you‚Äôre a premium subscriber sign-in and you can easily dig deeper. For live music fans we‚Äôve partnered with Songkick, the leading independent artist-ticketing and live discovery platform, to make it easy for users to find tour dates and buy tickets directly from the app. Search for artists across YouTube, SoundCloud, Apple Music and Spotify ‚Äì add anything you find directly to your playlists ‚Äì never lose a good track again. Follow blogs or friends so that you can always stay up to date with what‚Äôs new. Add your own artwork to any of your playlists. Share tracks and playlists easily across Facebook, Twitter, WhatsApp, SMS and email.', u'title': u'Lost Music ‚Äì Playlist Everything'}, {u'description': u'', u'title': u'LOST is an independent music service that will help you discover new music and video from top festivals, blogs and music sites.'}]

tagline: Easy workout tracking with friends
text_content:
[{u'body': u' Squid is a simple way to track the number of times you worked out in a week and compete with friends. We know that people generally have a weekly workout goal, so this app helps you stay consistent and motivated. Don‚Äôt be a Squid
Squid status is reserved for users that don‚Äôt log at least 1 workout in a given week. The objective is to not be the squid within your friend group. Workout counts are reset each week, so every week is a new week where you can be at the top. Features: 
 - Simple workout logging of an activity and a location.
 - History, intuitively depicting your past workouts so you can see how consistent you have been over time 
 - Ability to view friend‚Äôs workout history
 - Squid Slap your friends, motivate your friends to workout
 - Activity Feed to keep an eye on which of your friends are working out and getting slapped   ', u'description': u'Fitness Motivation and Tracking', u'title': u'Squid - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': u'Squid is a simple way to track the number of times you worked out in a week and compete with friends. tagline: The beautifully simple note-taking app
text_content:
[{u'body': u' Take notes, create checklists, record audio, and capture moments using Notebook. All your notes are instantly synced across your devices and to the cloud.
 
The simple, intimate joy of Notebook comes from using the app. We've been meticulous in our design, paying attention to every detail.
 
 
TAKE NOTE
 
Notebook provides different ways to take notes and capture your thoughts.
 
- Write notes. Start with text, add images, checklists, or audio, all in the same note.
- Create checklists to get stuff done with the dedicated checklist note card.
- Record audio notes while driving with the audio note card.
- Capture moments using the dedicated photo note card.
 
 
ORGANIZE NOTES
 
- You can organize various notes into notebooks.
- Notes can be grouped together.
- You can reorder your notes within a notebook.
- Move or copy note cards between notebooks.
 
 
SYNC
 
- Synchronize all your notes and notebooks across devices and to the cloud.
- Take a note on one device, add to it from another.
 
 
NOTABLE GESTURES
 
- Swipe your notebook or note card for additional information.
- Pinch to group note cards into a stack.
- Flick to find the note cards you need.
- In landscape view, pinch to fold note cards like an accordion.
 
 
CUSTOMIZE
 
- Change the color of your note cards.
- Choose a notebook cover or create your own.
- View your note cards in either grid- or landscape-style views.
- Create shortcuts for any Notebook on your home screen.
- Continue recording audio on any screen of your android device.
 
 
FIND NOTES- Search your notes within a notebook or across notebooks.
 
SHARE- Share your notes through email and other options.
 
 
Notebook is FREE. No Ads. No catch.
 
If you have any questions, please reach out to us at support@zohonotebook.com
 
Additional information about the app is available at zoho.com/notebook   ', u'description': u'Take notes, create checklists, record audio, and capture moments using Notebook', u'title': u'Notebook - Take Notes, Sync - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': u'Take notes, create checklists, record audio, and capture moments using Notebook. tagline: Track what apps you use the most on iOS
text_content: [{u'description': u'Track how much you and your family use your phone and tablet each day, automatically ‚Ä¢ See what apps you use the most too! Moment is the first and only app on the App Store to do this. ‚Ä¢ Set daily limits on yourself and find a balance for the screens in your life. Moment Family ‚Ä¢ Monitor all of your family member's screen time too. - Look at your entire family's day from the comfort of your own device. ‚Ä¢ Start screen-free family dinner time, which means for the next 60 minutes, every time a person in your family picks up their phone or tablet, an annoying alert will go off and everyone will hear it. How embarrassing! - You can decide how long each family dinner time will last. - Everyone in your family can start family dinner time, including your children. - Schedule it for the same time every day. ‚Ä¢ Change a family member's daily limit and force them to put down their phone when they're over that limit. The Highlights ‚Ä¢ Tracks how much you use your phone or tablet automatically. ‚Ä¢ Keeps track of what apps you use the most almost automatically. ‚Ä¢ Trains you with the Coach to use your phone less, if that's your goal. ‚Ä¢ Logs how many times you pick up your phone each day. ‚Ä¢ Force yourself off your device when you're over your limit, and force your family members to do the same. ‚Ä¢ Break down each day to see when you're on your device and what apps you're using. ‚Ä¢ Tracks where you go each day, and have it plotted on a map. ‚Ä¢ Invisible app. Once you set it up and as long as the app is running in the background, you never have to open it again. ‚Ä¢ Choose from 6 relaxing reminder sounds and 6 intense sounds for your daily limit reminders. Apple Watch ‚Ä¢ Quickly see how long you and your family have used your phone today. - You'll see a colorful icon for each one of your family members on your glance. Green means well under their daily limit, yellow means getting close, and red screams they went overboard. ‚Ä¢ No, the app doesn't track how long you spend looking at your watch. Warning to parents: Moment is not strictly about parental control. Using Moment Family as a parent gives you certain powers, but your children have power too. ‚Ä¢ If your daughter notices you on your phone while you're supposed to be watching a family movie together, she can start family dinner time for the entire family until the movie is over. That means no one can pick up their phone, and you as the parent can't turn that family dinner time off. ‚Ä¢ Your entire family can see everyone else's phone use for the day from the family scoreboard. You can see if your son is over his limit for the day, and he can see if you are over yours! Continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life. Moment has been designed to use GPS sparingly.', u'title': u'Moment - Track how much you and your family use your phone'}, {u'description': None, u'title': u'Moment ‚Äì Automatically track your and your family's daily iPhone and iPad useMegaphone icon for the CoachList of the apps you use the mostInfinity icon'}]

tagline: Gas magically delivered to your parked car
text_content:
[{u'body': u' Yoshi makes it so that you never have to go to another gas station.Use the Yoshi app to get filled up while your car is parked at work during the day, or at home.BENEFITS
- Save the Planet - Driving to gas stations wastes 1 billion gallons a year and underground tanks often leak. Yoshi offers a more environmentally friendly solution.
- Save Time - The average commuter spends 8 hours per year at gas stations. With Yoshi, that's time you can spend in a million other ways.
- Save Money - As a member, receive discounted gas prices. No more searching around town for a good price on gas.FEATURES
- Enter your car make, model, and what kind of fuel it takes
- Signup for autopilot and Yoshi will automatically fill your car every week so you never think about gas again
- Get a notification when Yoshi is done and your car is filled 
- Securely store your payment information for future fill-ups   ', u'description': u'Help save the planet by having Yoshi refuel your vehicle wherever you are!', u'title': u'Yoshi - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': u'Yoshi makes it so that you never have to go to another gas station. Use the Yoshi app to get filled up while your car is parked at work during the day, or at home. BENEFITS - Save the Planet - Driving to gas stations wastes 1 billion gallons a year and underground tanks often leak. Yoshi offers a more environmentally friendly solution. - Save Time - The average commuter spends 8 hours per year at gas stations. With Yoshi, that's time you can spend in a million other ways. - Save Money - As a member, receive discounted gas prices. No more searching around town for a good price on gas. FEATURES - Enter your car make, model, and what kind of fuel it takes - Signup for autopilot and Yoshi will automatically fill your car every week so you never think about gas again - Get a notification when Yoshi is done and your car is filled - Securely store your payment information for future fill-ups Note: Background GPS is only used for Yoshi delivery drivers. Continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life.', u'title': u'Yoshi!'}, {u'description': u'Never go to the gas station again. Yoshi will come and fill-up your car while you're parked. It saves time, money, and the planet.', u'title': u'Yoshi - Never Go to Another Gas Station '}]

tagline: Discover cities through customized walking itineraries
text_content: [{u'description': u'The only map of touristic and simply beautiful places, with on demand itineraries mapping a beautiful route. Our mission is to help you discover amazing places. 1- The best itineraries for your strolls, in more than 50 cities in America and Europe, including Paris, London, New York, Montreal, Boston, Chicago & San Francisco... Let us know which city should be next! Unique in the world (oh yeah!): your itinerary is personalized for your time and interests, suggesting the optimal number of beautiful and interesting stops. 2- Mapping all beautiful spots Have a look on the map and identify at a glance the highlighted beautiful spots and streets (monuments, cafes, hidden gems‚Ä¶) 3- Share beautiful places Rate the places you love (or those you don't) & add your own discoveries to the map. you will contribute to create a global map of beautiful places. How about starting to choose the beautiful itineraries rather than going through the fastest? This is our beginning, so everything is faaaar from perfect, but you can help us get closer. Let us know what you think! fabrice@pretty-streets.com PS: Continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life. But you can turn if off within the app!', u'title': u'Pretty Streets - Map of Beautiful Places'}, {u'description': u'Pretty-Streets', u'title': u'Pretty Streets : walk in the city through beautiful streets'}]

tagline: Create moving photos with one easy tap
text_content: [{u'description': u'Memories move. Now photos do too. Polaroid Swing lets you create moving photos with one easy tap. Capture one-second moments that magically come to life when you touch them or swing your iPhone. Share Polaroid moving photos with your followers on Polaroid Swing and out to Facebook or Twitter. Explore the best of this unique new visual medium through Featured Artists. Polaroid moving photos recreate life‚Äôs special moments: the kiss goodbye, the face breaking into a smile, the hair blowing in the wind. They combine the composition of a still with the vitality of a world that‚Äôs always moving. With Polaroid Swing you can also: Reverse the moving photo to perfect the moment. Take 3D selfies by rotating your phone around you. Select live filters for inky smooth Polaroid moving photos. Create your own moving profile image ‚Äì and add a tint via settings. Connect your Facebook and Twitter accounts to find friends. No passwords to remember! Sign up with Facebook, Twitter or magic link. The Polaroid Classic border is a trademark of PLR IP Holdings, LLC.', u'title': u'Polaroid Swing'}]

tagline: Never forget your medicine again
text_content:
[{u'body': u' With simple & elegant timeline, detailed inventory and smart notifications, Dose Direct takes away the hassle of users who juggle several medications at once, and makes sure they never miss a single dose ever again.
‚ÄúJust follow the prescription and you‚Äôll be fine.‚Äù
It‚Äôs supposed to be that simple.
But if it is, we wouldn‚Äôt see statistics like this.
-	80% of patients have occasionally missed at least one dose.
-	20% to 80% of patients make errors in taking medication.
-	20% to 60% of patients stop taking medications before being instructed to do so.
-	Less than 50% of patients with chronic conditions adhere to medication prescription.
Aside from treatment failure, patients‚Äô not correctly following medication instructions can cause an increase of $2,000 per patients in annual physician visits.
* Sources: Adherence to long-term therapies: evidence for action. - World Health Organization, Geneva; 2003
- - - - - -
No matter what the reason is, Dose Direct can change that:
-	Remind you when it‚Äôs time to take your pill with Dose Direct‚Äôs smart notifications
-	Remind you when your pill is running out, so you can get a refill
-	Beautiful timeline, let you know which pill you need to take each day, or each week
-	Quickly view your prescription intake history on any given day
-	Track your pill by doctor who described, or the prescription it belongs to
Dose Direct is the one stop for all your medicine scheduling needs.
- - - - - -
Please email us if you have any questions or suggestions to improve the app: support@ominext.com   ', u'description': u'Dose Direct is all your medicine scheduling needs rolled into one beautiful app.', u'title': u'Dose Direct ‚Äì Medicine Alert - Android Apps on Google Play'}]

tagline: Call multiple people simultaneously
text_content:
[{u'body': u' redCall is a free mobile app that allows you to make a phone call to a large number of users at once.
The way it works: your audience (i.e. followers) add you as a speaker on the redCall app, after which whenever you want to share with them a message in a personal way, you would go on redCall, record a voice message and press send. Instantaneously, your audience phones would ring as if you are personally calling them - exactly replicating a phone call.Your audience would pick up and listen to your call. If they are unable to answer, your message will be stored in a voicemail section in the app. Whether users in your audience pick up straight away or listen to the voicemail afterwards, your call can only be listened to once.   ', u'description': u'Connect with who you love & what you care about in the liveliness of phone calls', u'title': u'redCall - life, in phone calls - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': u'Connect with who you love and what you care about, all in the liveliness of phone calls. *** Winner of the London Entrepreneurship Forum 2015 First Prize - Voted Most Promising Startup! *** redCall is a free mobile app that allows you to make a phone call to a large number of users at once. The way it works: your audience (i.e. followers) add you as a speaker on the redCall app, after which whenever you want to share with them a message in a personal way, you would go on redCall, record a voice message and press send. Instantaneously, your audience phones would ring as if you are personally calling them - exactly replicating a phone call. Your audience would pick up and listen to your call. If they are unable to answer, your message will be stored in a voicemail section in the app. Whether users in your audience pick up straight away or listen to the voicemail afterwards, your call can only be listened to once.', u'title': u'redCall ‚Äì life, in phone calls'}]

tagline: The easiest and fastest way to make plans with your friends
text_content: [{u'description': u'Easily and quickly make plans with your friends. You can now spend less time planning and more time with the people around you. Say goodbye to tough decision making and massive back and forth group messages. Now all you need is PlanItUp. PlanItUp lets you create events with up to three options for date, location and time, the three key components that define an event. Once you invite your friends, they can easily see these options and pick anonymously the ones that fit them. This way everybody can freely select what they really want to do without peer pressure. The rule of thumb is to eliminate at least one option for each of the component when voting. Once voted, PlanItUP handles everything to ensure decision making by majority. Once the final plan is displayed, all you have to do is to confirm your attendance so that your friends can get excited to do things with you. And one more thing. We believe proper event planning should not require planning over and over. Therefore, we decide to let you decide the day and location of your event before the host can send your time options. This way you can decide on a better time to meet up because a reservation at a restaurant is not always guaranteed at the same time every day. PlanItUp lets you: - Create an event - Provide up to three options for location and date initially (Step 1) - Send it to the people you hand pick and let them see who is part of your event - Let them review and vote on their preference (by eliminating at least one option) - Majority rules and decides - Based on your results for location and date, now send them your time options (Step 2) - Let them review and vote again on those - Majority rules and decides now the final plan ‚Äî you know the location, date and time for your event now - Finally, let people know if you are coming or taking a ‚Äúrain check‚Äù (meaning no show) and see who else is joining you (Step 3) - Easily get directions to your event or add it to your calendar for reference from our app', u'title': u'PlanItUp'}, {u'description': None, u'title': u'PlanItUp ‚Äì The easiest and fastest way to make plans with your friends'}]

tagline: Visual learning app with 1,000 interactive 3D models
text_content: [{u'description': u'Download this app from Microsoft Store for Windows 10, Windows 8.1. See screenshots, read the latest customer reviews, and compare ratings.', u'title': u'Lifeliqe ‚Äì Windows Apps on Microsoft Store'}, {u'description': u'Lifeliqe is presenting a learning and productivity platform for interactive 3D, VR and AR with about 1,000 interactive 3D models in breathtaking quality and detail. For the very first time, learners with iOS devices have the chance to exclusively access the professional grade models of Corinth Classroom. Lifeliqe is customized for various topics in the K-12 curriculum in the following subjects: human anatomy, animal and plant biology, geology, chemistry, physics, geometry, paleontology, and history. All Lifeliqe content is scientifically accurate and guaranteed by professors from renowned universities around the world, such as Stanford University. New 3D models are added every week. Lifeliqe is a media company for the publishing and sharing of interactive 3D, virtual reality (VR) and 3D printable media. Education is the first industry launching on the Lifeliqe platform with more to follow. POWER OF VISUAL LEARNING Did you know that 65% students around the world describe themselves as visual learners? Lifeliqe‚Äòs intuitive tool allows everyone to study each model from all angles and distances. Turn the models with a simple swipe or zoom in with a pinch. CREATE RESOURCES WITH 3D MODELS With Lifeliqe Creator feature, educators have the power to create and publish interactive presentations and ebooks which integrate interactive 3D models instead of just flat images. LANGUAGE LEARNING WITH BILINGUAL VIEW Give your students a chance to learn scientifically correct vocabulary in two languages ‚Äì English and Spanish. You can change them easily on the menu and even display them at once. SHARING TO KEYNOTE OR POWERPOINT Each model can be shared as a slide for your presentation. While presenting, click the image or a link to the slide to instantly open the model in Lifeliqe app. AUGMENTED REALITY Augmented reality merges the real world with 3D models. Unleash your creativity and take impressive photos and videos. CHANGE BACKGROUND COLOR Predefined color schemes allow you to control the background of the models. If you're not satisfied with the background color you can change it in the menu. INTRODUCTION AND NOTES Nearly all Lifeliqe models have their own introductory content that explains what you‚Äôre seeing. You can also create your own notes to every model. DEEP ZOOM Explore the depths of a plant cell, human bone or hair structure. With many of our models, our unique deep zoom allows you to smoothly go from the surface all the way down to the cellular level. NOTICE Lifeliqe is packed with about 1,000 interactive 3D models. Protecting your available storage is important, which is why Lifeliqe adapts automatically to what's left on your device. Whether you have a small amount of memory available or a lot, Lifeliqe always leaves you with a significant amount of available storage space. SUBSCRIPTION PLANS Users can choose a monthly or annual subscription. Start your free trial and choose your preferred subscription. $14.99 USD / month: try it risk-free for 1 month $119.99 USD / year: try it risk-free for 2 months Annual subscription equals only $9.99 USD / month: you save almost $60 USD with a 1-year subscription. After your free trial ends, your iTunes account is automatically charged at the beginning of each month. Get in touch with the community and explore all the possibilities Lifeliqe offers. Contact us at: www.lifeliqe.com www.facebook.com/lifeliqe www.twitter.com/lifeliqe Privacy policy and terms of use: http://www.lifeliqe.com/privacy/ http://www.lifeliqe.com/terms-of-service/', u'title': u'Lifeliqe'}]

tagline: The best listening experience for podcasts
text_content: [{u'description': u'# UCast for iOS¬Æ, the ultimate podcast player 1) UCast is an application created by and for podcast followers. UCast is the first player podcast born with the philosophy of putting together design, a friendly interface, and also all customization and personalization for the most advanced and expert users. The application has a smart adaptation for each podcast you're listening, creating a personal experience for each show. 2) UCast has been designed using all the latest updates and features of iOS 9 with builtin support for 3D Touch technology and Spotlight searches to find your podcast. It also incorporates gestures controls to playback and manage podcast, everything has been designed to be simple, natural and intuitive. In addition, UCast, it is fully compatible with iPhone and iPad. ## Features * GESTURES BASED INTERFACE - There is nothing more natural than a gesture. So in UCast you can control playback with simple gestures on the screen. * SPEED CONTROL - Short of time but still want to hear all your playlist. Adjust the speed to your needs without losing audio quality thanks to our innovative system to control speed. * IMPROVED AUDIO - Feel like a whisper in your ear. Enjoy a unique sound experience thanks to our improved audio enhancement. * CONTINUOUS PLAY - Your favorite podcast, now without limits. UCast can play nonstop your favorite podcasts or those in the queue. * DESIGN - A unique experience. In UCast, each screen has been specially designed so that your favorite podcast looks better than ever. All controls have been carefully selected to offer the best playback experience. * 3D TOUCH - you can manage your subscriptions quick ‚Äòn easy and you can control playback through gestures. * CUSTOMIZABLE INTERFACE - An app for everyone. Set the interface you like most. Choose between light and dark theme, grid of 3x3 or 4x4, round or square covers, make your own UCast. And do not forget to share! * ADVANCED MANAGEMENT - All adjustments for the most demanding. With UCast you can manage your subscriptions, events, downloads, and control when everything is done is a Kids game. * STREAMING AND DOWNLOAD DIRECT - All your podcast anywhere under any circumstances. With UCast you can listen to your podcast via streaming or download to listen to offline at anytime, anywhere. * UPDATE AND BACKGROUND DOWNLOAD - Do not waste time with downloads. Schedule automatic updates to run in background and once when you open UCast your last episodes will be ready to play. * SLEEP TIMER - Stop the clocks with UCast. Set a timer to continue listening when you want. So you will not miss a single second of your favorite podcasts. * EPISODE SUPPORT - Browse quickly in between large episodes. UCast offers full support for audio chapters. So you can skip directly to the information you care about most. ## The future of UCast We are preparing many interesting new features for the application and this is not the end: * Custom playlists * Smart Lists * Synchronization between devices * App for Apple Watch * App for Android * Web App ## Price and Availability * UCast is available at launch for a discount price of ‚Ç¨ 1.99 during the first two weeks of release. * During the first days of release, Ucast will be available with a special discount of 50%. Take advantage of this special limited time. ## About UCast Team Juanjo Guevara - CEO & iOS Developer ¬∑ Twitter: @juanjoguevara Alvaro Bernal - Designer ¬∑ Twitter: @abn Fran Gallardo - Marketing ¬∑ Twitter: @fran__gallardo ## Contact Email: info@ucastapp.com Twitter: @ucastplayer', u'title': u'UCast - Podcast Player'}, {u'description': u'UCast is the best Podcast Player for iPhone & iPad', u'title': u'UCast - The Ultimate iOS Podcast Player'}]

tagline: Tinder for finding roommates
text_content:
[{u'body': u' Skip the classifieds and download the app that makes finding a roommate fun, safe and simple. 
 
Here‚Äôs how easy it is. You choose where you need a roommate and we show you potential roommates in the area. You‚Äôll be able to see the following information about each user. 
 
-profile picture
-name, age
-preferred neighborhoods
-mutual friends, mutual likes
-job, university
-about section that tells you more about what the other person wants*We do require you to login with your Facebook which makes your experience safer
 
Once you find somebody who is a possible fit as a roommate, just swipe right. If they also swipe right we‚Äôll connect you two with our in-app messaging. Simple enough, yah?The app is for anybody in need of a roommate, however, students in college trying to find off campus housing will be much more likely to have mutual friends when they are looking for a roommate. Our app is live in major markets like Seattle, Los Angeles, New York, Miami, Minneapolis, Phoenix, Chicago, San Diego, Las Vegas Boston, Houston, Dallas, Portland, Atlanta and San Francisco.  We are still growing our user base so certain markets have more people searching than others :)Whether you already have a room in your apartment that needs to be filled or are looking for people to rent a house you found, RentHoop can connect with you an awesome flatmate.   ', u'description': u'The most simple and fun way to find your next roommate', u'title': u'RentHoop - roommate finder - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': u'Skip the classifieds and download the app that makes finding a roommate fun, safe and simple. Your next roommate is only a swipe away. Here‚Äôs how easy it is. You choose where you need a roommate and we show you potential roommates in the area. You‚Äôll be able to see the following information about each user with Facebook login. -profile picture -name, age -preferred neighborhoods -mutual friends, mutual likes -job, university -about section that tells you more about what the other person wants Once you find somebody who is a possible fit as a roommate, just swipe right. If they also swipe right we‚Äôll connect you two with our in-app messaging. Simple enough? You shouldn't have to jump through a hoop to find a roommate. The app is for anybody in need of a roommate, however, students in college trying to rent off campus housing will be much more likely to have mutual friends when they are looking for a roommate. Our app is live in major markets like Seattle, Los Angeles, New York,, Phoenix, Chicago, Houston, Dallas, Portland, Atlanta and San Francisco. Whether you already have a room in your apartment that needs to be filled or are looking for people to rent a house you found, RentHoop can connect with you an awesome roomie.', u'title': u'RentHoop - Roommate Finder'}]

tagline: Custom swipe and GIF keyboard
text_content: [{u'description': u'*** Free for today only! *** BRIEFKEY is your fully customizable, all-in-one Swipe Keyboard with intelligent personalized prediction and auto-correct. All learning and processing occurs on your device only for privacy. Swipe in English, Spanish, and Russian with more languages coming. BRIEFKEY provides in-keyboard access to your calendars, contacts, and photos so that you never have to switch between apps again. GIFs, emoji, and stickers are all built in. You can even translate messages into 40 languages, search the Internet, make animated cartoons, and get directions to share without leaving your message! New GIF creator to make custom GIFs and looping videos. Select or take photos and video. Add custom text, apply filters, and adjust speed, then post or share your creation. ++++BRIEFKEYS++++ ‚Ä¢ Create your own BRIEFKEYS by assigning a custom icon to any frequently used text or action. BRIEFKEYS will then appear in the top of your keyboard. Create BRIEFKEYS for any text, including names, addresses, emails, URLs, phone numbers, signatures, directions. ‚Ä¢ Cartoon BRIEFKEY - choose one of the custom animated characters and add your own text. Current political characters include Bernie, Hillary, Trump, Obama, Johnson, Jong-un, and Putin. More to come very soon. Send requests. BRIEFKEY is used for political and social commentary and is not endorsed by any public figure included. ‚Ä¢ Translate BRIEFKEY - translate text to or from 40 languages right from your keyboard ‚Ä¢ Calendar BRIEFKEY - display your calendar in the keyboard, automatically insert calendar entries into messages and emails, and add new entries to your calendar. ‚Ä¢ Contact BRIEFKEY - display all of your contacts right in the keyboard and share contact information easily. ‚Ä¢ Photo BRIEFKEY - display your camera roll photos and attach multiple photos to emails and messages with one touch. ‚Ä¢ Location BRIEFKEY - share your current location with one touch. ‚Ä¢ Bing BRIEFKEY lets you search the Internet, insert links, and even view webpages right from your Keyboard. There are also Search Briefs for Images and Wikipedia. Check movie times without leaving your message and share with one touch. ‚Ä¢ Foursquare and Places BRIEFKEYS - search restaurants, stores, movies, museums, parks, and more from your keyboard and send addresses, links, and maps with one touch. ‚Ä¢ GIF BRIEFKEY lets you search for and share GIFs and Stickers in messages, Facebook posts, and across your favorite social media. ****Customize your own keyboard**** ‚Ä¢ Choose your favorite color, image, or GIF to customize your keyboard's background. Search millions of GIFs and save to your camera roll to create unique animated themes. ‚Ä¢ Animate your keys with effects including explosions, floating hearts, rolling dice, and falling snow! ‚Ä¢ Choose the size, shape, color, and font of your keys and text. ‚Ä¢ Personalize your space bar and all function keys with designer icons to fit any theme. Icon packs include sports, music, food, beer/wine/martini, animals, tech, science fiction, and many more. ‚Ä¢ Emojis are suggested as you type for easy access. ‚Ä¢ Swipe the space bar to move the text cursor like a touchpad. IMPORTANT: You will need to install BRIEFKEY just like any other keyboard. If you need help or something is not clear, please email us at support@briefkey.com. Please be aware that BRIEFKEY will require "Full Access" to access the Internet, display custom themes and perform certain other functions. We respect your privacy and do not ever read, collect or store what you type with our keyboard. In fact, you can still use BRIEFKEY to type without full access. Apple requires "Full Access" to be enabled for any third-party keyboard to access the Internet. For your security and peace of mind, whenever you enter passwords or sensitive information, like credit card numbers, in secure fields, the Apple system keyboard will automatically appear for you to use. App Preview Music: www.bensound.com', u'title': u'BriefKey ‚Äì Custom Swipe & GIF Keyboard'}, {u'description': None, u'title': u'BriefKey'}]

tagline: Equipment free, bodyweight strength training app
text_content:
[{u'body': u' Get set for a fitness revolution with mobiefit BODY. It is the most effective fitness training program, adapted to your schedule, your fitness level and your goals, whether it is weight loss, shedding calories, body-building, toning and shaping, or simply learning the right exercise techniques.  It features automatic rep counting, fitness tracking after each workout, ability to repeat your training for the day and a feature to perform next day's workouts. This s the only home fitness companion you need to lose weight, burn calories, build muscle, boost your health and get your body in shape! mobiefit BODY gets you working out with fitness icons ‚Äì Anoop Singh and Bani J ‚Äì who act as the chief motivators and exercise companions within the app, with free HD fitness videos for upper body, lower body or core strengthening exercises. This personal trainer automatically counts your reps and gives you a customized body-weight exercise routine that‚Äôs ideal for your fitness level. ‚ñ∫‚ñ∫Train with Mr World‚óÑ‚óÑ
With a Mr World 2015 title under his belt, actor and pilot, Anoop Singh gives you all the right diet and fitness tips. His unique workout style showcases his incredible flexibility, body-building expertise and a world-class physique. ‚ñ∫‚ñ∫Work out with TV Icon‚óÑ‚óÑ
Bani J (MTV Roadies alumni) is one of India‚Äôs most loved TV personalities. She brings a unique sense of style to all your workouts with her focus on flexibility, nutrition, and shaping and toning! ‚ñ∫‚ñ∫No equipment or gym needed‚óÑ‚óÑ
Start working out anywhere, anytime. With mobiefit BODY, there‚Äôs no need for any expensive training equipment. Don‚Äôt incur any extra gym costs as you can exercise at home, in the park or in the open! ‚ñ∫‚ñ∫Customized training plan‚óÑ‚óÑ
Not everyone can do 50 squats, pushups or crunches from the start! So mobiefit BODY sets a Benchmark Test to know your fitness level and gives you a customized workout routine based on your ability.‚ñ∫‚ñ∫Automatic rep counts‚óÑ‚óÑ
Thanks to modern sensor technology, the mobiefit BODY fitness app automatically tracks all your workouts by counting reps and sets for pushups, crunches and squats. ‚ñ∫‚ñ∫Quick Workouts‚óÑ‚óÑ
Don‚Äôt want to enter a training program or don't even have time for 7-minute workouts? Quickly choose from Upper Body, Core and Lower Body exercises to finish your workout in under 5 minutes. ‚ñ∫‚ñ∫Workout diary‚óÑ‚óÑ
Tracking your workouts is easy with our dashboard. Keep a tab on your exercise history and map your progress. ‚ñ∫‚ñ∫Videos and tips‚óÑ‚óÑ
100+ in-app videos from our celebrity coaches Anoop and Bani at no extra cost! Our companions show you how to perform any workout with minimal risk of injuries, helping you make the most of your training. Coming soon:
‚ñ∫Champions & Versus Mode
‚ñ∫Book My Coach ProgramUnlike other fitness apps mobiefit BODY is not just about telling you which workout to choose; we take it a step beyond by guiding you on each and every aspect of your fitness from tracking to fitness tips. Exercise not only boosts your body but also charges up your mind, allowing you to tackle any challenge. Your body and mind will both be thankful for this personal trainer. Burn calories, lose weight, gain energy to keep going and watch as your confidence grows. This is your best chance to unleash your full potential. Get in touch with us at body@mobiefit.com. For any technical queries or app-related problems, drop a line to support@mobiefit.com, and share your experience, feedback and suggestions with feedback@mobiefit.comDon‚Äôt forget to leave a review after installing the app. Follow ‚Äòmobiefit‚Äô on Facebook, Twitter, Google+ and Instagram to keep up with all the latest features, contests, updates and challenges from all our apps! Visit mobiefit.com  for more information   ', u'description': u'Bodyweight-based workouts with fitness icons with no need for equipment or gym', u'title': u'mobiefit BODY Home Workouts - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': u'Get fitter with our apps - mobiefit RUN, mobiefit WALK and mobiefit BODY - and mobiefit's training programs', u'title': u'mobiefit - Running app, walking training and workout motivation'}]

tagline: The web browser for your Apple Watch
text_content: [{u'description': u'Brand New Features: -WatchWeb has bookmark support WatchWeb is THE essential application for anyone with an Apple Watch. Use it to look up information, sports scores, and anything else Siri can't do for you! Browse the web on the most and best rated Apple Watch Web Browser! Please Note: WatchWeb does not display "full" versions of websites. Also, please update your watch to the latest possible version before trying to install WatchWeb to prevent possible problems. WatchWeb is an innovative web browser designed specifically for use on the Apple Watch. WatchWeb presents you with pages run through a top-of-the-line optimization algorithm that automatically formats content for best viewing on the Apple Watch. Rather than having to rely solely on Siri‚Äôs limited capabilities for obtaining information, you now have access to the whole indexed internet directly from your watch. WatchWeb makes it effortless to look up information, read news, or just surf the web. Simply enter a search using either dictation or our built-in character list and get started! We think you'll find it quite useful! Here's what people are saying about WatchWeb: "Should you need to look up some information that Siri cannot given her regional restrictions, or check sports scores for your local teams, or maybe even read some headlines to kill a few seconds of your time, you should take WatchWeb for a spin." -iDownloadBlog "I will be using WatchWeb from now on" -Technos Amigos "Stupendously Useful" -MarcianoPhone', u'title': u'WatchWeb - The Web Browser for your Apple Watch'}]

tagline: Turn your boring run into an epic adventure
text_content: [{u'description': u'Transform your ordinary walk, jog or run into an epic adventure and feel like a hero battling orcs, goblins and dragons! Get heroic level fitness where calories burned equals gold earned‚Ä¶ Fit for Battle is an interactive audio based running app where you are the hero at the centre of an epic fantasy adventure. Each run is turned into a quest where your performance directly influences the direction of the story. Your buddies Kia the elf and Keg the dwarf describe the world around you and let you know when to speed up and slow down. The driving cinematic music and effects will get moving from zero to hero! THE ULTIMATE MOTIVATOR Look forward to your next run! The story keeps you entertained and you forget you are working out. Earn amazing gear to armour up your character by turning calories burned into gold earned! Unlock stacks of achievements to earn surprise rewards. You can even challenge your mates to see who is the fittest of them all‚Ä¶ ATTACK & FLEE Speed up to attack monsters, smash down doors and escape dragons! Be careful though as you can lose lives when monsters hit you back! Your decisions change which path you take and random encounters make each run different from the last. HEALTH & FITNESS Fit for Battle rewards exercise and is suitable for all levels of fitness. It is easy for anybody to pick up and play, walk, jog or run it. It syncs with Apple‚Äôs Health kit to give you a personalised experience. You can run outdoors or indoors and set your difficulty and duration. EPIC ADVENTURE Welcome to the world of Athletica, where the fast earn glory, and the slow die painful deaths. You are a fresh recruit, a former king‚Äôs errand runner who has been called up to solve a mystery. What is uncovered will rock the foundations of the world. Will you be quick enough to overcome this evil threat? You are joined by Shia the elf, Keg the hot headed dwarf and a whole cast of characters that will share in your adventure. They are your adventuring party and provide all the story and game cues so you are part of the action. Each character has their own story and agenda. Who is trustworthy? And which one will steer you good or bad? Follow the mysterious story to a thrilling final showdown‚Ä¶ Note: This app is best experienced on iphone5S or greater. iPhone 4S and iPhone 5/5C is best used outdoors only iPhone 4 and older are unsupported at this time.', u'title': u'Fit for Battle'}]

tagline: The app for lifters üí™
text_content: [{u'description': u'* Log your workouts, track your progress, improve your form, hit PRs * Lift with your friends, motivate each other and share tips * Compete on any exercise, with your friends and the entire community Gravitus is the app for lifters. Track your workouts easily and efficiently with a UI designed to minimize tapping and maximize lifting. Add friends so you have lifting buddies to motivate you whether they‚Äôre in the same city or across the country. Compete with your friends on the leaderboards on any exercise, from who can do the most crunches to who has the strongest squat or the heaviest bench press. For those of us who enjoy hitting the gym, Gravitus makes it even better! Whether you're a bodybuilder, powerlifter, or you just enjoy weightlifting, Gravitus is packed with features to help you get fit and stay strong: * Blazingly fast, beautiful and simple to use * Log a new workout or repeat a previous one, we'll help you remember what you lifted last time * On a routine? Plan workouts ahead of time with our workout templates feature * Setup your training maxes and automatically compute weight goals based on a percentage of your training max * Interact with your friends and other lifters, fist bump them for a good workout and leave comments for extra motivation * Discover new exercise and master your form with exercise videos and tips * Every exercise has a leaderboard, see how you measure up against your friends and the Gravitus community * Built in one rep max calculations let you compare your strength potential across workout styles * Can't find an exercise you're looking for? Add it to our database within the app! * No more backups. Whether you share your workouts with others or keep them private, your data is safe with us. Continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life.', u'title': u'Gravitus - Workout Tracker and Strength Training Log'}]

tagline: See interesting things other people are up to
text_content:
[{u'description': u'*** Featured App by React Native *** Next time you‚Äôre bored and not sure of what to do in your free time, open Helium to see interesting things other people are up to. From suggestions about restaurants, bars, places of interests (heritage sites, museums, art galleries, etc.) to interesting events and travel memories, you‚Äôll find it on all Helium. There was a time when people tried something new based on suggestions from people like them and not reviews collected from unknown people. At Helium we believe the best recommendations come from people like you and we have built an experience around this belief. Features - See what people like you are doing in their free time and let their recommendations help you out of boring times. - Share anything interesting or cool you've been up to recently. - Filter recommendations by location so you easily discover the most interesting places around you. - Follow the city you call home or your next travel destination and let the locals be your guide. - And with every interaction, we'll tailor the recommendations to make sure you see what you‚Äôll like. tagline: Motorcycle safety App for iPhone and iPad.
text_content: [{u'description': u'GoRide is a motorcycle safety app to detect falls and accidents. The app uses the iPhones built in sensors to analyse and detect if you have fallen. If the app detects a fall, it will begin a 20 second countdown before sounding an alarm and sending a notification to your chosen saviours. They will then be sent your current location and phone number so they can contact and find you quickly to make sure you are safe. Your location is only shared if you have fallen and is only available to the people that you choose. The app does not track or upload your location unless it detects a fall. The app requires an Internet connection to upload the user's location in the case of a fall. The phone must be mounted vertically in portrait on the handlebars of the bike to ensure the most accurate results for detecting falls. Please read and accept the Disclaimer in the app before using the Buddy feature. The new Buddy feature is available on iPhone and the saviour feature can be used on both iPhone and iPad.', u'title': u'GoRide'}, {u'description': None, u'title': u'GoRide'}]

tagline: Publish tweetstorms on the go
text_content:
[{u'body': u' Storm it is simple app that allows you to add or collect your ideas / thoughts and share them as a Tweetstorm on Twitter.The term "Tweetstorm" (not Tweet Storm) was coined and made famous by entrepreneur, investor - Marc Andreessen. It‚Äôs a series of tweets from one person that starts with a number and a slash. Those numbers mean that this is the first Tweet of a longer thought, followed by the second, and sometimes third and fourth.This series of posts, known as a Tweetstorm, is a way to share thoughts and comments that are too long for the 140 character limit.Features
- Collect all your thoughts / ideas and tweet storms in one place
- Storm your ideas on Twitter maintaining the response chain
- Automatically add the count to your tweetstorm - 1/N or 1/
- All ideas are stored as drafts (forecasted) and editable if they aren‚Äôt tweetstormed yetA tweetstorm helps to keep the chain of thought in the twitter timeline itself, but be conscious of your readers. Bombarding the timeline with too much content might be irritating for some. You don‚Äôt want to be blocked or muted forever do you?Do share your your feedback, comments and suggestions at support@nfnlabs.in or connect with us on twitter @nfnlabs   ', u'description': u'Collect your ideas / thoughts and share them as a Tweetstorm on Twitter.', u'title': u'Storm it - Android Apps on Google Play'}]

tagline: Uses your genetics & smartphone to help extend your life.
text_content: [{u'description': u'Rthm is the AI that uses your genetics and smartphone to help you extend your life. It works by combining the biosensors in your phone, used to monitor your breathing, heart rate, sleep, and activity, with your unique genetic profile to generate life improving recommendations aimed at life extension. It is the only mobile app capable of monitoring your heart rate and breathing rate through clothes, allowing it to track your cardiovascular health over time, guide your meditation, and remove the question of ‚Äúis this exercise and meditation really working?‚Äù Though it works without a genetic test, signing up for the DeepRthm genetic analysis allows the AI to use your DNA and the length of your Telomeres (molecular markers of stress and aging) to curate your precise nutritional, exercise, and behavioural needs, and deliver the results directly to your app. Get Motivated. -Set your daily goals for steps, active time, meditation time, and sleep duration. Rthm monitors your progress towards these goals using a fun and intuitive user interface. Get Heart Rate in 6 seconds. -Simply hold the phone flat on your chest and wait until you feel a vibration. -If you are exercising and your heart rate is elevated select exercise mode before placing on chest for an accurate reading. -Improve your heart health by tracking your resting heart rate and overall fitness. Get Active. -Rthm uses Health Kit to track your activity trends, steps, distance, calories. Get Mindful in 2 minutes. -Easy meditation anywhere with real-time feedback from your breathing and heart patterns. Choose a meditation time, hold your phone still, and breathe with the visual guide. The phone will vibrate when your meditation has completed. You will receive a summary of how your heart rate changed through the meditation. Get Rested. Rthm tracks your sleep times automatically and maps your circadian rhythm to provide recommendations on how you can improve your sleep. Get DeepRthm. -Opt for DeepRthm Genetic Analysis and receive a DNA collection kit used to sequence your genes and telomere length. -Receive genetic based health recommendations for a longer life. Get Smart Tips. -Rthm discovers insights and provides tips on what you can do to improve your well-being Get Rthm.', u'title': u'Rthm - The Life Extension App'}]

tagline: On-demand, location-based live streaming
text_content: [{u'description': u'StreamLi. Live Streaming Marketplace, allows users to easily create requests for live streaming from any location in the world, hire local broadcasters and get exclusive live video content. We want to empower users to explore the World in new way, their way, and see places and events in real time. The StreamLi's app allows users to both get live streams of whatever they want from any location in the world and also provide live streams for others. Broadcast can be payed with money or Reward points( users can earn points by providing service for other members). Through Explore feature of the App users will be able to browse locations and see recommendations for attractions, events etc. at each of the places. In its simplest form it is a three stage process: 1) Create a Request: Enter the location and description (What you want to see), choose the length of the live stream you require and submit request. Notification is sent to local broadcasters who can accept request. 2) Hire the local ‚ÄúBroadcaster‚Äù/Videographer. After broadcaster accept request , click on Hire and make payment ( with either Rewards Points or In-App-Purchase). 3) Watch the Live Stream that you have commissioned: Request the start of the stream and the ‚ÄúBroadcaster‚Äù will start the live stream. During the Live Stream you can direct the ‚ÄúBroadcaster‚Äù by typing your comments in the chat window. Continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life.', u'title': u'StreamLi - Live Stream By Request'}]

tagline: Read later app with improved notes, message and save
text_content:
[{u'body': u' Basketapp lets you save and organize articles, videos and any other useful links in a beautiful and simple way to increase your web productivity, even when you are offline.Categorize and apply labels on news, research findings and recipes you save to find them quickly. Capability to read your articles later in a clutter free environment, makes it perfect companion for you while travelling, sitting in leisure or while sipping morning coffee.MAIN FEATURES:- Easily access your items category wise.
- Share an item with your friends and colleagues.
- Save data with 'wi-fi only syncing' while in data plan.
- Get an eye soothing reading experience with suitable reading modes.
- Find items in one go with link types (article, video, document) or label you set or traditional search.
- Save items in Basket from your favorite apps like Flipboard, Feedly, Google Newsstand or from browser via share.
- Every article will be downloaded to make available **OFFLINE**, so you can read them anytime you want, away from internet connections.To help you get started:
- Easily import your bookmarks from your browser and services such as Pocket, Instapaper and Delicious**Help us to translate Basket - http://translate.basketapp.net-----------------------------------------------------------------1. You can also add and enjoy bookmarks in your basket from our really awesome Google chrome extension and web dashboard. Visit  https://www.basketapp.net/apps/chrome to know more.2. For other platforms: https://www.basketapp.net/apps/3. Visit us at: https://www.basketapp.net4. email us at connect@basketapp.net and let us know how we can improve and help you in better way.   ', u'description': u'Save articles, assign notes and read later, even offline anytime anywhere.', u'title': u'Basket - Bookmark & Read Later - Android Apps on Google Play'}]

tagline: Top articles for your professional skills
text_content: [{u'description': u'Mybridge is a free app that makes your professional life simpler. Pick your skills in tech and let Mybridge do all the work of searching and collecting articles for you to read daily. ‚Ä¢ Top 10 articles: There are many terribly written articles out there. Mybridge AI ranks top articles every day, filtering out the poor quality content for you. ‚Ä¢ Collections: Mybridge AI puts together related articles, tools and tutorials to help you learn quickly and improve your work (e.g. JavaScript open source projects, design style guides, growth case studies of billion dollar companies) ‚Ä¢ Personalized feed: Mybridge AI gets smarter as you read more, producing a richer content feed, personalized to your skills and reading patterns. WHO IS THIS FOR? Programmers and designers use this app to learn more about web design, web development and software engineering. Entrepreneurs and marketing professionals use it to learn the latest on acquiring customers and building the next great company. See below for available skills and interests. Programming - HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, ES6, NodeJS, AngularJS, ReactJS, Swift, Python, Java, PHP, Ruby on Rails, Machine Learning, Mongo DB, MySQL. Design - User Experience (UX) Design, User Interface (UI) Design, User Research, Usability Testing, Prototyping, Wireframing, Photoshop, Sketch 3, Animation Design. Business - Entrepreneurship, Tech News, Leadership, Building a Startup, Product Management, Raising Funding, Pitching to Investors. Marketing - Growth Hacking, Search Engine Optimization (SEO), Social Marketing, Online Advertising, Content Marketing, Analytics, Email Marketing, App Marketing & App Store Optimization (ASO), Conversion Optimization, Customer Retention.', u'title': u'Mybridge: Read top articles for your professional skills'}]

text_content:
[{u'description': u'BitTorrent Now is the best place to experience music and video from the underground artists you don‚Äôt know about yet. Find your favourites and filter them according to your needs depending on size and/or price range. Depending on where you want to put the art piece and what you want to spend on it, you can filter and search your favourites up to the point you are absolutely sure that it is a best fit. Buy the ones you love as soon as you have found it and want to be the first and only one to possess this unique piece of art. tagline: Understand legislation in Congress and contact lawmakers
text_content: [{u'description': u'**Featured on MSNBC, the Today Show, The NYTimes, Wired, Politico and the iTunes App Store Countable makes learning about what your government is up to easy and fun. Learn about issues you care about, influence Congress with one tap voting, and rally your friends around specific legislation. SEND VIDEO MESSAGES TO YOUR REPS - Use the camera on your iPhone/iPad to record video messages - Send them to your elected reps and break through the noise - Tell your story in your own voice and be heard! MAKE UP YOUR OWN MIND - Daily notifications about upcoming votes - Short non-partisan summaries of legislation - Unbiased arguments for and against HOLD YOUR REPS ACCOUNTABLE - See how your votes align with your lawmakers - Post an opinion or vote and we‚Äôll inform your lawmakers - Don‚Äôt be surprised if you receive a message back COMMUNITY - See what other people are saying about the issues you care about - Upvote their opinions and show your support - Post principled arguments and help change people‚Äôs minds ------- Accolades: - ‚ÄúSlick, easy to use and could definitely help inform your opinions.‚Äù - New York Times - ‚ÄúTelling your senator how to vote is as easy and ‚Äòliking‚Äô a Facebook picture.‚Äù -Tech Crunch What our users say: - ‚ÄúFast, easy way to interact with Congress.‚Äù - ‚ÄúMakes it easy to stay informed with D.C. and ultimately let's my voice be heard.‚Äù - ‚ÄúAn easy way to keep track of bills in congress and give feedback to my senators and representatives!‚Äù We love feedback! Email us at support@countable.com Follow us at @Countable, facebook.com/countable.us, and plus.google.com/+CountableUs/posts About Countable: Countable was created by a team of dedicated Americans based in San Francisco and Washington DC. We believe that using technology properly we can make American democracy work in a fashion similar to what our founders envisioned. Our advisory team includes former Senator Evan Bayh, Joe Trippi, who ran Howard Dean‚Äôs revolutionary presidential campaign in 2004.', u'title': u'Countable - Contact Congress and Vote on Bills'}]

tagline: Fast and powerful .NET C# and F# IDE for iOS
text_content: [{u'description': u'Continuous is a fast and powerful .NET C# and F# IDE that runs directly on the iPad and iPhone (no network needed!). With it, you can write apps and games using your favorite languages on your favorite devices. Continuous is always building and running your code so you can see changes as you type. Writing interactive apps in Continuous is a pleasure compared to the traditional code-build-run cycle. It frees you to make lots of small changes and see their effects immediately - no more waiting for builds or deployments and no more clicking around trying to get to the screen you're trying to code. Continuous looks and works in many of the same ways as traditional .NET IDEs so you'll feel right at home, but it also strives to advance the state of the art in IDEs with these features: >>> Full C# 6 and F# 4 compilers so you can use the latest tech >>> Automatic compiling and running so you can focus on the code and the results >>> Fancy text editor with tabs, semantic highlighting, inline error bubbles, and inline values that are updated as you type >>> Watch window enables you to view graphical objects in your app (UI and images), inspect live objects as your app runs, create instances of new objects, and call methods >>> Code completion with inline type info and documentation makes learning new APIs fun >>> Uses standard .NET file and project formats so you can share code with other IDEs >>> Includes Xamarin.Forms and UIKit to build apps and SpriteKit and SceneKit to build games >>> Split screen support so you can keep documentation by your side >>> Execution powered by a new IL interpreter If you're new to .NET or iOS coding, you will love the code completion with integrated documentation and the fun examples that come with the app. If you're a .NET pro, then you will love the support for projects and the ability to inspect objects as you code them - whether they're in a script or just a normal project file. If you're new to programming, C# is an great language to learn: it's powerful yet friendly language, example code is all over the internet, and there are plenty of jobs out there waiting for you. If you enjoy thinking a little differently, then you will love that F# is included and fully supported. This amazing programming language will teach you to write better code and will arm you to solve problems that you thought were too big or hard to solve - like writing an IDE.', u'title': u'Continuous .NET C# and F# IDE'}, {u'description': u'Continuous - C# and F# IDE for the iPad Over the past six months I have been working on a new .NET IDE for the iPad, and today I am very pleased to release it on the App Store. Continuous gives you...', u'title': u'pr√¶clarum - Continuous - C# and F# IDE for the iPad'}]

tagline: Relive your Snapchat Stories
text_content: [{u'description': u'ellie lets you relive your Snapchat Stories. Once you download ellie we begin storing your stories so that you can re-watch them whenever, forever. We have also made it possible to share your stories quickly and easily with your friends. And for the times when you want to share more than a Snapchat story, we have an in-app camera that lets you create whole new stories within ellie. Best of all, ellie is totally free :) Hope you love it! If you have any questions email jacob@tryellie.com', u'title': u'ellie by SnapMemories'}]

tagline: Tiny bluetooth sensors that influence healthy habits
text_content:
[{u'body': u' WHAT IS PROJECT MOVEThis app is a companion to MOVE hotspots (www.habithotspots.com)- an exciting interactive workplace wellness technology installation that you can get for your entire office - or even just for your team. MOVE hotspots help your organization or team impact one simple but powerful wellness goal - break sedentary work habits that are harmful to your health, and take healthy breaks through the course of a busy day at work.MOVE gives you a reason to get up and move more throughout your workday - and reinforces this behavior over time - leading to beneficial habit formation.To deploy Project MOVE - You‚Äôll need to go to www.quantifiedhabits.com/move and purchase a set of MOVE hotspots - smart indoor location sensors. Once you have installed these hotspots at your workplace, email all users a link to download this companion Project MOVE app, and an access code to register. Alternately users can download and register the MOVE app all by just visiting a MOVE hotspot and following the printed instructions on it.WHO IS IT FOR?
Project MOVE is ideal for small businesses and teams that are looking for an easy to deploy worksite wellness installation that practically runs itself and doesn‚Äôt require elaborate roll-out announcements,  or handing out fitness trackers or buying expensive treadmill desks for your employees/ team.WHAT YOU CAN DO WITH PROJECT MOVETransform your workplace into an interactive wellness installation 
--------------------------------------Make your environment come alive with our MOVE hotspots - turning communal areas such as water coolers, copy rooms, cafeteria and rec rooms into "activity checkpoints" that credit you for periodically getting up and visiting them. For example - you could deploy a MOVE hotspot in the stairwells of your office to nudge and reward users to take the stairs. Or consider placing our MOVE hotspot in the hallway and motivate users to take the longer route to their desks after they take a lunch break.The possibilities for deploying Project MOVE in fun, creative ways are only limited by your imagination! Deploy customized wellness messaging
--------------------------------------
Whether it is motivational reminders or funny taunts to get users to move, or informative and educational content, or mini-challenges to pique their curiosity, appeal to their sense of purpose or pride ‚Äì MOVE has it all! You can use our pre-existing content, or even add your own by writing to us.Run custom wellness contests
--------------------------------------
MOVE is a great platform for running wellness challenges. You can sponsor prizes for your team or others in your organization to motivate them to move more, pick and announce winners, validate winnings - all through Project MOVE.ON THE IMPORTANCE OF BREAKING SEDENTARY WORK HABITS Research continues to show that excessive sitting may contribute to chronic disease, worsen your quality of life and even shorten your lifespan. Over a busy stressful workday, we also take very few breaks. Yet when we think of health and wellness - we tend to equate it to counting steps or hitting the gym or getting our morning or evening cardio.But what about the little things? More and more research is pointing to the importance of just moving that extra bit more throughout the day. What‚Äôs even more interesting is that when researchers studied communities where some of the longest-lived people in the world can be found - they found three things in common: Create an environment that encourages physical activity, avoid overeating, and cultivate a sense of purpose.Project MOVE is inspired by this notion ‚Äì and wants to help you transform your living environment in ways that subtly nudge and motivate you into light physical activity, and taking more frequent healthy breaks.Tell your HR/Wellness Coordinator/ Manager about Project MOVE today. Come be a part of a wellness revolution!Find us on twitter: @QHabits   ', u'description': u'Next Generation Wellness Technology to help you break sedentary work habits.', u'title': u'Project MOVE - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': u'WHAT IS PROJECT MOVE This app is a companion to MOVE hotspots (www.habithotspots.com)- an exciting interactive workplace wellness technology installation that you can get for your entire office - or even just for your team. MOVE hotspots help your organization or team impact one simple but powerful wellness goal - break sedentary work habits that are harmful to your health, and take healthy breaks through the course of a busy day at work. MOVE gives you a reason to get up and move more throughout your workday - and reinforces this behavior over time - leading to beneficial habit formation. To deploy Project MOVE - You‚Äôll need to go to http://www.habithotspots.com and purchase a set of MOVE hotspots - smart indoor location sensors. Once you have installed these hotspots at your workplace, email all users a link to download this companion Project MOVE app, and an access code to register. Alternately users can download and register the MOVE app all by just visiting a MOVE hotspot and following the printed instructions on it. WHO IS IT FOR? Project MOVE is ideal for small businesses and teams that are looking for an easy to deploy worksite wellness installation that practically runs itself and doesn‚Äôt require elaborate roll-out announcements, or handing out fitness trackers or buying expensive treadmill desks for your employees/ team. WHAT YOU CAN DO WITH PROJECT MOVE Transform your workplace into an interactive wellness installation -------------------------------------- Make your environment come alive with our MOVE hotspots - turning communal areas such as water coolers, copy rooms, cafeteria and rec rooms into "activity checkpoints" that credit you for periodically getting up and visiting them. For example - you could deploy a MOVE hotspot in the stairwells of your office to nudge and reward users to take the stairs. Or consider placing our MOVE hotspot in the hallway and motivate users to take the longer route to their desks after they take a lunch break. The possibilities for deploying Project MOVE in fun, creative ways are only limited by your imagination! Deploy customized wellness messaging -------------------------------------- Whether it is motivational reminders or funny taunts to get users to move, or informative and educational content, or mini-challenges to pique their curiosity, appeal to their sense of purpose or pride ‚Äì MOVE has it all! You can use our pre-existing content, or even add your own by writing to us. Run custom wellness contests -------------------------------------- MOVE is a great platform for running wellness challenges. You can sponsor prizes for your team or others in your organization to motivate them to move more, pick and announce winners, validate winnings - all through Project MOVE. ON THE IMPORTANCE OF BREAKING SEDENTARY WORK HABITS Research continues to show that excessive sitting may contribute to chronic disease, worsen your quality of life and even shorten your lifespan. Over a busy stressful workday, we also take very few breaks. Yet when we think of health and wellness - we tend to equate it to counting steps or hitting the gym or getting our morning or evening cardio. But what about the little things? More and more research is pointing to the importance of just moving that extra bit more throughout the day. What‚Äôs even more interesting is that when researchers studied communities where some of the longest-lived people in the world can be found - they found three things in common: Create an environment that encourages physical activity, avoid overeating, and cultivate a sense of purpose. Project MOVE is inspired by this notion ‚Äì and wants to help you transform your living environment in ways that subtly nudge and motivate you into light physical activity, and taking more frequent healthy breaks. Tell your HR/Wellness Coordinator/ Manager about Project MOVE today. Come be a part of a wellness revolution! Find us on twitter: @QHabits', u'title': u'Project MOVE - Wellness Technology to help you break sedentary work habits'}]

tagline: Family & friends scheduler
text_content: [{u'description': u'"A brilliant app to have - highly recommend!‚Ä¶" 5 03-Mar-2016 Such a great app to have - I would not be without it now! We can now all easily see who is doing what and when they are doing it without one of us only having the details on the family calendar in the kitchen, and the other just guessing!! "Mum's best friend‚Ä¶" 5 03-Mar-2016 Fantastic app - easy to use, everyone knows where they are supposed to be and when and the control freak in me can keep an eye on them all! "Fab app for knowing who is doing what in the family‚Ä¶" 5 03-Mar-2016 This is a fabulous app for keeping track of family activities & life - no more need to ensure you have told hubby a 100 times what the plan is everyday as this app holds all the info in one place! Droppa may look like any other calendaring app but it works entirely differently. Droppa is like no other scheduler/ calendar system. Droppa communicates just like texting. Droppa helps you to keep in contact and informed about what all your family and friends are doing and helps you keep everyone "in the loop!" Do you have problems organizing your family activities or find it hard to arrange dates with friends? Do you keep a family calendar hanging up at home but no one seems to take any notice of it other than you? Then you need Droppa! Droppa is a fantastic new way of interacting with your family and close friends and informing them via push notification rather than all other calendars/organizers which rely on email. Users all around the world are finding that Droppa makes family and friends organisation so much easier Keep all you family and friends in touch with Droppa. Let your husband, wife, partner, children, parents, best friends, colleagues, or club members, in fact anyone, keep informed with push notifications from Droppa. Droppa means that the family calendar is with you at all times and everyone can send you, or you can send them, drops inviting you to events or just keeping you up to date with what‚Äôs going on. Social gatherings, meeting up with friends, kid‚Äôs activities, work occasions, medical appointments, anything ‚Äì it‚Äôs all in Droppa! Droppa is an easy scheduler that lets you organize, invite or just inform your phone‚Äôs contacts of events or activities. Droppa is smartphone based and lets your contacts ‚Äúdrop‚Äù events into your schedule or, conversely, lets you ‚ÄúDrop‚Äù events into your contacts' schedules. And because only the phone‚Äôs contacts can drop then it‚Äôs safer for children to use aswell. All users will be able to group their contacts into social groups such as family, friends, colleagues, clubs etc. All users will be able to send ‚ÄúDrops‚Äù instantaneously and inform contacts by push notification. The ‚ÄúDrops‚Äù will contain details of activities or events which, upon acceptance, will automatically enter their contact‚Äôs calendars forming a viewable daily/weekly/monthly schedule. The user will therefore be kept informed about activities they need or wish to be aware of. Users will also be able to ‚Äúshare‚Äù drops thereby keeping other users informed about activities. Each ‚ÄúDrop‚Äù becomes its own chat-room allowing attendees to discuss and chat about the event. WHY USE DROPPA: ‚Ä¢ AS EASY AS SMS: organize your family and social calendar as easy as SMS. It‚Äôs on your phone and therefore with you at all times. ‚Ä¢ SECURITY: As Droppa only allows your phone‚Äôs contacts to drop with you, or you with them, Droppa is safer for children to use. ‚Ä¢ ALERTS: on receiving a drop Droppa will send you an alert informing you that a drop has been received. ‚Ä¢ NO EMAIL ADDRESSES NEEDED: because Droppa operates via push notifications you don‚Äôt need all your contacts‚Äô email addresses to send ‚ÄúDrops‚Äù. (User‚Äôs email address is required to register and to log in). ‚Ä¢ NOTIFY: if you receive a ‚ÄúDrop‚Äù informing you of an event or activity and you think others need to know about that event, whether on an involved or just a "need to know" basis, then Droppa can forward or ‚ÄúNotify‚Äù to the relevant contacts', u'title': u'Droppa'}]

tagline: Vector graphics editor. Fast and intuitive.
text_content:
[{u'body': u' Inker is a vector graphics editor designed to simplify sketch inking, logotype, comics, tribal or any other digital drawing. Images created with Inker can be exported to SVG and EPS and used anywhere in the web or imported into popular desktop graphics editors for creating AI or CDR files.
You are recommended to use a stylus and a tablet with screen size comfortable for drawing (at least 7''). If you feel uncomfortable with your device, try the desktop app version.Dear MIUI (Xiaomi) users, your OS has some problems with saving files. Go to Settings - Installed apps - Documents - Enable.   ', u'description': u'Vector graphics editor', u'title': u'Inker - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': None, u'title': u'Inker - Chrome Web Store'}]

tagline: Organic fundraising discovery, connecting angels & founders
text_content: [{u'description': u'Unicorn is a fundraising discovery tool connecting angel investors and early-stage tech start-ups through data, design, and functionality. Founders are required to fill out basic information accompanied by a recorded 15-second elevator pitch. Angel investors are required to provide a brief bio as well as a list of their top-three portfolio companies. The sign-up process can be as quick as one minute. If you're interested in connecting, you swipe right. Otherwise, you swipe left and move on. Start-ups beware! You only have five swipe-right requests per 24-hour window. After two people mutually opt in by swiping right, they're added to each other's connections. Start-ups are then encouraged to make the introduction and extend the dialogue. The fundraising discovery process is exhausting. We decided to make it quick, painless, but most of all...fun!', u'title': u'The Unicorn App'}, {u'description': u'', u'title': u'The Unicorn App'}]
