text_content: [{u'description': u'YEAY is a revolutionary e-commerce experience that redefines what it means to buy and sell on a mobile device. With full-screen vertical video only, users are able to create and consume diverse content in its most current, concise and enjoyable format. Sell it your way - on YEAY!!! Here‚Äôs what makes YEAY special: VIDEO ONLY: YEAY is a platform that just presents videos - because selling through photos is done! BROWSE EASY: Full-screen vertical video content for a more ergonomic, honest & entertaining experience. SIMPLE UX: Navigate through your feed using a simple swipe. LIVE SALES: Purchase items LIVE with one simple click. MAKE IT YOURS: Follow your favourite brands, sellers or people to stay up to date with all that you love. GO GLOBAL: Create sales videos that will be seen by millions of users across the world to maximise your reach!', u'title': u'YEAY'}]

tagline: Airbnb for beauty professionals. Rent salon space whenever.
text_content:
[{u'body': u' For cosmetologists:
Download the ShearShare Android App and start servicing your clients whenever wherever with a few simple taps.With ShearShare, you can
‚Ä¢ Book professional salon suites and find booths for rent directly from your Android phone
‚Ä¢ Service all your clients in 1-2-3 days instead of spacing out your schedule over an entire week
‚Ä¢ Make the career transition to cosmetology less painful by leasing salon space on a per-day basis
‚Ä¢ Build your book of business the day you graduate from beauty school! Pay a day rate versus weekly booth rent
‚Ä¢ Continue to service your clients that relocate by leasing space in their zip code
‚Ä¢ Before you move north/south/east/west, try out a mini salon suite in the area first
‚Ä¢ Married to a military serviceman or servicewoman? Now you can work wherever, whenever and have a schedule as flex as theirs
‚Ä¢ Experience different world cultures by selecting a new work location every month
‚Ä¢ Service your destination wedding clients in a clean, professional, friendly salon environment
‚Ä¢ Access your itineraries, view pictures of available salons, and get directions to your listingWelcome to the next generation of the beauty business!----------------------
For salon owners:
Download the ShearShare Android App to manage your temporary salon listings and connect with cosmetologists the world over.With ShearShare, you can
‚Ä¢ List your salon space and manage your listings directly from your Android phone
‚Ä¢ Fill your unused salon suites, barber stations, and booths on a temporary basis
‚Ä¢ Feel confident in hosting temporary stylists, as each user is a confirmed licensed cosmetologist
‚Ä¢ Lease your excess inventory for a time that's convenient for you
‚Ä¢ Make the same amount of money on your salon space in 1-2 days versus what it normally takes a week to generate
‚Ä¢ Enjoy a secondary stream of income by hosting traveling stylists
‚Ä¢ Accept or decline cosmetologists on the go
‚Ä¢ Update your salon calendar availability with ease
‚Ä¢ Manage your inquiries and update salon rules and pictures right from your Android phoneWelcome to the next generation of salon management!Join our beta community to provide feedback, and gain early access to new features: http://www.shearshare.com/get-the-app/Still reading? Download the ShearShare App now!Yes, we‚Äôre on Twitter: www.twitter.com/shearshare
And Instagram: www.instagram.com/shearshare
And Periscope: www.periscope.com/shearshareGet to know the ShearShare team and the awesome ShearShare App by visiting www.shearshare.com. We all know time is money, so with this app, I can quickly knock out the needed barbershop searches that would usually take me hours to do.‚Äù ‚ÄúFantastic app! This is a wonderful idea! tagline: iOS app to test any REST service
text_content: [{u'description': u'Kat is the best thing to happen to your API workflow. It's a full-featured iOS app to test any REST service. It doesn't matter if you're developing an app to connect to an API or developing the API itself, with Kat you can create a request and examine the response. Kat supports GET, POST, PUT and DELETE requests with headers, bodies and parameters. It can display data in a special JSON view, text with syntax highlighting or render the html for you. Kat is designed to work on iOS 9 and 10, so you too can have the freedom of developing on the iOS platform. Kat is the second app of the ‚ÄòDeveloper pets‚Äô collection, and can be purchased together with a discount. I would love to hear your thoughts about Kat, and if there are any pets that you are still missing on iOS!', u'title': u'Kat - An API Tester'}]

tagline: An encyclopedia that talks to your kids
text_content:
[{u'description': u'kidkedoo develops a talking encyclopedia for young kids that makes it fun and easy to access a whole world of exciting knowledge. It encourages curiosity, independence and a joy for learning! Our products suit children's natural needs, nourish their curiosity, and encourage active pursuit for information.', u'title': u'Kidkedoo, Where kids go to know!'}, {u'body': u' Woohoo! Join thousands of curios kids worldwide, who are already exploring and discovering new things and places with the best educational app Wikids, an encyclopedia that talks to kids!Wikids, enable kids who can't read yet satisfy their curiosity, independently !Designed for independent discovery, Wikids gives kids ages 3-8 the freedom to ‚Äúlook up‚Äù what interests them. The super-accessible app explains in kid-friendly language over 192 (!) topics. Each entry is approximately 80 words in written form and narrated in a friendly voice, and accompanied with colorful images.Try now and get 24 fascinating entries for FREE!Did you know that grasshoppers listen from their bellies? That lightning is hotter than the Sun? That it took almost 2,000 years to build the Great Wall of China? Soon your kids may learn these and many more fascinating facts about amazing animals, beautiful places, and intriguing cultures, even before they can read or read well.Now you can earn medals on Wikids, which encourage you to explore more!Wikids is 100% kids safe and ad-free.This Wikids app contains the following categories:
‚Ä¢	Animals
‚Ä¢	The Human Body -NEW!
‚Ä¢	Space- NEW!
‚Ä¢	Countries
‚Ä¢	Nature
‚Ä¢	Musical Instruments- NEW!
‚Ä¢	Landmarks and Monuments
‚Ä¢	Traditional FoodFeatures:
- 192 exquisite entries to broaden your child‚Äôs horizons. 
- Medal system that encourages your curious kids to explore more!
- High quality narration and imagery.
- Intuitive navigation by category or by the ABC.
- Interrelated entries. For example, if your child explores "France", Wikids will also suggest the entries "Eiffel Tower" and "Croissant".
- 100% safe, clean content.
- Ad-free.   ', u'description': u'The Encyclopedia That Talks To Your Kids! Designed for independent discovery.', u'title': u'Wikids, Encyclopedia For Kids! - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': u'Woohoo! Join thousands of curios kids worldwide, who are already exploring and discovering new things and places with the best educational app Wikids, an encyclopedia that talks to kids! Wikids, Encyclopedia That Talks To Your Kids! Designed for independent discovery, Wikids gives kids ages 3-8 the freedom to ‚Äúlook up‚Äù what interests them. The super-accessible app explains in kid-friendly language over 120 topics. Each entry is approximately 80 words in written form and narrated in a friendly voice, and accompanied with colorful images. ‚ÄúWe were just looking for an app like this for our 4 year old son who asks lots of questions. What a great way to discover the world before learning to read. We love it!‚Äù by WeAreHappyNow5668322 - Appstore review ------Download now for FREE access to 10 entries ---- Wikids feeds your kids‚Äô natural appetite to learn. Did you know that grasshoppers listen from their bellies? That lightning is hotter than the Sun? That it took almost 2,000 years to build the Great Wall of China? Soon your kids may learn these and many more fascinating facts about amazing animals, beautiful places, and intriguing cultures, even before they can read or read well. Wikids is 100% kids safe and ad-free. ‚ÄúJust downloaded this app, and it's brilliant!!! Very educational, interactive and fun. Great for curious kids. tagline: Add crying Michael Jordan to your photos
text_content: [{u'description': u'The Crying Michael Jordan meme is definitely the meme of 2016. This app allows you to make your very own Crying Michael Jordan meme in the palm of your hand. Simply give it a photo to examine - by camera, selfie, or a photo in your album - and it will detect faces in the photo and put Jordan faces over them. Want to move them around a little bit? Your fingers can do all the work. Simply pinch, swipe, or rotate any head to move it around. Rub a Jordan head up and down to erase it. Hit the plus button to add one at the top of the image. Feel free to share photos any way you'd like through your device, or just save them to your camera roll. Thank you for downloading, and I hope you enjoy this app!', u'title': u'Crying Jordan Meme Generator'}]

text_content:
[{u'body': u' Dub to your favorite movie scene, make your pet talk, create Bad Lip Reading videos, commentaries. The possibilities are endless. Through these dubs, people have entirely a new medium to express themselves and their creativity. Dublr empowers anyone to create new stories with their voice to over the popular videos and share them with the friends. Getting started is super easy. 
1. Pick a video from app, or upload your own
2. Preview the video and when you are ready dub your voice over it
3. Share your dubbed videos with your friends   ', u'description': u'A cool way to dub over a video & share. Dublr makes video fun. Get it for FREE.', u'title': u'Dublr App - Android Apps on Google Play'}]

tagline: Simple, minimal & easy note-taking
text_content:
[{u'body': u' When we started Buno (an abbreviation of Bucket Notes), the main purpose was to make note taking simple, beautiful and intuitive. And here we are to redefine that. Here‚Äôs how:‚Ä¢ QUICK NOTES
Capture your everyday thoughts with our simple swipe gesture that makes it super easy to take notes
-Swipe down, take a note and swipe down again to save it. 
- Minimal interface to avoid any distractions while taking notes to help you focus on writing
- Clip inspirations, images or even your sketches. 
- Organisation is made easy with our systematic bucket technique that helps you categorise thoughts seamlessly. Create a Bucket or save it into ‚ÄúUncategorised‚Äù to move it later on. 
- Real-time word count for writers to keep a track of progress. ‚Ä¢ SECURITY 
Apart from design, our next focus was mainly on security due to the sensitive information a user can save on our app. We took utmost care in developing an advanced encryption system that protects your notes on the server side incase of any unauthorised access. 
We also built a clean 4-digit password protection that can be activated from the Settings tab. ‚Ä¢ GESTURE
Buno was created with a goal to make buttons redundant so developed a gesture based UI that helps you take notes with just one swipe to start and save your thoughts. ‚Ä¢ SEAMLESS SYNC
Buno syncs seamlessly with Android, iOS(coming soon) and Web App(coming soon). Take note on one device and continue editing on another device. Our advanced mechanism syncs notes so quick that you won‚Äôt even notice it. ‚Ä¢ SHARE, MOVE or DELETE
We love to share what we create so once you swipe left on any note you'll have icons which will help you share your note across different platforms, move to a different Bucket or delete it from the server completely.---

tagline: The text editor for iPhone, iPad and Apple Watch!
text_content: [{u'description': u'Eddie is a text editor for iPhone, iPad and Apple Watch. You can create a document on your Apple Watch using voice dictation then send it to your iPhone with one tap for further editing. All of your documents save to the cloud, allowing you to continue editing the document on your iPad. Your documents will save to the device if you do not have an internet connection then automatically upload when you connect. Use the built in web browser to quickly research and copy into your document. Switch to night mode to darken the UI and improve focus at night. You can create a written document by using the voice dictation in Apple Watch which can then be viewed and edited on the iPhone or iPad.', u'title': u'Eddie'}, {u'description': u'Eddie is an intelligent cloud based text editor for the Mac, iPhone, iPad and Apple Watch.', u'title': u'Eddie'}]

text_content: [{u'description': u'Ahoy News for MAC delivers the most interesting and talked about stories from across the internet using the power of machine learning. Ahoy News removes the up worthy articles. The wording of these headlines is always ‚Äúwhat happened next will blow your mind‚Äù or ‚Äúhow it ends up is heart-breaking‚Äù or ‚ÄúYou will get angry when you see‚Ä¶‚Äù and on and on. tagline: Automatically get all the photos friends' take of you
text_content: [{u'description': u'Automatically get all the photos friends' take of you. How it works PhotoKharma uses face recognition to let you access the photos of you on friends‚Äô phones. You give friends access to the photos they‚Äôre in, and in return they give you access to the photos you‚Äôre in. That's kharma! Once you have access, you can download the photos you love--or ask to delete the photos you hate. What about privacy? Don‚Äôt worry, you‚Äôre in full control. You can give all of your friends access--or just your very closest friends. You can also block any photo you want. How to set it up Give a friend access to the photos they‚Äôre in and invite them to the app. When they join and give you access to the photos you‚Äôre in, you‚Äôll both be able to view the photos you take of each other. It‚Äôs simple! Special bonus Got kids? A spouse? A special someone? Friends can give you access to photos of them too!', u'title': u'PhotoKharma--get lost photos of you'}, {u'description': u'', u'title': u'PhotoKharma'}]

tagline: Play, remix and create dance music
text_content: [{u'description': u'BANGERS is the iPhone app to PLAY and REMIX the greatest dance music hits and even CREATE your own. No experience required! PERFORM YOUR FAVORITE DANCE MUSIC TUNES Play the hits with very simple tools. Combine Clips, One Shots and FX like a pro. REMIX THE HITS Change sounds, edit beats, add FX. Make them yours! LEARN WHILE PLAYING A GAME Every song can be played as a game (Practice Mode) or performed and remixed (Creation Mode). Get a high score and earn credits to unlock songs. THE HOTTEST STYLES Electro, Future, Deep and Tech House, Dance Pop, Dubstep and Trap & more to come. THE GREATEST SONGS More than 70 tracks available, including all those tunes you love to dance to. WEEKLY UPDATES Never get bored: new songs added on a weekly basis! UNLIMITED PREMIUM SUBSCRIPTION: - You can subscribe for unlimited access to the BANGERS full content - The subscriptions are $3.99 weekly, $7,99 monthly and $39.99 annually* - You‚Äôll be able to play all available songs and challenges for the duration of the subscription - Payment will be charged to iTunes Account at confirmation purchase - Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of current period - Account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period at the cost of the chosen package - Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user‚Äôs Account Settings after purchase - No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during active subscription period *Price are equal to the value that ‚ÄúApple‚Äôs App Store Matrix‚Äù determines is equivalent of the subscription price in $USD.', u'title': u'Bangers - Play, Remix and Create Dance Music Hits'}, {u'description': u'BANGERS is the app to PLAY and REMIX the greatest electronic dance music hits and CREATE your own. No experience required. Free download!', u'title': u'Bangers ‚Äì Play, Remix and Create Dance Music Hits'}]

tagline: Never get sunburnt again
text_content:
[{u'body': u' Exposure to sunlight‚Äôs ultraviolet radiation (UV) can damage to your skin, cause sunburn and increase your risk of skin cancer. UVLens shows you when you need to take care and when you can safely enjoy the sun.  -Get active more. Spend more time outdoors AND stay safe from the sun
-Keep your family safe, designed to warn you when the UV is really high
-Education. Learn what you need to do depending on how strong the UV isFeatures:
‚Ä¢ Plan out the best time to be outside
See the UV forecast for the day, see when it‚Äôs safe to be outside and when to avoid the sun.‚Ä¢ Find your burn risk
Find out how long you can spend in the sun by taking a personalised skin type assessment.‚Ä¢ Shedding light on UV
UV is deceptive and invisible to our eyes, learn what protection measures to take and when to apply sunscreen.About
UVLens is being developed by the team at Spark 64 Ltd, a company making products to help people live healthier outdoor lives. Contact us at enquiries@spark64.com Follow us
www.uvlens.com
www.facebook.com/UVLens
twitter.com/uvlens   ', u'description': u'UVLens keeps you safe in the sun.', u'title': u'UVLens - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': u'UVLens keeps you safe in the sun. tagline: Idea to mobile prototypes in minutes. Zero coding required.
text_content: [{u'description': u'Demonstrate is an easy-to-use, free prototyping app allowing users to create native app demos without writing any code. Prototypes created using Demonstrate make use of native transitions & gestures, allowing you to import your paper or whiteboard sketches and even high-fidelity screens from the camera roll or Dropbox. Demonstrate allows you to play your projects in full-screen mode, giving the app prototypes a rich native feel. tagline: Receive your landline calls on your mobile.
text_content: [{u'description': u'Warning: this application is intended for users of the Swissvoice Voice Bridge Base station ----- Swissvoice Voice Bridge application allows you to place & receive calls from your plain telephone line (PSTN) using your iOS device using the WiFi connection available in your home. Outside home, user is notified from call with notifications. The application is compatible with any iOS6 and newer device.', u'title': u'Voice Bridge'}, {u'body': u' Warning : this application is functional only with Swissvoice Voice Bridge base station.This application is still in beta mode: your feedback will quickly be taken into account. Voice Bridge transforms your mobile into your new fixed phone!Swissvoice Voice Bridge application allows you to place & receive calls from your traditional landline (PSTN) using your android device at home. While away from home, your smartphone is notified of incoming calls on your landline. The application is compatible with any android 4.2.x and newer device.   ', u'description': u'Swissvoice - Voice Bridge - Your landline on your mobile', u'title': u'Voice Bridge - Android Apps on Google Play'}]

tagline: 1st icon-based watch that teaches kids good habits and time
text_content:

tagline: Sometimes all we need is to go offline and just hang
text_content: [{u'description': u'JUST HANG is a great way to connect with your friends! we all know the feeling, we have some time to spend, but everybody seems to be busy and you‚Äôre starting to feel like ‚Äúthe annoying‚Äù friend so you end up alone‚Ä¶ at home‚Ä¶ again! But now you have the tool to get out of the house and be social without feeling like ‚Äúthe annoying salesman‚Äù who‚Äôs knocking on everyones door. Just quickly make your ‚Äúevent‚Äù in a couple of taps, choose who you want to invite and wait - OR you can go directly to the invite section (friends) and see if anybody already have posted an event where you could join - it‚Äôs simple, hassle-free and fun! CHAT, MEET UP & JUST HANG! We use in-app purchase which gets you the feature to invite and see invites from "STRANGERS" and it will also get rid of the ads. GO PRO and get access to extra features and remove advertising. - the subscription is not auto-renewable and you will need to purchase again when the selected subscription period expires to keep the PRO features! The monthly cost of the PRO membership will decrease the longer commitment you make, so the 12 month period is about 50% cheaper a month than the monthly subscription.', u'title': u'Just Hang - the social app'}]

text_content:
[{u'body': u' Emojifi - Tag words to emojis and express more‚òÖ ‚å® Use your default keyboard - Emojifi provides emoji suggestions using your existing keyboard without the pain of switching keyboard just to get the emoji suggestions üòÄ. As you type, emojis will automatically pop up on a bar called Emoji bar for you to select. You don‚Äôt have to scroll through the several pages to find the right emoji to use.‚òÖ üè∑ Tag words to emoji & express more -  Emojifi has a set of words tagged to each emoji. But what if you want to tag some other word/words to an emoji ü§îü§î. 
Use Emojifi‚Äôs (üí™ Patent pending üí™) tagging feature to tag any word to any emoji       For example
           üôà Custom tag this emoji for word ‚Äòblushing‚Äô apart from its regular use of ‚Äòsee 
                  no evil‚Äô
           ‚öΩ In addition to the regular tag of ‚Äòsoccer‚Äô, you can also tag this emoji to the       
                  word ‚Äòfootball‚Äô or ‚ÄòFIFA‚Äô or your favourite player
           üçª This emoji is tagged to word ‚Äòbeer‚Äô. Want to tag this emoji to the word ‚Äòparty‚Äô? Use emojifi.
           You can use Emojifi to tag üÜó to the word ‚Äòkk‚Äô or tag üëç to ‚Äòkk‚Äô or tag üëå to ‚Äòkk‚Äô ‚òÖ üëÜTap functionality -  Click on any emoji in the emoji bar and the typed word gets replaced by the clicked emoji. Long press to insert tagged word along with the emoji ‚òÖ üì≤ Works in any app - Emojifi works in all your favourite apps like Whatsapp, Facebook Messenger, Snapchat, Kik, Instagram, Twitter, Hangouts and many more. üò¶üòßüò±Gifs & Stickers to be supported very very soon ü§òü§òü§ò Emoji used in our app is provided for free by http://emojione.com. Emojifi team thanks the entire team of Emojione for providing such wonderful emoji sets for free.   ', u'description': u'Tag words to emoji & get emoji suggestions with your existing keyboard ‚å®', u'title': u'Emojifi -Tag words to emoji üòÄ - Android Apps on Google Play'}]

tagline: A beautiful Mac app for Trello
text_content: [{u'description': u'Paws is a beautiful Trello client for Mac. It brings Trello to your desktop with native notifications, powerful shortcuts and more - away from the distractions of your browser. - Beautiful minimal interface that lets you stay productive and doesn‚Äôt get in the way of your work. - Get notified whenever there‚Äôs new activity in any of your Trello boards. - Set a global shortcut that opens the main window from anywhere. - Navigate between your starred boards with a quick shortcut Trello is already full of useful shortcuts and options. We‚Äôve made sure they work as they were intended, including keyboard shortcuts, drag & drop and more. **Paws requires a free Trello.com account to use. You can create a Trello account in Paws. ** Paws for Trello is built by a small team. We‚Äôd love to know how we can make you even more productive, so get in touch via the App Store ‚ÄúSupport‚Äù link, or tweet us @GoFriendlyFoxes. ---- Some useful Paws shortcuts: - Cmd+Alt+T - Open Paws from anywhere (customizable) - Cmd+1-9 - Quick access to your Starred Boards - Cmdl+0 - Open Boards page - Right-click on card - quick edit menu - All Trello shortcuts still work! ---- Paws for Trello is not affiliated, associated, authorized, endorsed by or in any way officially connected to Trello, Inc. (www.trello.com). Trello and Trello logo are trademarks of Trello Inc.', u'title': u'Paws for Trello on the Mac App Store'}]

tagline: Personal assistant that helps you manage your time
text_content: [{u'description': u'Trevor is a personal assistant that helps you manage your time in a mindful way. He keeps your Calendar and Reminders in sync, so you can schedule your tasks, right into your calendar, with a simple drag & drop. Planning your day takes just seconds and works like magic. Your to-do lists are limitless, but your time is not. With Trevor, you can take control of your time, by scheduling the things you need to get done, and then work with clarity, focus and peace of mind. - Plan your day - Track time and progress - Schedule tasks from a searchable, centralized list - Focus your time and energy on the task at hand - Make time for the things that matter - Use Natural Language Use Trevor for personal tasks, work, education, business, growth hacking, and more. It works in a very simple and familiar way. Just download the app and take control of your time. "Our essential intent is to help you find the time for the things that make your life fulfilling. This is just the first step." - George, Founder', u'title': u'Trevor AI - Time Management Assistant'}]

tagline: Unique and wacky approach to news, now on iOS and Apple TV
text_content: [{u'description': u'A unique and often wacky approach to news in technology, media, and entertainment, Cheddar is broadcast daily from the floor of the New York Stock Exchange, with exclusive CEO and founder interviews and the best of technology and media coverage. With this Cheddar subscription, you will receive: ‚Ä¢ Daily weekday updates from the stock exchange floor ‚Ä¢ Exclusive interviews with top tier CEO's ‚Ä¢ The company profiles you care about ‚Ä¢ Business advice straight from the experts Subscribe to get access to Cheddar videos, right on your iPhone or iPad. ‚Ä¢ Pay $6.99 a month with a 30-day free trial, renewing monthly.* ‚Ä¢ Pay $59.99 a year with a 30-day free trial, renewing annually.* * All payments will be paid through your iTunes Account and may be managed under Account Settings after the initial payment. Subscription payments will automatically renew unless deactivated at least 24-hours before the end of the current cycle. Your account will be charged for renewal at least 24-hours prior to the end of the current cycle. Any unused portion of your free trial will be forfeited upon payment. Cancellations are incurred by disabling auto-renewal. Terms of Service: https://cheddar.vhx.tv/tos Privacy Policy: https://cheddar.vhx.tv/privacy', u'title': u'Cheddar.com'}, {u'description': u'Cheddar is a live and on demand video news network focused on covering the most innovative products, technologies, and services transforming our lives. The network covers this news through the lens of the companies and executives driving these changes. Cheddar broadcasts from Post 10 on the floor of the New York Stock Exchange and NASDAQ Marketsite.  The company was founded by Jon Steinberg, President and Chief Operating Officer of BuzzFeed from 2010 to 2014.', u'title': u'Cheddar'}]

tagline: All your credit cards on one device
text_content:
[{u'body': u' Add mobile tap & go to VISA cards you already own. Simply add a card to the app and you're ready to tap. Tap & pay all the way*Card details stay on the app*
Your card details never leave the app. Tapito does not communicate with the internet and card details are never stored on any cloud server.* Works in North and South American countries*
Tapito will work with Mastercard and VISA debit and credit cards issued anywhere but only with contactless terminals in North & South American countries, including: Argentina, Brazil, Mexico, and USA.   ', u'description': u'Tap & go with a VISA card you already own.', u'title': u'Tapito - Android Apps on Google Play'}]

tagline: Watch the best web videos of the day ‚Äì even offline!
text_content: [{u'description': u'‚ÄúTHE BEST OF WEB VIDEO, EVERY DAY‚Äù (TechCrunch) Apple‚Äôs ‚ÄúBEST OF 2015‚Äù video app is coming to iPhone for free. Watch the top 10 web videos of the day ‚Äî even without internet! Curated by video experts, based on your interests and automatically preloaded to your iPhone overnight via Wi-Fi. Data plans and bad connections won‚Äôt stop you anymore. ‚ÄúINTRIGUING, HIGH-DEFINITION CONTENT‚Äù (Refinery29) Imagine if every time you wanted to watch a good video, someone gave you a great one: hand-picked from thousands of brand-new videos online, by a team of award-winning filmmakers, every single day. Hyper is the critically acclaimed daily top 10 video playlist that does exactly that. ‚ÄúSPECTACULAR VIEWING EXPERIENCE‚Äù (App Recap) The best part: videos are instantly available on the go, even without internet! How? Your playlist automatically preloads overnight while you‚Äôre sleeping, making Hyper the easiest way to watch awesome videos anywhere: * NO MORE SEARCHING. We scout the web every day. Based on your interests, we select the best videos for you. * NO MORE LOADING. Videos are magically available offline. Preloaded overnight, for instant playback by day. * NO DISTRACTIONS. We‚Äôve built the cleanest and fastest video interface you‚Äôve seen, to put content front and center. What others say: ‚ÄúHYPER CUTS THROUGH THE JUNK‚Äù (The Next Web) ‚ÄúTHE BEST & NEWEST VIDEOS ONLINE‚Äù (Adweek) ‚ÄúHANDPICKED BY VIDEO EXPERTS‚Äù (Gizmodo) ‚ÄúMAKES YOU WANT TO WATCH & DISCOVER‚Äù (WIRED) ‚ÄúTOTALLY BLOWN AWAY. HYPER IS A MUST-HAVE‚Äù (TP) Please note: Offline functionality is only available on iPhone and not yet supported for all videos. We‚Äôre working hard on expanding our offline video inventory and bringing the feature to iPad. This is our first iPhone release. If you have any feedback or experience any problems, please shoot us an email at feedback@watchhyper.com. We appreciate it!', u'title': u'Hyper: Daily Videos Offline'}, {u'description': u'Apple‚Äôs ‚ÄúBest of 2015‚Äù video app is coming to iPhone. Watch the best web videos of the day ‚Äì even offline! Download now for free.', u'title': u'Hyper | Your Daily Top 10 Video Playlist'}]

tagline: Create a city guide with help of your friends.
text_content: [{u'description': u'Flamyngo is a crazy simple way to save your favourite places and ask your friends for theirs. Imagine going to New York for your next trip. You reach out to your friends via Facebook or email and ask them which coffee venues, restaurants, parks or stores to visit. Flamyngo makes this process way easier and helps you to get the best out of a city! Select which friends you want to ask for their suggestions and receive all of them in one inbox. Your friends can add places easily, without even having to sign up for Flamyngo. All they need to know is the name of the place and Flamyngo will automatically find it for them including all the info you need like opening hours, contact info and photos. Here‚Äôs what to expect: ‚Ä¢ Easily add your own favourite places to your guide; ‚Ä¢ Forget the hassle of asking travel tips from friends! Receive all suggestions in one inbox with all the info you need; ‚Ä¢ Turn these suggestions from your inbox into your own beautiful city guides; ‚Ä¢ More time to travel and explore amazing places! Flamyngo is just getting started. We read every review to make the app better for you. Stay tuned for more! Let‚Äôs connect: Facebook: facebook.com/FlamyngoAndCo Instagram: @FlamyngoAndCo Twitter: @FlamyngoAndCo Any feedback? Please send it to ‚Äòtech@flamyngo.co‚Äô. Many thanks!', u'title': u'Flamyngo - the new way to ask friends for travel tips'}, {u'description': u'Flamyngo is an easy way to share your favourite places with your audience. Quickly add your favourite places to your blog posts in the context it deserves.', u'title': u'Flamyngo'}]

tagline: Writing notes made simple
text_content: [{u'description': u'A simple, markdown based note-taking app. # Key Features: - Write notes, journals & research in markdown (easy-to-read, easy-to-write plain text format) - Read notes in clean and beautiful previews. - Organize notes in multiple notebooks. - Search notes by title or content within notebooks. - Experience the app in two beautiful themes, Light & Dark. - Sync notes across your Mac, iPhone, iPad, and iPod Touch using iCloud Drive. # Code-Highlighting: Note-Preview supports code-highlighting for multiple programming languages with & without line-numbers. To use code-highlighting enclose the code in your notes in ```prettyprint // Write Code here ``` To add line-numbers with code-highlighting use ```prettyprint linenums:1 // Write Code here ``` # To-do lists: You can cerate to-do lists or task-lists using "[ ]" and "[x]" at start of list items, - [x] Completed Task - [ ] Incomplete Task like so. # iPad only features: - Editor-only & Preview-only modes on iPad allow you to write & read notes in a distraction-free UI. - Use the app in multi-app multitasking mode to take notes while performing activities in other apps side-by-side.', u'title': u'Falcon Notes'}]

tagline: Train your voice with your own virtual vocal coach
text_content:
[{u'body': u' SWIFTSCALES was created by singers, for singers, and is the first app to simulate sitting at the piano with a vocal coach. Unlike other apps & audio lessons, SWIFTSCALES moves with you, as high or low, fast or slow as needed. You control every session in real time or passively, the only limits being the 88 keys of the piano and your imagination. No musical knowledge required! In fact, vocal coaches themselves can use SWIFTSCALES on the go to train and warm up students with exercises they already teach thanks to the app's endless flexibility and customization.Whether beginner or master, student or teacher, SWIFTSCALES grants a lifetime of ever evolving vocal training. Singers, this is the app you've been waiting for!APP FEATURES: (*)-First user interface of its kind
-Built in sessions from beginner to expert
-No prior musical knowedge required
-Create custom sessions of any difficulty
-Complete control of sessions in real-time
-Unlimited amount of training variation
-Create your own custom scale patterns
-Professionally recorded audio samples
-Bonus Reading and exercises for novices
-Video Tutorials for using the app
-Contextual help on every page of the app
-Supports every mobile device size/shape*The vast majority of the features in this app are available free of charge, ad supported. To enable extended app features and remove advertisements, users may upgrade via a one-time in app purchase. You control every session in real time or passively, the only limits being the 88 keys of the piano and your imagination. No musical knowledge required! tagline: Fastest way to find live sports streams
text_content: [{u'description': u'Sportle is the fastest and easiest way to find live sports streams. Within seconds, you can find where a game is streaming and whether you have access to it. It's also the essential sports app to discover live events you didn‚Äôt know were happening. ‚Ä¢ Find live streams from one app across networks like ESPN, Fox Sports, NBC Sports, YouTube and more ‚Ä¢ Did you know access to cable credentials allow you to stream? Enter them one time to see what games you have access to ‚Ä¢ Favorite teams to receive custom notifications ‚Ä¢ Never miss the final minutes. Get notifications for games going down to the wire and tap to watch instantly What publications have said about Sportle: ‚Ä¢ Fox Business: "The Google of streaming sports‚Äù ‚Ä¢ Vice: ‚ÄúThe easiest way to find live sports streams‚Äù ‚Ä¢ Mashable: ‚ÄúSportle makes streaming major sporting events easy" Leagues, tournaments and sports covered include: Football (NFL, NCAA, International Leagues) Basketball (NBA, NCAA, International Leagues) Baseball (MLB, College World Series, Little League World Series, International Leagues) Hockey (NHL, KHL, VHL, Other International Leagues) Soccer (Euro Cup 2016, Copa America, EPL, La Liga, Bundesliga, Serie A, Ligue 1, MLS, Champions League, World Cup, Olympics and much more) Golf (PGA, Masters, US Open, PGA Championship, British Open, LPGA, Other Major Tournaments) Tennis (ATP, WTA, Wimbledon, US Open, French Open, Australian Open) Olympics Auto Racing (Nascar, Formula 1, Indianapolis 500 and much more) Mixing Martial Arts (UFC, Bellator, ACB) Surfing (World Surf League and more) Rugby Boxing Badminton Cricket Handball E-Sports Press Conferences Want to suggest a new feature, report streams that are missing, or need support? Email: info@sportle.tv Twitter: @sportletv', u'title': u'Sportle„ÉªLive Sports, Streams, Scores, and Schedules'}]

tagline: Listen to your favorite news sites when you can't read them
text_content: [{u'description': u'Listen to the websites you love... as you drive, work out, or relax! Meep's professional narrators read stories aloud about your favorite topics... from science to celebrities, sports to politics, and 1000s more. Download Meep and listen to what you love in less than a minute! - Skip anything you're not in the mood for. Meep is always learning what you like, and improving your stations. - Listen for 5 minutes or 5 hours and get the stories you care most about. - Hear what your friends have listened to recently, and send them your recorded reactions. - Mix in fun stuff like music clips, local weather, and stock prices. - There's no set up time, and no podcasts to look through. - Light magazine-style content that won't hurt your brain! - Hear news as it happens, not hours or days later. Try Meep and let us know what you think at feedback@meep,com! ---- Want to subscribe to Meep? - You do not need to subscribe to enjoy up to 50 stories/month. - Meep offers additional story credits and features with a subscription: * Basic: 250 storiy credits/mo, up to 5 stations. 7 days free, $7.99/mo after. * Plus: 500 story credits/mo, up to 10 stations. Currently on sale for $6.99/mo, billed annually. * Premium: Unlimited stories and stations. $9.99/mo - Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period - Account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period, and identify the cost of the renewal - Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to your Account Settings after purchase - No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during active subscription period - Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when the user purchases a subscription to that publication. - Our Privacy Policy and Terms of Use are available at http://www.meep.com/privacy/', u'title': u'Meep - Listen to News from the Web'}, {u'description': u'', u'title': u'Your Personalized Radio Magazine'}]

tagline: Catch up with the news in 10 sec or less.
text_content: [{u'description': u'Don‚Äôt have enough time to read about all that is going on in the world? NOD - News On Demand - tailors content to your attention span. Everyday, discover the three most important stories in the news. Read a short or a long article about it. Whether you have 10 seconds or 5 minutes, there is great content waiting for you, handpicked from the world‚Äôs 100+ best sources. Launch the awesome catch up feature by tapping on the date and find out what happened while you were offline. Don‚Äôt follow the news, get it! - SLEEK DESIGN: each story is displayed on a card, to allow you to get the whole picture at a glance. Decide if you want to go deeper based on a set of clues: minutes to read, source, teaser. Crafted for an outstanding visual experience on all iPhone devices, including iPhone 6 and 6 Plus. - RAPID NAVIGATION: grab the card you want to read first, swipe the card to the side when you‚Äôre ready for the next one, access the catch up feature from the main screen (date) or from the last screen (past stories). Effortless and quick. - INSTANT FEEDBACK: as you swipe the cards, we learn what made you a more informed citizen (NOD!) or what was less interesting for you (dismiss). No complicated set up needed before the first use. The NOD Widget for iOS 8 offers a glimpse of a leading story, directly from the Notification Center on your device.', u'title': u'NOD - News On Demand'}]

tagline: Discover, give feedback and support startup ideas
text_content:
[{u'body': u' - A simple, easy-to-use, elegant interface reminiscent of popular social media feeds
- Quickly give feedback by swiping left/right to dismiss or be reminded of an idea if it becomes popular
- Tap on an idea to learn more. Love an idea to follow its progress and shape its direction
- Spread ideas by easily sharing them via social media
- Explore ideas that are nearby
- Quickly poll your followers for directional feedback regarding pricing, desirability, feasibility, among other things
- See all of your followers, across all ideas, and their expertise
- Gauge interest of your followers in being future customers via pledging   ', u'description': u'Get quick feedback and connect with potential customers, experts and investors.', u'title': u'Flare - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': u'Where great ideas gather', u'title': u'Flare'}]

tagline: The new era of social messaging
text_content:
[{u'body': u' Yubl brings you closer to the people and things you love. tagline: Weather based radio and music discovery
text_content: [{u'description': u'weatherTunes Weather based radio/discovery. The right tunes for right now. Just hit play and go! weatherTunes creates playlists that fit the weather conditions around you, giving you the perfect songs for right now. Just choose your favorite genre and start listening. weatherTunes works behind the scenes using conditions currently around you, including things like how cloudy it is, humidity, and even time of day, to pick songs that will fit that moment in time. Features: - No thinking, just hit play - View current weather conditions - Listen to the perfect songs for this moment in time - Background images change to match the weather conditions - Watch the youTube video while listening - Choose from 12 different genres', u'title': u'weatherTunes - Weather based radio/discovery. The right tunes for right now.'}]

tagline: Connecting businesses with fans, customers, and community
text_content: [{u'description': u'Twitter Dashboard is a free app that makes it easy to manage your business on Twitter. It‚Äôs the perfect tool to help you schedule Tweets, get right to the Tweets that matter, and engage more with your customers and community. Dashboard offers a single destination to get things done. It gives business owners a clear picture of what‚Äôs being said about their businesses and offers insights about their Tweet performance. Twitter is a place where businesses can share news, tell stories, and have conversations that support, educate, and delight their customers. Dashboard can help. Use it to: - See all the Tweets about you, so you don‚Äôt miss anything important. - Schedule your Tweets to save time and reach more people. - Track your analytics to understand what‚Äôs working and get the most out of Twitter. - Get Tweet ideas and inspiration with built-in tips for businesses. Dashboard is currently in beta.', u'title': u'Twitter Dashboard'}]

text_content:
[{u'body': u' ALWAYS READY, CONNECTED, AND FAST. Just ask.
The free Amazon Alexa App is a companion to your Alexa device for setup, remote control, and enhanced features. Alexa is always ready to play your favorite music, provide weather and news updates, answer questions, create lists, and much more. Alexa's brain is in the cloud, so she continually learns and adds more functionality over time. The more you use Alexa, the more she adapts to your speech patterns, vocabulary, and personal preferences. 
 
HOW IT WORKS
Interactions with Alexa are automatically mirrored visually on your Amazon Alexa App, providing more information as you want it. The Amazon Alexa App lets you easily manage your alarms, music, shopping lists, and more -- wherever you are. 
 
FAST WI-FI and EASY SET UP
Connect to your home's Wi-Fi network using the free Amazon Alexa App, with its simple guided setup. Now you can stream all of your music, listen to radio stations, and have access to news and information, all by voice -- or with the Amazon Alexa App's intuitive interface. text_content: [{u'description': u'Postepic is a new way to capture, share and collect your favorite quotes from the books you read. Discover great books and authors with a continuous feed of thousands passages shared by the community. With Postepic you can: ‚Ä¢ Capture a photo or a screenshot of a quote from a book you are reading. ‚Ä¢ Post it to Postepic library or save it in your private collection. ‚Ä¢ Discover epic books by easily browsing and searching quotes posted by others. ‚Ä¢ Share quotes to promote books and authors among your friends, family and social networks. ‚Ä¢ Collect in one place all quotes you posted and liked. Let us know your feedback. Write a review, drop us an email at hello@postepic.com or reach out to us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/postepic', u'title': u'Postepic ‚Äì Share Quotes & Discover Epic Books'}]

tagline: Share and discover the best gameplay highlights
text_content: [{u'description': u'Leet is where gamers share and discover the best gameplay highlights. Share your epic, funniest, or most ridiculous highlights right from your Xbox, PS4, or PC in 3 simple steps. Select your gameplay video, trim it down to that perfect moment, and share with your friends and followers! Can‚Äôt find what you‚Äôre looking for? Search and explore your favorite games or follow streamers and eSports players so you never miss a highlight. AWESOME FEATURES ‚óè Discover the best gameplay highlights from all your favorite games ‚óè Upload and trim your highlights from your Xbox One, PS4, or PC ‚óè Search and explore highlights from the community ‚óè Build an audience, follow streamers, and never miss a highlight ‚óè Share your highlights to Facebook, Twitter, and Instagram Leet was built for gamers, by gamers. Our goal is to celebrate gamers and their amazing moments! Got a question, or just want to say hi? Send us an email at love@leetapp.co or tweet us @leet_app ‚ñ∏ Follow us on Twitter @leet_app ‚ñ∏ www.leetapp.co', u'title': u'Leet - Gameplay highlights from Xbox, PS4, and PC'}, {u'description': u'Share and discover awesome gameplay clips.', u'title': u'Leet - Share your awesome gameplay highlights'}]

text_content: [{u'description': u'Vampr is an app that helps you to discover, connect and collaborate with musicians and music lovers alike. Who you know or where you live are no longer barriers for getting on with playing and making music. DISCOVER - Find a guitarist, singer or producer for your latest project, audition for that punk band you always wanted to join or simply discover friends with the same taste in music. text_content: [{u'description': u'--== Make Remarkable Photos ==-- Remarkly captures just the ink from paper notes, sticky notes, or even a paper napkin and places it onto your photos and screenshots. Personalize photos using your own handwriting. Create your own custom hand-drawn emoji. Add a comment on Facebook¬Æ. Send off a quick customized "Happy Birthday". Capture and share that napkin inspiration. tagline: The easiest way to create customizable employee applications
text_content:
[{u'body': u' WISP app is a mobile employee handbook.  It simplifies the execution of company‚Äôs HR management practices of onboarding, employee engagement, and employee information. WISP delivers the most important corporate information directly into the employees‚Äô mobile phones. 
Your mobile employee handbook will give users a quick access to the company‚Äôs policy, info, and staff contact book (phone numbers, skype IDs, and e-mail addresses).   Employees will always be updated about what happens in the company with WISP‚Äôs news sharing and commenting option. They will also be able to communicate with each other in an instant corporate messenger. Features:
‚Ä¢	Adding and changing the company info, mission; branding the app with company‚Äôs logo and corporate colors
‚Ä¢	Sharing company‚Äôs policy
‚Ä¢	Creating and managing staff‚Äôs contact book
‚Ä¢	Sharing and commenting company‚Äôs news
‚Ä¢	Tagging news to share with selected groups of users
‚Ä¢	Using a corporate messenger to communicate with colleagues  IMPORTANT! 
The app is simple to use and manage. It is configured and customized within the web interface. All changes made in the web interface are immediately shown in the app. You need to subscribe at wispapp.com to start using your unique corporate employee handbook app.   ', u'description': u'WISP is an easy-to-customize employee handbook application.', u'title': u'Wisp Handbook - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': u'WISP app is a mobile employee handbook. It simplifies the execution of company‚Äôs HR management practices of onboarding, employee engagement, and employee information. WISP delivers the most important corporate information directly into the employees‚Äô mobile phones. Your mobile employee handbook will give users a quick access to the company‚Äôs policy, info, and staff contact book (phone numbers, skype IDs, and e-mail addresses). Employees will always be updated about what happens in the company with WISP‚Äôs news sharing and commenting option. They will also be able to communicate with each other in an instant corporate messenger. Features: ‚Ä¢ Adding and changing the company info, mission; branding the app with company‚Äôs logo and corporate colors ‚Ä¢ Sharing company‚Äôs policy ‚Ä¢ Creating and managing staff‚Äôs contact book ‚Ä¢ Sharing and commenting company‚Äôs news ‚Ä¢ Tagging news to share with selected groups of users ‚Ä¢ Using a corporate messenger to communicate with colleagues IMPORTANT! The app is simple to use and manage. It is configured and customized within the web interface. All changes made in the web interface are immediately shown in the app. You need to subscribe at wispapp.com to start using your unique corporate employee handbook app.', u'title': u'Wisp Handbook'}]

tagline: Smart clipboard history and snippet manager for Mac
text_content: [{u'description': u'Paste is a new way to copy and paste for your Mac. It keeps everything you've ever copied and lets you use your clipboard history anytime you need it. Paste recognizes and stores text, images, links, files and any other type of content and generates informative previews for easy browsing. Paste works in background and tightly integrates into your system and your workflow. An intuitive user interface and improved user experience allows you to focus on your core tasks and not on the application itself. Key features: ‚Äî Extends your clipboard history capacity up to unlimited. ‚Äî Pinboards and favorite snippets. ‚Äî History management, rules and exceptions. ‚Äî Intelligent search with flexible filters. ‚Äî Quick Look preview for any type of content. ‚Äî Select and paste multiple items simultaneously. ‚Äî Drag-n-drop multiple items to any application. ‚Äî Paste plain or rich text. ‚Äî Send clipboard history to other devices via AirDrop or share with your friends. "Paste is the Mac clipboard manager you never knew you needed." ‚Äî The Next Web ‚ÄúPaste is a simple, effective and pretty clipboard manager for the Mac.‚Äù ‚Äî 9to5Mac ‚ÄúPaste‚Äôs unsurpassed interface and OS X integration make it a standout among its more powerful peers.‚Äù ‚Äî Macworld You'll get started in no time and discover how Paste increases your productivity!', u'title': u'Paste ‚Äì smart clipboard history & snippets manager on the Mac App Store'}]

tagline: Creating quality time for parents and kids!
text_content:
[{u'body': u' O‚ÄôDaddy helps us enjoy quality time with our kids and create memorable moments. With thousands of activities and events to enjoy, O‚ÄôDaddy finds the best matches for our very own kids, at home, nearby, and outdoors.Our award-winning app O‚ÄôDaddy is very easy to use: Just let the app know the ages and genders of your kids, enable location, and you‚Äôll immediately receive relevant suggestions and ideas for fun activities and events that you could enjoy with your children on your quality time together. You'll get details on each activity, addresses and contact information for venues, and available discounts - all within the app. If there's interesting information regarding the activity - like articles, how-to videos, or related products, you'll find them all there, only a tap away.O'Daddy creates family quality time in several ways:
‚ñ∫Secures time with our kids through intelligent reminders. Balance work, life and smartphone usage better. Get home earlier to play! Turn off screens and put away devices to enjoy uninterrupted quality time.
‚ñ∫Suggests ideas for activities tailored to our kids based on their age, location, and preferences.
‚ñ∫Finds the best locations and deals near you: Whether you‚Äôre in the neighborhood or traveling with the family, ODaddy is the easy way to find the best places for kids‚Äô activities as well as the best coupons and discounts.
‚ñ∫Lets us focus on our kids, not your smartphone: Our optional Quality Time Mode turns off all mobile distractions (data and sounds) on our smartphone to help us focus on our kids and overcome our smartphone addiction. See how long you can part from your device!ODaddy saves us time searching for activities, so we can quickly put our phones away and enjoy uninterrupted time with our kids. When our kids are enjoying quality time with us, they‚Äôre away from their smartphones and tablets too ‚Äì which helps them avoid mobile addiction and enjoy face-to-face communication.Here at O'Daddy we welcome your feedback and are available to support you! Let us know what you think and what we can improve. Reach out to us at support@odaddy.me. 
If you like O'Daddy, please rank us with 5 Stars :-)Note: We efficiently use location information in order to offer intelligent notifications and insights. tagline: Tinder to find the cutest pet in the world!
text_content: [{u'description': u'Cutesy is the "Rate my Pet" app where you can rate other people's pets to determine the cutest pet in the world, or upload pictures of your pets, to see if your pet is the cutest! Is your pet cute or not? Will your pet be the pet of the day, week, or month? Download cutesy to find out! * Give and receive gifts for having cute pictures of your pet! * Upload multiple pictures of your pet * Upload and view Live Photos! * Choose between many many breeds of dogs, cats, and bunny rabbits! * Puppies, kittens, bunny rabbits absolutely encouraged * Give love to other people's pets, and impose your judgement! * Will your pet reach the top of the leaderboard? * Have your own pet owner's profile! Follow us on our social media platforms as well! https://instagram.com/cutesyapp/ https://twitter.com/cutesyapp/ https://www.facebook.com/cutesyapp Snapchat: Cutesy', u'title': u'Cutesy - The cutest pets!'}]

tagline: Digital business cards that are easily shared and searched
text_content:
[{u'body': u' WITH KNOWEE your contacts will reach you more easily that with traditional cards. Knowee cards are MORE EFFICIENT!Please, go to www.know.ee, sign up and create your cards. It's free!Know.ee IS:
- A powerful manager for traditional business cards with lots of helpful modern functionality
- A tool to make business card exchange easy and convenient. Save time and money and boost efficiency in networkingKnow.ee is more than:
- A business card to contact translator
- A business card scannerThe World loves business cards and will always do, but they are weird! 
- They are sticky: Tend to gather in stacks
- They are slippery: Scanners or assistants won‚Äôt get it right
- They contaminate: Your smartphone may get full of strangers
- They go undercover: No way you will find that oneWith Knowee you can:* CREATE YOUR OWN CARDS. Type in your data, upload card images (or design them), logo and portrait pic if you want. Create your personal cards as you need. i.e. with or without mobile number, postal address, etc. 
* SHARE A CARD. Select the card and share it using your phone, tablet or desktop. Send URL to click (email, whatsapp, SMS) or QR code to scan
* RECEIVE A CARD. Click and view it, Click/tap to call, email or navigate to address, view social media, download to contacts (if desired) and store the business card. Exchange info is also stored (location and date) for later search along with your notes.SEARCH, FIND & DO
Sort and search your Card Holder by anything you remember:
Name, surname, company, position, address, exchange date and location.
Find instantly the card you are looking for and...
**What do you want to do?
Click and call, email or navigate there, download contact to your device, export contact to Gmail, Yahoo, etc. or send card by email. Also, check where and when you received that cardALWAYS WITH YOU
Take this app and take your cards with you to share them when you need:
Send a link to your card via SMS, WhatsApp or email
Offer the QR code of your card to scan it
Get your counterpart to access your card instantly!KNOWEE PHILOSOPHY
The idea behind Knowee is that business cards are persistent, this is, You cannot make changes in a card. If you need, you create a new one and share it again as you would do with traditional cards. A card that is given will never change! Think of the implications of this idea.AND we believe that business cards should not become contacts by default. Knowee stores all your business cards so you can search, find and do, but only those cards you want or need will become contacts in your phone, Gmail, Yahoo, etc. just by hitting a button. Easy and convenient.FINALLY: DEAD EASY FOR OTHERS
Give your card as a URL via SMS, WhatsApp or email or send a QR to Maria...
And Maria will instantly click/tap and:
View data, call, email, navigate, store card, download contact‚Ä¶
NO TYPING. NO SCANNING!Email SIGNATURE:
Include a signature in your emails with a thumbnail of your card that links to your card in Knowee so people can click and store your card or contact straight away.PLUS much more useful functionality to come.Please, go to www.know.ee, sign up and create your cards. tagline: Custom animated posts for social media
text_content: [{u'description': u'Create eye-catching animated posts and stand out on social media. That‚Äôs the Ripl effect. Free Features: ‚Ä¢ Custom Post Designs: Pick from a variety of eye-catching styles to showcase your content ‚Ä¢ Simple Customization: Font, color, music and other options to help you craft the perfect engaging post ‚Ä¢ Streamlined Sharing: Just one click to share your post on Facebook, Twitter and Instagram ‚Ä¢ Engagement Summary: Keep track of engagement on your posts - across all profiles - in one place ‚Ä¢ Multi-Photo Animations: Use up to 4 photos in animated collages and slideshows Upgrade to Ripl PRO to use these exclusive features: ‚Ä¢ PRO Design Catalog: Unlimited access to dozens of animated designs, with new designs added every week! ‚Ä¢ Custom Logo: Remove the Ripl logo from your posts or replace it with your own logo or watermark ‚Ä¢ PRO Music Library: Choose from dozens of tracks for your posts, with everything from inspirational piano to pulsing workout beats ‚Ä¢ Scheduled Posts: Make posts in advance and schedule them for the best time to reach your audience ‚Ä¢ Save to Camera Roll: The flexibility to do more with what you create in Ripl Ripl PRO is an optional subscription that renews automatically on a monthly basis for a price of $9.99/month*. Try it FREE for 7 days! *Prices vary outside the United States ---Subscription Details--- Payment for Ripl PRO will be charged to your iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase. Your Ripl PRO subscription will automatically renew unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. You can manage your Ripl PRO subscription or turn off auto-renew in your iTunes Account Settings after purchase. No cancellation of a subscription is allowed during the current active subscription period. Privacy Policy: bit.ly/RiplPrivacy Terms of Use: bit.ly/RiplTerms', u'title': u'Ripl - Create Animated Posts for Facebook, Instagram & Twitter'}, {u'description': u'An app to easily create eye-catching posts that help you or your business stand out on social media.', u'title': u'Ripl - Custom Animated Posts for Social Media'}]

text_content: [{u'description': u'Meet awesome people with your friends, over complimentary drinks. The 1st round of drinks is always on us! See why Fox, BuzzFeed, and The Boston Globe have called Cheers different from other apps. 1. Make a group with 1-2 friends and check out all the other groups of friends going out in your city. 2. Tap Cheers for people you‚Äôd want to grab drinks with - get a match when interest is mutual. 3. Select ‚ÄúPick A Place‚Äù right in the conversation to meet up for drinks together. 4. Your concierge will leave a reservation and a round of complimentary drinks under your name. Cheers! Make tonight memorable. Questions, feedback, support? Let us know! concierge@getcheers.co If you like the app, leave a quick review! It means a lot. Privacy: We never, ever post to you or your friends' Facebook. Period.', u'title': u'Cheers - Drinks With Friends.'}]

tagline: FaceTime meets livestreaming
text_content: [{u'description': u'Get up close and personal with your favorite broadcasters. Watch your favorite broadcasters when they stream live on Flurry. See everything as it happens. Chat with broadcasters and people from around the world using emojis and stickers. Features: ‚Ä¢ Explore and discover new, talented broadcasters. ‚Ä¢ Enjoy high quality live video streaming. ‚Ä¢ Send instant messages to your favorite broadcasters. ‚Ä¢ Chat using emojis and stickers. ‚Ä¢ Purchase gifts for your favorite broadcasters! Gifts include heart-shaped balloons and party confetti. ‚Ä¢ Join your favorite broadcaster on screen. ‚Ä¢ Receive push notifications to ensure you don‚Äôt miss your favorite broadcasters. ‚Ä¢ Invite your friends from social networks to Flurry events. Access Flurry from your iPhone (5S, 5, 5C, 6, 6 Plus, 6S, 6S Plus) or iPod Touch (6th generation). Flurry is coming soon for other platforms. Stay tuned. Note video quality and voice quality vary depending on internet connection speed, location, signal strength and other factors. Got questions or suggestions? Email us at support@flurrylive.com. text_content: [{u'description': u'BucketListly is the ultimate bucket list community app that helps you unlock achievements in real life and share your travel stories and experiences among travelers. Snap a photo of you achieving your dreams, write how you did it and share your story on Facebook, Twitter and Foursquare with one click. With BucketListly you can: ‚Ä¢ Keep track of your dreams with an online bucket list you can access any where in the world. ‚Ä¢ Accumulate your life experiences into one page that is accessible on your phone and your computer. ‚Ä¢ Share your life accomplishments on all your social networks in an instant ‚Ä¢ Get endless inspiration from other travelers and great appreciation from other traveler's who find your stories fascinating. ‚Ä¢ Collaborate with one another to achieve an even bigger life goals.', u'title': u'BucketListly'}, {u'description': u'BucketListly is the most beautiful and advanced bucket list you will ever have', u'title': u'The Most Beautiful & Advanced Bucket List App ‚Äî BucketListly'}]

tagline: Clear music and sound customized by your hearing profile
text_content: [{u'description': u'Listen to music with more clarity, instruments, more you. Create your earprint, adapt your favourite music (Spotify, Soundcloud or iTunes) and enjoy sound the way you were meant to hear. As featured in: Forbes | Huffington Post I TechCrunch I Psychology Today I WIRED Because the best music experience is a personal one. Clear, rich and full sound based on how you hear. Mimi is the way you were meant to listen to music. --------------------- Use Mimi to: --------------------- Listen with more clarity, hear more nuances and details Hear music come alive, especially in the airplane or in the subway Rediscover your love for music, especially when you have hearing difficulties Turn the volume down and enjoy healthy listening --------------------- What does Mimi do to music? --------------------- Mimi Music is inspired by the way the human ear works. By creating your earprint, you can hear your music like you are meant to hear it. We have developed a unique patent pending technology that fundamentally changes the way you listen based on extensive R&D. The way you listen to music is determined by several factors. How music is recorded and processed into a digital format combined with the hardware you use to listen to your music are some of the obvious things. However, your very own ear plays a big part. Your earprint determines how you listen to the world, how the world and music sounds for you. Everybody listens differently - create your unique earprint now and unlock your music. --------------------- What does Mimi do for you? --------------------- Mimi gives you the power to truly hear your music the way you prefer. Mimi takes an earprint using our CE medically certified test technology (based on the #1 Hearing Test in the App Store) to unlock your music. Once you have your earprint, you can adjust your music to the way you were meant to hear it - at its best. Everybody, including you, hears differently, therefore we‚Äôve considered all hearing abilities in the engineering of Mimi Music. Mimi Music is built to suit your range of needs, leaving it completely up to you to decide how much depth and clarity you want. --------------------- Healthy listening --------------------- With Mimi your music not only sounds better, but it‚Äôs also kinder to your ears. Why? You‚Äôll be able to turn the volume lower while listening to Mimi - notice it will appear just as loud. When you mimify your sound, you‚Äôre adding quality and loudness without being destructive to your ears. It‚Äôs still up to you to keep it at a safe listening level, but you won‚Äôt be needing full-blasted volume to get the most of your music anymore. --------------------- What our users say --------------------- A MUST HAVE IN MY DAY TO DAY LIFE! 5* - LouieGaga - 12/02/2016 ‚ÄúThis app is absolutely breathtaking. The quality of my hearing went to hell due to me blasting music in my ears 24/7, but with Mimi Music I got the quality I once loved back! Thank you so much! Please make sure Mimi Music is available FOREVER!‚Äù Fantastic 5* - itsjaaasperre - 21/02/2016 ‚ÄúThis app makes everything sounds a thousand times better than it did, I'm very pleased. 10/10 would recommend.‚Äù Makes my cheap ear buds sound great! 5* - Micmko - 07/12/2015 ‚ÄúI don't know how they do it, but the dynamic range that Mimi delivers is super.‚Äù **Say hello to us** We are always excited to hear from our users. Get in touch with us if you have questions, stories, ideas or concerns to hello@mimi.io **Do you want to hear more from Mimi?** Check our blog: http://www.mimi.io/blog/ Twitter: https://twitter.com/mimihearing Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/mimihearing', u'title': u'Mimi Music - clear sound unlocked by your earprint'}, {u'description': None, u'title': u'Mimi | sounds like youMimi | sounds like youmimi'}]

tagline: Help stop sex trafficking by uploading photos of your hotel
text_content: [{u'description': u'TraffickCam enables you to help combat sex trafficking by uploading photos of the hotel rooms you stay in when you travel. Traffickers regularly post photographs of their victims posed in hotel rooms for online advertisements. These photographs are evidence that can be used to find and prosecute the perpetrators of these crimes. In order to use these photos, however, investigators must be able to determine where the photos were taken. The purpose of TraffickCam is to create a database of hotel room images that an investigator can efficiently search, in order to find other images that were taken in the same location as an image that is part of an investigation.', u'title': u'TraffickCam'}, {u'description': None, u'title': u'TraffickCam | Web AppThreeDubMedia ¬∑ jquery.event.drop'}]

tagline: Cleans and organises your files in Mac desktop automatically
text_content: [{u'description': u'*** 80 % OFF FOR A LIMITED TIME *** Declutter is an solution to a problem that every Mac user faces - Desktop Clutter. Declutter helps you to create intelligent folders with rules based on file names and extensions so that it can automatically move the files to respective folders on desktop and keep the desktop clean always. Major Features Beautiful Desktop We all love when we buy our new Mac. It is the face of the device. Declutter helps you to keep it that way and even makes it more beautiful. Intelligent Folders Declutters helps you to create beautiful and intelligent folders in your desktop. Each folder is configured with rules so that the desktop is cleaned based on them. File Name or Extension Rules The rules for intelligent folders in desktop can be created based on both file names or file extensions so that the clean up can be comprehensive and at the same time granular. Complex Rules The rules can be configured with multiple file name or file extension conditions. This enables the app to declutter the desktop with accuracy like human intelligence. Folder Colors and Icons Declutter app enables you to add beautiful colours and icons to the intelligent folders that you create to make the already clean desktop more beautiful. Automatic Declutter Declutter app enables you to configure automatic clean up for the timing configured to ensure that the desktop is always clean. Instant Reach Declutter app is available in menubar always if you enable it to launch on start and can be activated in a single click or configured hot key stroke. Launch on Start You can configure the Declutter app to launch on start so that the app is launched silently and keeps the desktop clean automatically. WE ARE JUST A CLICK AWAY If you have questions about the app or face an issue while installing, configuring, updating or using the app please send us an email at support@macappstudio.com.We usually respond within minutes of receiving the issue report. Almost all of the issues that are reported are resolved in the same day. We have no way of contacting you or resolving the issue you are facing if you post an issue as a review.', u'title': u'Declutter on the Mac App Store'}]

tagline: Your travel experiences in one neat place
text_content:
[{u'body': u' Prava travel app is part of Essential Summer Travel Apps 2016 by Mashable!
Travel with friends and family is fun but clunky - you have to juggle different tools / apps before the trip, during the trip and after the trip. Need an easier way? Say hello to Prava. Keep all of your group's trip plans, details, photos, expenses and experiences in one simple place.With the free Prava travel app, it's easy to:‚Ä¢ PLAN THE TRIP - Create your trip group, chat and build the travel itinerary (agenda).‚Ä¢ MAKE THE TRIP - Capture and instantly share travel photos, expenses, locations and notes (blog) of the travel with your trip group.‚Ä¢ PUBLISH THE TRIP - Publish the shared travel photos and travel notes (blog) together as a group to your contacts and other Prava users. Let them get inspired and connect with you. The trip itinerary, expenses, chat, locations and private photos remain private within the group. You can choose not to publish the trip as well :)‚Ä¢ EXPLORE TRIPS - Discover trips published by your contacts and other Prava users, connect with them, get inspired and plan your next travel.Prava frees you from juggling multiple tools for group travel such as chat app, to-do app / notepad, expense app / bills, various social media for photos and blogs - and having to go back to them again for memories. Plus, Prava is the world's first group travel app which is also a social media for publishing and exploring trips.Get the iPhone companion app at - https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/prava-group-travel-made-easy/id1099762609MORE REASONS TO USE PRAVA:‚Ä¢ AD FREE - Free travel app, No ads.‚Ä¢ FUN TO USE - Google Material Design Framework UI.‚Ä¢ CREATE OFFLINE - No Internet? No problem! Prava is your travel app which can be used without the need for an Internet connection, and all shared items you create will be instantly synchronized with your trip group as and when you are connected to the Internet. Plus, already shared data within the trip group like chat, itinerary, photos and expenses are also available for offline access.‚Ä¢ AMAZING CONTROLS FOR PRIVACY AND SHARING - Want to keep all aspects of the trip to yourself? Sure! Need to record an expense just for you? Done! Want to share some photos with your trip group or publish them to all Prava users? Easy as 123! Download Prava travel app now to explore the amazing privacy and sharing features!‚Ä¢ WORKS WITH YOUR PHONE NUMBER - Why bother having to remember yet another username and password? Prava works with your phone number and integrates seamlessly with your phone‚Äôs existing address book. ‚Ä¢ QUICKLY CONNECT WITH YOUR CONTACTS - You always travel with your contacts, right? So, your address book is used to quickly and easily connect you with your contacts who have Prava so there‚Äôs no need to add hard-to-remember usernames / IDs / handles.‚Ä¢ ALWAYS LOGGED IN - With Prava, you‚Äôre always logged in so you don‚Äôt miss what is shared by your trip group. No more confusion about whether you‚Äôre logged in or logged out. ‚Ä¢ ALL YOUR TRIPS IN ONE PLACE - Secure storage on cloud. tagline: Your restaurant decider
text_content: [{u'description': u'You know the trusted friends you turn to when you need a reliable restaurant suggestion? In our circle, that's us...and we don't disappoint. The Infatuation (formerly known as Immaculate Infatuation) has become one of the country's most trusted resources for honest, relatable perspective on restaurants. Now it's even easier to find the ideal spot that's ‚ÄúPerfect For:‚Äù Date Night, Girls' Night Out, Dinner With The Parents, and much more. This app makes searching through The Infatuation‚Äôs vast database of carefully curated reviews both easy and enjoyable. This is the restaurant guide that you've been looking for. ‚ÄúApps for finding restaurants are plentiful, but most of them leave me feeling overwhelmed. I want someone to choose for me, and I trust the authors of this app to do that. Their taste has never led me astray.‚Äù - Joshua Brustein, The New York Times FEATURES: ‚Ä¢NEARBY: Find nearby restaurants around your current location, while also moving the map to see restaurants anywhere and everywhere. ‚Ä¢SEARCH: Browse and combine from four different search categories to find the restaurant that best suits your needs. Categories include: Perfect For (example filters: Girls‚Äô Night Out, Late Night Eats, Outdoor/Patio Situation), Cuisine, Neighborhood and more. ‚Ä¢HIT LIST: Now it‚Äôs easy to keep track of your favorite restaurants and the ones that you have been dying to try. ‚ÄúHit List‚Äù any of our reviews on the app and it‚Äôll keep a running list of your favorite and future targets. Hit Listed restaurants will also show up in red on the Nearby map.', u'title': u'The Infatuation: Restaurant Reviews for New York, Los Angeles, San Francisco & Chicago'}]
