tagline: Control Apple TV from your mobile device or Mac.
text_content:
[{u'description': u'Looking for Apple TV remote replacement? Lost native remote? CiderTV is just for you. CiderTV is a bluetooth remote control for 2nd, 3rd and 4th generation Apple TV. Control your Apple TV right from your Mac. The app lets to navigate between menus right from your Mac. Main controls: Arrow left = Move to the left Arrow right = Move to the right Arrow up = Move up Arrow down = Move down Enter = Select Esc = Menu Hotkeys: Option + Arrow up = Select previous device Option + Arrow down = Select next device Option + Shift + Tab = Hide/Unhide CiderTV window To start, just follow easy setup instructions or visit https://cidertv.com/osx for more details. Follow @CiderTV in twitter for latest news and updates. Help us to create the best remote for watching Apple TV with your feedback!', u'title': u'CiderTV on the Mac App Store'}, {u'body': u' The app is the best alternative for an Apple TV control on Android market.Looking for native Apple TV remote alternative? Check out CiderTV - free app to control 2nd, 3rd and 4th gen Apple TV from your Android phone or tab. Works with non-jailbroken Apple TV 2G up. The app is especially handy in emergency situations (original remote is often lost or broken, empty batteries, etc). Handy built-in keyboard lets you to type texts (ex, movie titles) and rapidly send them to your Apple TV screen. CiderTV requires active WiFi connection, Android OS v. 4.0.3 and above. Native Apple TV remote is NEEDED but only for initial app setup. If you DO NOT HAVE APPLE TV REMOTE right now - any other remote controls (including apps) paired with your Apple TV before will be good for CiderTV setup as well. Not a solution for you? Visit our FAQ inside the app to learn more alternative waysUniversal remote app.Unlike other universal IR remote controls, Cider TV works via WiFi, so it is compatible with many Android devices and availbale even for the devices without built-in Infrared blaster (receiver). You can easily navigate Apple TV menus and watch favorite movies using CiderTV even from phone and with no infrared support (ex. Google Nexus, Sony Xperia, Motorola Droid, OnePlus, Xiaomi, Huawei, some Samsung Galaxy phones, Meizu, Lenovo, ASUS ZenFone etc). No need to jailbreak Apple TV.No matter how many Apple TVs do you have - with Cider TV app you can control all your 2G, 3G, 4G AppleTV devices from one screen.  Easy to Set Up. Pleasant to Use.CiderTV is super simple, pairs in seconds and is absolutely FREE to use. Pairing is needed only for first step. No full screen ads, no push notification ads or any other pop-up ads! No additional hardware needed. We peel all the superfluous features of other universal remote analogues from the app to create best smart AppleTV remote for your Android device.Find something good to watchCiderTV Wi-Fi remote app comes with handy built-in keyboard. It lets you to send texts to your Apple TV screen, rapidly type login and password on it from your phone and tablet.Our smart remote comes with intuitive gesture navigation so you can search for best TV shows, photos, music, games and movie episodes on your Apple TV in seconds. Please note that the app doesn`t support AirPlay, so you can't use CiderTV to stream, cast or share content from your Android device to your Apple TV via Air Play.  Here are some basic gestures to control:- TAP to Select (Play/Pause)
- DOUBLE-TAP to go back
- LONG-TAP (press for a second) - go back to Home Screen
- SWIPE LEFT/RIGHT/UP/DOWN - move between menu items
- SWIPE LEFT/RIGHT - rewind video or fast-forward. Further swipes will increase rewind/fast-forward speedHate juggling between remotes? Always losing your TV remote?CiderTV app saves you from this pain. Cider TV is the only remote for AppleTV that can also control your TV volume (via IP)! No need to change between remotes. Navigate menus, enjoy watching favorite movies and adjust your IP-enabled TV volume with all-in-one elegant solution. Almost all modern smart TVs support DLNA volume control from the box. Important note: CiderTV guarantees your Sony and LG Smart TVs volume control support. More TVs support (i.e. Samsung) is coming soonHelp and Support is Close ByVisit http://cidertv.com/faq for FAQ, contact us in online support chat inside the app or drop an email support@cidertv.com.Follow us on Twitter https://twitter.com/CiderTV for latest updates (and help us to create the best remote with your feedback).   ', u'description': u'Control & keyboard for 2, 3, 4 gen Apple TV via WiFi + TV volume. No jailbreak', u'title': u'Remote for Apple TV - CiderTV - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': u'This app is the best remote for your Apple TV! It perfectly works with non-jailbroken Apple TVs (2nd, 3rd and 4th generation), letting you to control the box like with Apple remote, use its apps and adjust linked Smart TV volume from same screen. Super simple setup, intuitive navigation, online support. The same as on screenshots. Enjoy! Twice featured on iDownloadBlog and Macsources. Always losing your remote? That‚Äôs where CiderTV app comes to the rescue. Control your box from iOS device with ease. This app needs native remote (only for 1st setup), but even if you do not have it, any other remotes (including apps), paired for use with your Apple TV before will work as well. And once you pair CiderTV next time you'll be safe. Want a solution right now? There are other options on how you can set up CiderTV without the Remote. For more information please visit our FAQ inside the app or ask support via in-app chat. Still feeling like you are out of luck? Well, you can always order a new remote. And link it to CiderTV once it arrives. This way, if you happen to lose your remote a second time, you won‚Äôt be in any hurry to order another one. With CiderTV remote app you can: - easily navigate menus with gestures, - watch movies, songs or TV programs running on your Apple TV, - find favorite photos, videos, apps and other content, - quickly send text queries for your Apple TV with built-in keyboard, - change linked Smart TV volume from same screen. And since CiderTV v2.0 and above you can control your box from Notification Center Widget that will boost your watching experience! Play/Pause, Navigation and the long-awaited Menu button. Easy and quick. Please note: to control Apple TV box from widget you need to pair it from the CiderTV app first and then add CiderTV widget to your Notification Center. Hate juggling between remotes? Always losing your remote? CiderTV app saves you from this pain. No more need to switch between several remotes with this all-in-one elegant solution. Remote control + built-in keyboard for use with Apple TV + Smart TV volume control (over IP/DLNA). The app is especially handy in emergency situations (original remote is lost or broken, empty batteries, etc). And it just works! Tired of slow and buggy remote alternatives? You will love CiderTV intuitive navigation from the first touch. Here are some basic gestures to control: - TAP to Select (Play/Pause) - DOUBLE-TAP to go back - LONG-TAP (press for a second) - go back to Home Screen - SWIPE LEFT/RIGHT/UP/DOWN - move between menu items - SWIPE LEFT/RIGHT - rewind or fast-forward. Further swipes will increase rewind/fast-forward speed *** The app is FREE for use with your Apple TV. You do not need to pay anything if you have only 1 device *** If you like CiderTV or have any questions - DM @CiderTV in Twitter or email us at support@cidertv.com', u'title': u'CiderTV: the new remote app for ATV control & Smart TV volume on iOS'}]

tagline: Connect with people who share your interests
text_content:
[{u'description': u'Welcome to the hello network. Discover the hello app and: - connect with people who share your passions - immerse yourself in content relevant to your interests - express yourself and create connections Join hello and become part of something special. Download now to explore hello. Hello Network, Inc. was founded by well-known social pioneer Orkut Buyukkokten (creator of orkut.com) and a small group of ex-Google engineers. After witnessing the evolution of social networking over the past 16 years, Orkut was inspired to help bring people together around their common interests -- a vision that changes how the world does social. Why hello? - hello is a new kind of social network - express what you‚Äôre passionate about - connect with people who share your interests - discover content you care about - be yourself and have fun! - express your passions and explore new ones - choose from 100+ personas that reflect your true self - discover different personas; you may even uncover a new passion - as your interests evolve over time, hello grows with you - immerse yourself in content relevant to your interests - explore your folio to discover your communities - contribute content aligned with your interests - earn reputation within your personas and attain status - connect with people who share similar passions - the hello community is brimming with folks who share common interests. invite your friends or make new ones! - reach out to an audience who understands you - embrace a new community and meet new people. hello helps you break the ice with assisted introductions - experience the fun of games in a social network - express yourself, build your reputation, and climb up the leaderboard - interact with the community to unlock achievements, reach milestones and earn rewards - compete with your friends and reach levels of new heights To find out more, check out hello.com', u'title': u'hello.com'}, {u'description': None, u'title': u'hello network'}, {u'body': u' Welcome to the hello network.
Discover the hello app and: 
- connect with people who share your passions
- immerse yourself in content relevant to your interests 
- express yourself and create connections
Join hello and become part of something special.
Download now to explore hello.Hello Network, Inc. was founded by well-known social pioneer Orkut Buyukkokten (creator of orkut.com) and a small group of ex-Google engineers. After witnessing the evolution of social networking over the past 16 years, Orkut was inspired to help bring people together around their common interests -- a vision that changes how the world does social.Why hello?
- hello is a new kind of social network
- express what you‚Äôre passionate about
- connect with people who share your interests
- discover content you care about
- be yourself and have fun!
- express your passions and explore new ones
- choose from 100+ personas that reflect your true self
- discover different personas; you may even uncover a new passion
- as your interests evolve over time, hello grows with you
- immerse yourself in content relevant to your interests
- explore your folio to discover your communities
- contribute content aligned with your interests
- earn reputation within your personas and attain status
- connect with people who share similar passions
- the hello community is brimming with folks who share common interests. invite your friends or make new ones!
- reach out to an audience who understands you
- embrace a new community and meet new people. hello helps you break the ice with assisted introductions
- experience the fun of games in a social network
- express yourself, build your reputation, and climb up the leaderboard
- interact with the community to unlock achievements, reach milestones and earn rewards
- compete with your friends and reach levels of new heightsTo find out more, check out hello.comNote: hello is only available for devices running Android 5.0 (Lollipop) and later.   ', u'description': u'hello.com, a new social network', u'title': u'hello.com - Android Apps on Google Play'}]

text_content: [{u'description': u'Doozyrama is a simple way to create and share awesome places. Express yourself by sharing created or visited places, and follow your friends to see what they‚Äôre up to. Use Doozyrama to: ‚Ä¢ ERASE THE FOG to find out where you‚Äôve been. By the way, the most interesting stuff is usually beyond the fog, so keep going! ‚Ä¢ CREATE awesome PLACES and share what you find. ‚Ä¢ DESCRIBE places with EMOJI. You know, each place is not just about the food we eat or the beverages we drink, the most important part are the emotions it brings! ‚Ä¢ CHECK-IN to new places to share with your friends where you are and what you‚Äôre up to. ‚Ä¢ stay up to date with ACTIVITIES NEARBY. ‚Ä¢ ADD FRIENDS to see what they‚Äôre up to. ‚Ä¢ MEET other PEOPLE who are sharing places you‚Äôll love. ‚Ä¢ easily KEEP TRACK of all places you‚Äôve been to. ‚Ä¢ EARN POINTS, COMPETE with friends and other users to get the Crown. ‚Ä¢ ACHIEVE built-in goals and UNLOCK HEROES to show how awesome you are! Questions? We respond to every inquiry. Please contact us: support@doozyrama.com *Continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life.', u'title': u'Doozyrama - Places, Check-ins, Emoji on the Map'}, {u'description': None, u'title': u' Doozyrama '}]

tagline: Use your voice to power freedom of expression
text_content: [{u'description': u'Voizd is your anonymous and fun Audio messaging board. Post your secret thoughts, hidden opinions, and confessions or just share your feelings without being judged, labeled or trolled. Listen to secret thoughts and opinions of other people near you. Connect with like-minded people...Give and receive support. **** No Signup Required **** What is Voizd? Voizd is an anonymous social space where you can freely express every opinion & thoughts in your own voice without the fear of ever been recognized, judged or labeled. Listen to what others really think about various topics (when they know they won‚Äôt be judged) and connect with like-minded people. Have a question? Post it to the vibrant community and get their unbiased advice and support. Highlights: ‚Ä¢ Express yourself in your own voice, while your identity remains hidden. ‚Ä¢ Voice morphing feature to make your voice & you completely Anonymous. ‚Ä¢ Listen to real Voizd opinions & secret thoughts of people near you & from around the world. ‚Ä¢ Browse and listen to Voizd opinions based on # trending topics. ‚Ä¢ Respond to other people Voizd opinions using comments & array of emoticons ( emoji) like Hugs, LOL, Hi5, luvit, Angry, OMG. ‚Ä¢ Connect with like-minded people from near you and around the world ‚Ä¢ It‚Äôs like listening to local ham radio of secret thoughts and whispers ‚Ä¢ Also share voice / audio expressions, thoughts onto instant messengers like Whatsapp , iMessage, Twitter, Facebook and G plus for free If you require further help, send us an email on Support@voizd.com', u'title': u'VOIZD ‚Äì Voice without fear'}]

tagline: Connecting people through sports
text_content: [{u'description': u'Bvddy, is your ultimate tool to discover new friends that play the sports you love. We are the world's first smart-matching app that connects you to sports partners at your level and in your area. We match, you play! From tennis buddies, to running buddies, to yoga buddies, to gym buddies... we've got you covered. Just download the app and get swiping. With Bvddy you can: ‚Ä¢ Seamlessly connect with buddies near you. ‚Ä¢ Get matched with people your same level. ‚Ä¢ Create and manage your own sporting events. ‚Ä¢ Discover venues near you, from yoga studios to soccer fields. ‚Ä¢ Chat with your matches to coordinate your game. ‚Ä¢ Review your matches. Join the Bvddy and start connecting with people through sports.', u'title': u'Bvddy: Connecting people through sports'}]

text_content:
[{u'body': u' Kittens and Cats are now your video ringtone! Yes, this is ‚Äúfurreal‚Äù, cat videos for every incoming call, life will never be the same. Don't worry cats will make it better.Don't want to reject a call, cause the person will know you sent them to Voice Mail?

text_content: [{u'description': u'Freshsales is a refreshingly new CRM that is packed with features to boost your sales team's productivity.', u'title': u'Freshsales | The CRM for High Velocity Sales Teams'}, {u'description': u'The Freshsales mobile app for iOS makes it easy for you to access your customer data and track your sales pipeline, while on the go. You can add leads, contacts, accounts and deals, make phone calls, send emails and change deal stages even when you are away from your desk. The changes are automatically synced with your Freshsales web app so your customer data is always up-to-date. Freshsales is an online customer relationship management software with built-in phone and email, event tracking, lead scoring, automations and more.', u'title': u'Freshsales'}, {u'body': u' The Freshsales mobile app for Android makes it easy for you to access your customer data and track your sales pipeline, while on the go. You can add leads, contacts, accounts and deals, make phone calls, send emails and change deal stages even when you are away from your desk. The changes are automatically synced with your Freshsales web app so your customer data is always up-to-date. Freshsales is an online customer relationship management software with built-in phone and email, event tracking, lead scoring, automations and more. tagline: Use 3D Touch to open up apps
text_content: [{u'description': u'Save space in your dock by using Shortcuts Shortcuts uses 3D Touch to directly open up your favorite apps. Set up the apps of your choice once and then 3D Touch away! This app works best for apps which have 3D Touch: iPhone 6s and iPhone 6s+ Currently featuring shortcuts to: - Calendar - iBooks - Mail - Maps - Music - Apple News - Phone (choose a contact to quick call) - Reminders - Safari - Settings - Wallet (Premium content) - Alien Blue - Amazon - Amazon Music - Around - Box - Candy Crush - Candy Crush Soda Saga - Capital One - CityMapper - Cloud Magic - Dropbox - Evernote - Facebook - Facebook Messenger - Fitbit - Flipboard - Google - Google Calendar - Google Chrome - Google Drive - Google Gmail - Google Hangouts - Google Inbox - Google Maps - Google Photos - GroupMe - IMDb - Instagram - iTranslate - KakaoTalk - Line - LinkedIn - LinkedIn Sales Navigator - Lyft - Netflix - Outlook - Pinterest - Shazam - Slack - Sleipnir - Snapchat - Spotify - Square Cash - Textwell - Transit - Tumblr - Twitter - Uber - Venmo - Vine - Waze - WeChat - Weibo - WhatsApp - Yahoo Finance - Yahoo Weather - Yelp - Youtube', u'title': u'ShortcutsFree - Dock Saver'}, {u'description': u'Shortcuts is an iOS Application built by Andrew Fang.', u'title': u'Shortcuts by Andrew Fang'}]

tagline: Meditation for people who never have time
text_content: [{u'description': u'Simple Habit is the best meditation app for your busy life. It's just 5 minutes a day, on topics that matter to you. Reduce stress, improve sleep, boost focus and memory, and improve well-being. Download now and get our signature 7 day meditation series for free. Simple Habit meditations are designed by a Harvard psychologist and guided by the world's best teachers that we've personally invited - from mindfulness teachers at Google to young former monks to authors to veterans. Meet them all in one place, on Simple Habit. *** Featured #1 in "New Apps We Love‚Äù in May 2016 *** Featured #1 in "Health & Fitness - Meditation & Mindfulness" in May 2016 Got any questions or feedback? Reach out to us at feedback@simplehabitapp.com. Thanks for using Simple Habit :) Unlimited Premium Subscription Simple Habit offers three auto-renewing subscription options: $3.99/week, $14.99/month and $119.99/year. These prices are for United States customers. Pricing in other countries may vary and actual charges may be converted to your local currency depending on the country of residence. Your subscription will automatically renew at the end of each term and your credit card will be charged through your iTunes account. You can turn off auto-renew at any time from your iTunes account settings but refunds will not be provided for any unused portion of the term. Privacy policy - http://www.simplehabitapp.com/#!privacy-policy/cwhpq Terms and conditions - http://www.simplehabitapp.com/#!terms-of-service/qg84k', u'title': u'Simple Habit - Medit¬≠ation on the go'}]

tagline: Livestreaming platform for mobile gamers
text_content:
[{u'body': u' Mobcrush is a community for streaming games, watching tournaments and connecting with other gamers that love the same games you do. You can start streaming your screen, camera and microphone with just a touch, right on your phone.  Note: Officially supported Android devices include: the Nexus 5 & 6, and the Samsung Galaxy S6, S6 Edge, and S6 Edge+. We encourage you to try using Mobcrush with other devices, we'll be supporting more in the future. Viewing content is supported on most devices with Android 4.1+. Your favorite creators, eSports players and developers play and stream on Mobcrush. Watch exclusive streams from ESL, Toucharcade, iHasCupquake, sssniperwolf, JackFrostMiner, RumblySuperset, Bigbst4tz2, AviatorGaming, TeamEpiphany, nickatnyte, and MonsterDroiid. Plus, easily stream games like Minecraft: Pocket Edition, Vainglory, Clash Royale, C-Ops and Hearthstone to a welcoming community.Features: + Broadcast your live gameplay directly from your Android phone
+ Start streaming, build your fanbase and connect with fellow gamers 
+ Watch exclusive tournaments and events in real-time
+ Follow your favorite broadcasters and never miss a broadcast
+ Discover new and exciting games to play and stream Having problems or have suggestions to make Mobcrush better? 
Use the help section of the app or visit mobcrush.com/support and we‚Äôll get right back to you. Add us on Snapchat: 
mobcrushFollow us on Instagram: 
instagram.com/mobcrushFind us on Facebook: 
facebook.com/mobcrushFollow us on Twitter: 
twitter.com/mobcrushThanks for your support!   ', u'description': u'Watch and create gaming live-streams from your phone, and chat with other gamers', u'title': u'Mobcrush - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': u'Mobcrush is a new community for streaming games, watching tournaments and connecting with other gamers. Streaming has never been easier, download the companion app for Mac and start broadcasting from your iPhone or iPad with just one click. Note: In order to broadcast, you must use the Mobcrush companion app for Mac, available in the Mac App Store. Your favorite creators, eSports players and developers play and stream on Mobcrush. Watch exclusive live broadcasts from ESL, Toucharcade, iHasCupquake, sssniperwolf, JackFrostMiner, RumblySuperset, Bigbst4tz2, AviatorGaming, TeamEpiphany, nickatnyte, and MonsterDroiid. Plus, you can easily stream games like Minecraft: Pocket Edition, Vainglory, Clash Royale, C-Ops and Hearthstone to a welcoming community. Features: + Broadcast live gameplay from your iPhone or iPad with the Mobcrush companion app for Mac or Windows (Alpha) + Start streaming, build your fanbase and chat with friends + Watch exclusive tournaments and events in real-time + Follow your favorite broadcasters and never miss a broadcast + Discover new and exciting games to play and stream Having problems or have suggestions to make Mobcrush better? Use the help section of the app or visit mobcrush.com/support and we‚Äôll get right back to you. Add us on Snapchat: mobcrush Follow us on Instagram: instagram.com/mobcrush Find us on Facebook: facebook.com/mobcrush Follow us on Twitter: twitter.com/mobcrush', u'title': u'Mobcrush'}]

text_content: [{u'description': u'', u'title': u'FeatherApp.co - Home'}, {u'description': u'Feather allows you to control all of your Nest devices from your Apple TV. With support for the Nest Thermostat, Nest Camera, and Nest Protect you can control and monitor your home from the comfort of your couch. Thermostat - View current inside temperature - Set target temperature - View outdoor temperature - View outdoor weather - Set heating mode - Set Home/Away Camera - View streaming snapshots of your camera (10 per minute with Nest Aware subscription or 2 per minute without) - View camera status - View most recent action (GIF) Protect - View Smoke status - View CO status - View last test and other data fields Other Features - Alerts callout issues with your home - Swipe access locks on thermostat to limit family access - Swipe access locks on camera to prevent unauthorized viewing - Nest access encrypted at all points', u'title': u'Feather - Control your Nest'}]

tagline: Rapid design and prototyping for the iPhone and iPad
text_content: [{u'description': u'Just had the next billion-dollar app idea? Grab a pen and within minutes your idea will come to life. Marvel lets you design apps on your iPhone or iPad! Turn sketches, mockups and wireframes into interactive, tappable app prototypes that allow you to demo your ideas and share with others. Play with your app ideas on the iPhone, iPad and Apple Watch! It‚Äôs super simple to get started, all you need is an idea and some pen and paper. How it works: - Draw your app screens on paper, then take photos or add mockups from Dropbox/Creative Cloud (including Photoshop files!). You can even draw directly on the screen! - Link each screen together using touch areas to form your app demo‚Ä¶then press play! - Ready to show the world? You can share prototypes using Email, SMS or Twitter and send to any phone or desktop. Everything is synced to your Marvel web account too, so you always have access to your prototypes no matter where you are.', u'title': u'Marvel - Design Apps On Your Phone'}, {u'description': u'Turn sketches, mockups and designs into web, iPhone, iOS, Android and Apple Watch app prototypes.', u'title': u'Free mobile & web prototyping (iOS, Android) for designers ‚Äì Marvel'}]

tagline: Turn Gmail into a smart CRM
text_content: [{u'description': u'NetHunt CRM - your smart inbox for Gmail to automate business processes around email handling. It is a full-featured CRM solution inside Gmail and Google Apps.', u'title': u'NetHunt CRM, your smart Inbox (Gmail sales CRM)'}, {u'description': u'NetHunt CRM is a CRM system for Gmail and Google Apps. Start using NetHunt smart inbox and manage your CRM data on the go. It‚Äôs a comprehensive CRM system that enhances the functionality and possibilities of Google Apps ecosystem. NetHunt CRM allows you to create and manage sales pipelines, organize support service, carry out hiring or marketing campaigns and more. FEATURES * Turn your emails into CRM records. * Organize and manage your sales leads, marketing outreach or support cases into customizable Views. * Group and sort records by assignees, stages, deal size or what you currently need. * Color code your emails, Records, and Groups for faster navigation. * Set Follow-ups on emails and Records and turn them into a ToDo list. * Fast and full sync with the web version of NetHunt CRM. NOTE: NetHunt CRM for iPhone requires you to have an active NetHunt account. It can be created by installing the NetHunt CRM browser extension available from the official NetHunt CRM site (http://nethunt.com/) or Chrome Web Store (https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/nethunt-crm-for-gmail/kaeigipjcamcanmmhgpniimjagdleoee?hl=en).', u'title': u'NetHunt CRM'}, {u'description': None, u'title': u'NetHunt CRM for Gmail - Chrome Web Store'}]

tagline: Making conversations possible again
text_content:
[{u'body': u' Making conversations possible again through calls that are convenient, useful, and fun.
- No need to give out your phone number or email
- Pre-screen people via their social profiles
- Only take calls when you want - no more interruptions
- Calls are capped with a time limit (5 min by default) so you‚Äôll never be stuck on a long call again
- Publish your best calls to social media, or keep them private 
- All calls are free
Who is using SpareMin
- Comedians are using it to record and share micro-podcasts
- Podcasters are using it to do easy interviews
- Busy professionals are using it to clear their inboxes and calendars
- Investors are using it to help take pitches, without getting stuck on never ending sales calls
- Professors are using it to replace traditional office hours
- Pastors are using it to share knowledge amongst themselves and their congregations 
- Influencers are using it to host impromptu Q&A sessions with their fans
- Volunteers are serving students and communities in their spare time
- And more!
Why use SpareMin
- Too busy to keep in touch with your extended network? SpareMin allows you to take short calls without filling up your calendar
- Get asked for advice all the time? Talk when you‚Äôre free and share the recordings when a question comes up again 
- Have a podcast? Take calls from fans and your audience and incorporate them into your next episode 
- Want to volunteer your time to your community and network of people?  Just give people your handle and ‚Äúpay it forward‚Äù by sharing your time
Still thinking, ‚ÄúWhy can‚Äôt I just use xyz for this?‚Äù - If you don‚Äôt mind giving out your phone number, getting stuck on never-ending calls, constantly scheduling or texting back and forth, and feeling obligated to stay on the phone forever, go for it. But, times have changed and the phone call needed an update. 
We love getting feedback, so please don‚Äôt be shy. Send all questions or comments to feedback@sparemin.com, and someone from our team will be in touch.Requires a valid Facebook or LinkedIn account. tagline: Task manager with a unique data input system
text_content: [{u'description': u'Taskcode is a masterfully created task manager with a unique data input system. Unlike other reminder apps, where the user constantly have to tap from one option to another, Taskcode allows the easiest way of specifying all attributes of a reminder like due date, time, subtasks, title, repeat function etc. simply by typing. This allows for a much quicker and efficient way of inputting data. There are 6 simple codes, a user can use in combination to set reminders: ‚Äú ‚Äù for title # for due date @ for due time $ for repeat functionality % for subtasks * for color of a tile Preview 1: ‚ÄúOffice Task‚Äù Meeting with John & Julie #tomorrow @noon When you type the above and tap save, Taskcode automatically accepts due date as the next day and time as 12:00 pm, with title as ‚ÄòOffice task‚Äô - because # is used to specify due date, @ is used to specify due time and any character inside double quotes become the title of the tile. Preview 2: ‚ÄúBuy from Supermarket‚Äù %Milk %Sugar %Apples #010716 @0300p Here the task will be titled as ‚ÄòBuy from Supermarket‚Äô with subtask items listed as Milk, Sugar and Apples with the due date as 1st of July 2016 (010716), and time as 3:00 Pm (0300p). Preview 3: ‚ÄúTake Medicine‚Äù $daily @0800a This will remind you to take your medicine every day ($daily) in the morning at 08:00 am (@morning can also be used). Any text without these codes will be saved as a simple note. Detailed tutorial and walkthrough tutorial are available inside the app. Added Features include: ‚Ä¢ Auto suggestion for codes ‚Ä¢ Code & Color shortcut drawer ‚Ä¢ Dark theme & White theme ‚Ä¢ Snooze control ‚Ä¢ Multi-select for batch actions ‚Ä¢ Archiving of tiles and more Master these 6 simple codes and discover how logical and faster it is to input data.There are hundreds of apps available to enter data manually but you deserve something better. www.taskcodeapp.com hello@taskcodeapp.com', u'title': u'Taskcode - for tasks, subtasks & notes'}, {u'description': None, u'title': u'taskcode'}]

tagline: Manage email policies from your smartphone
text_content:
[{u'description': u'The Zoho Mail admin app is a native app for iOS and Android that lets administrators manage their company email accounts in just a few swipes.', u'title': u'Zoho Mail Admin Mobile App.'}, {u'body': u' The Zoho Mail Admin App is designed with a complete understanding of System Administrators like you. A classic Black and Red design reminiscent of the powerful system shell lets you manage all your admin tasks in just a few swipes. The App greets you with a lucid dashboard, showcasing upfront the total number of users and groups in your Mail account. Dig deeper, and you get to do all these:User Management: Add users, reset passwords and change user roles, all on the go
Group Management: Add members to a group, remove members from a group and change roles
Mail Moderation: Approve/reject emails that need moderation (for those few emails that are too urgent to wait for you to get to your computer)
Storage Management: You can add extra storage for a user using the "storage" addonNote: The App is intended for Administrators of Zoho Mail Organization. You would require an active Zoho Mail administrator account to use this app.   ', u'description': u'Manage users, groups, mail settings and moderate emails all from one App.', u'title': u'Zoho Mail Admin - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': u'The Zoho Mail Admin App is designed with a complete understanding of System Administrators like you. A classic Black and Red design reminiscent of the powerful system shell lets you manage all your admin tasks in just a few swipes. The App greets you with a lucid dashboard, showcasing upfront the total number of users and groups in your Mail account. Dig deeper, and you get to do all these: User Management: Add users, reset passwords and change user roles, all on the go Group Management: Add members to a group, remove members from a group and change roles Mail Moderation: Approve/reject emails that need moderation (for those few emails that are too urgent to wait for you to get to your computer) Storage Management: You can add extra storage for a user using the "storage" add-on Note: The App is intended for Administrators of Zoho Mail Organization. tagline: Monitor your key metrics, everywhere you go
text_content: [{u'body': u' A mobile dashboard that keeps all your key metrics in one place, everywhere you go.Stay up to date on trends, funnel conversion rates, and retention rates all in one app. All you need to do is login with your Mixpanel email address that you already use on the web.Features:- Trends: See how people are engaging with your app by measuring the actions people take. - Funnels: See where people are dropping off.- Retention: See how often your users come back and how valuable your app is.- Notifications: Get a push notification when your metrics change in a surprising way. (Coming soon...)- Security: If two-factor or single-sign-on is required for your account, you'll be able to securely login.- Personalized: Your dashboard is personalized for what you care about.- All your data: If you utilize multiple projects for different apps or different parts of your application, you'll be able to make a dashboard for each project.   ', u'description': u'The official Mixpanel companion app', u'title': u'Mixpanel - Android Apps on Google Play'}]

tagline: A virtual pronunciation coach
text_content: [{u'description': u'ELSA is a mobile application that functions as a personal coach to help English learners around the world	speak English more correctly and confidently', u'title': u'ELSA - Your virtual pronunciation coach'}, {u'body': u' Learn to speak English fluently and like a native speaker with ELSA, the world's first English Language Speech Assistant. ELSA is a mobile application to help everyone speak English like a native speaker. ELSA is an artificial intelligence teacher who will help you have perfect English pronunciation, practice frequently-used English words, phrases and communications. For the first time, users can learn how to speak English and benefit from the specialized feedback and practical vocabulary. Down the street, up the block, around the corner, we‚Äôll show you things you can actually engage with in real life.Locopass is FREE.
How it Works:1. Explore Your World
When you enter a Locopass Zone the app will notify you.
If you leave the Zone, the notification will disappear.
2. Discover the Possibilities
Click on the notification and the app will open up to your Feed where you‚Äôll see details regarding an event or promotion in your immediate vicinity.
3. Maximize Your Experience

Simply learning more about happenings in your area
Locopass was designed with the purpose of helping users get more out of life in their country, city, town or village. tagline: Photo collage maker
text_content:
[{u'description': u'Poto is a powerful collage maker and photo editor for you to create amazing collages using your photos, fun stickers, text with cool fonts.', u'title': u'Poto - Photo Collage Maker'}, {u'body': u' With Poto, you can put multiple photos together in one beautiful collage and greatly enhance it with various kinds of decorations. It‚Äôs very easy to use, and super fun to play with.Poto - Photo Collage Editor comes with a load of handy features, and allows great freedom and flexibility. Dozens of templates:
Support creating both single framed photo and multiple-photo collages which can contain up to 9 photos.Customize templates:
Make adjustments on templates. Create borderless, rounded-edge collages.Easy editing
Freely rotate, zoom in/out, and re-arrange your photosStylish fonts:
Poto provides a hand-picked selection of cool fonts, and allows a wide range of editing options: rotate, scale, change color, add multiple texts.Cute stickers:
Choose from dozens of stickers to spice up your photos!Artistic filters
Give your collage a tint of artistic touch. These special effects can be applied both globally and individually on your photos.Easy Sharing
Share your collages onto all major social platforms (Facebook, Instagram and many more) with just a few taps.
Join with millions of collage fans in the world and start making your own stunning collages now!   ', u'description': u'Awesome Photo Collages. Personalise Your Photos Anytime with Poto!', u'title': u'Poto - Photo Collage Maker - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': u'Poto is a powerful collage maker and photo editor for you to create amazing collages using your photos, fun stickers, text with cool fonts. Poto Photo Collage Editor provides a load of handy features, and allows great freedom and flexibility. With Poto, you can arrange the photos exactly the way you like it. It‚Äôs very easy to use and super fun to play around. Dozens of templates: Support creating both single framed photo and multiple-photo collages which can contain up to 9 photos. Enhanced editing Freely rotate, freely zoom in & out, and freely move photos in the collages. Frames and backgrounds Dozens of backgrounds that can instantly make your photos stand out! Stylish text: More than 100 fonts available. Allows a wide range of editing options: rotate, scale, change color, add multiple texts. Cute stickers: Choose from dozens of stickers to spice up your photos! Artistic filters More than a dozen are available. These special effects can be applied both globally and individually on your photos. Easy Sharing Share your collages onto all major social platforms (Facebook, Instagram and many more) with only a few taps. Join with millions of collage fans in the world and start making your own stunning collages now!', u'title': u'Poto - Photo Collage Maker'}]

text_content:
[{u'description': None, u'title': u'ABBYY TextGrabber + Translator - mobile OCR and full-text translation'}, {u'description': u'ABBYY TextGrabber easily and quickly scans, translates and saves your chosen text or QR-codes from virtually any printed material. Simply take a picture of the text on 60+ languages or QR-codes and immediately edit, hear it spoken aloud via VoiceOver, translate it into 90+ languages, send your text by SMS or e-mail, or share it quickly on Facebook, Twitter or Evernote. Translation is available as a separate in-app purchase. ***** Winner of SUPERSTAR Award in the "Mobile Productivity App", "Mobile Image Capture App" and ‚ÄúText Input‚Äù categories in Mobile Star Awards ------------------------ ‚ÄúTextgrabber is probably the best app which adds another function to your iPhone: a scanner‚Äù- The Irish Times ‚ÄúThe results get delivered relatively fast, which is great. A must have for students‚Äù - appadvice.com ‚ÄúThe Best Image-to-Text App for iPhone‚Äù - lifehacker.com ------------------------ With ABBYY TextGrabber you can save and translate any printed text you need with a tap of your screen: ‚Ä¢ Receipts ‚Ä¢ Travel documents ‚Ä¢ Notes ‚Ä¢ Magazine articles ‚Ä¢ Book fragments ‚Ä¢ Manuals and instructions ‚Ä¢ Recipe ingredients, etc. ------------------------ KEY FEATURES: ‚Ä¢ Easy and accurate text or QR-codes capture from printed sources, such as books, magazines, ads, timetables, etc. ‚Ä¢ Accurate on-device text recognition for 60+ languages, including German, French, Spanish, Portuguese, Russian, English, Chinese, Korean and others ‚Ä¢ Instant translation into 90+ languages (Internet connection is required, separate in-app purchase) ‚Ä¢ Powerful text-to-speech capability with the VoiceOver system feature ‚Ä¢ Adjustable font sizes and audio prompts to assist visually impaired people ‚Ä¢ Fast and convenient sharing via Facebook, Twitter, Evernote, email or SMS ‚Ä¢ All extracted text is automatically backed up and can be easily found in the ‚ÄúHistory‚Äù folder ------------------------ The application is partially compatible with the iPad 2 and iPod Touch 4 Gen (uploading images from photo album is only available). OCR HINT: Please select the appropriate language (up to three at a time) before recognition VIEW DEMO VIDEO on YouTube: http://bit.ly/TG-iOS-Video Twitter @ABBYY_Mobile Facebook: http://facebook.com/AbbyyMobile ----------------------- IMPORTANT NOTE FROM THE DEVELOPERS Unfortunately, we are unable to respond to your comments here. With any questions and suggestions please contact us directly at support@abbyy.com ABBYY TEXTGRABBER IS THE BEST WAY TO DIGITIZE, SAVE AND TRANSLATE ANY PRINTED INFORMATION! Please leave a review if you like ABBYY TextGrabber . Thank you!', u'title': u'TextGrabber - image to text app: copy recipe from a cookbook, scan QR code, capture text on photo and send to translator'}, {u'body': u' TextGrabber + Translator easily extracts snippets of text from a variety of printed sources by using the device‚Äôs camera. You can digitize printed information and translate it into any of more than 90 languages anywhere anytime. ***** Winner of SUPERSTAR Award in the ‚ÄúText Input‚Äù category in the Mobile Star Awards ***** Just take a picture of the text, and you can immediately edit and translate it, share via e-mail and SMS, or transfer it directly to other applications installed on your device - social networks, online storage services, etc. With TextGrabber + Translator you can scan and translate: 
‚Ä¢ Documents 
‚Ä¢ Receipts 
‚Ä¢ Notes 
‚Ä¢ Articles 
‚Ä¢ Book fragments 
‚Ä¢ Manuals and instructions 
‚Ä¢ Product ingredients, etc. ------------------------ 
MAIN FEATURES: 
‚Ä¢ Accurate Internet-free text recognition in more than 60 languages, including English, German, French, Spanish, Portuguese, Russian, Greek, Chinese, Korean and others. 
‚Ä¢ Captured text can be easily edited or copied to the clipboard 
‚Ä¢ Instant translation from more than 90 languages (please note: an Internet connection is required for translation)
‚Ä¢ Fast & convenient information sharing via email or SMS 
‚Ä¢ One-tap transferring of recognition results to other applications - social networks, online storage services, etc. via Android ‚ÄòShare‚Äô function 
‚Ä¢ Search engine support 
‚Ä¢ All captured texts are stored in the app and can be easily found anytime in the ‚ÄúHistory‚Äù folder. ------------------------ 
SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS: 3 mega pixels camera or more with autofocus
An Internet connection is not required for OCR!OCR HINT: Please select the appropriate language (up to three at a time) before recognition ------------------------ 
ABBYY Mobile on Facebook: http://fb.com/abbyymobile 
FOLLOW US on Twitter @ABBYY_Mobile   ', u'description': u'Recognizes texts from paper and translates them into 40 languages!', u'title': u'TextGrabber + Translator - Android Apps on Google Play'}]

tagline: AI that repaints photos in the style of your favorite artist
text_content: [{u'description': u'Malevich is an artificial intelligence that repaints any picture in the style of your favorite artist. Malevich works the way human brain does. Using next generation neural networks it mixes contents of your photo and the style of your favorite artist. Whether you want your image to be painted by Van Gogh, Monet, Picasso, Andy Warhol, Munch, Renoir or Dali, we offer you a tool transforming your photo to art quick and easy. ART MADE EASY Upload your photo The first picture defines the scene you would like to paint Choose a style The second picture defines the style of your painting Create Malevich server will paint the image for you It‚Äôs not an ordinary filter or photo-editing tool. It is much more! Imagine how great artists of all time might have painted your selfie, your commute to work, your friends, or your dinner. Not every result is a masterpiece, because you need to find a match between a style and the photo. Yet, you can create some amazing artworks with Malevich. This is very computationally intensive, even on a cloud of the fastest computers it takes a few minutes to process your photo. GET SOME INSPIRATION See what others have created in the feed from Instagram. Want to see your works in the feed, use #mlvch hashtag in a post. QUALITY and PRICING We create high quality 1024x1024 images. Because generating them requires a lot of computational power, free images are limited to five per day. This is done to make a short queue. You can buy as many additional images as you want. They will be generated ahead of queue (usually in less then 3 min). ULEASH THE ARTIST WITHIN! Our team focuses on making artworks better, decreasing waiting time and lowering prices. Please, send your questions and suggestions to support@mlvch.com', u'title': u'Mlvch ‚Äì create artworks in styles of famous artists like Van Gogh, Malevich or Kandinsky'}, {u'description': None, u'title': u'Malevich'}]

text_content: [{u'description': u' KarmaCircles is a platform for finding skilled people, request them for an online/phone/in-person meeting and then thank them for the time & help given by them through KarmaNote.', u'title': u'Welcome to KarmaCircles - Log In, Sign Up or Learn More'}, {u'body': u' KarmaCircles is a platform to search for skilled people, request a meeting (online/phone/in-person) and then thank them for the time & help given by them. People give their time out of the goodness of their heart and to build their online reputation around various skills.KarmaMeeting - You can search for professionals by name, skills, groups & location. We call them KarmaGivers. If you need help from them, you can request a KarmaMeeting from these KarmaGivers.KarmaNote - After a KarmaMeeting, you are supposed to send a KarmaNote to your KarmaGiver. KarmaNote is a form of thank-you note for taking the time to help you with something. PLEASE NOTE THAT IT IS NOT FEEDBACK. One should be thankful to the KarmaGiver for the time that they gave you. It doesn‚Äôt matter whether their advice was useful or not. You also get the opportunity to endorse the KarmaGiver for up to three skills.You could thank KarmaGivers for a KarmaMeeting in the past. You can also thank one of your contacts for a KarmaMeeting in the past. The contact may not be registered on KarmaCircles platform yet.KarmaGroup - You can join a KarmaGroup to be part of your company's network or your schools's alumni network. One can send you a KarmaMeeting request only if you share at least one group with them. To create KarmaGroup for your company or school, please contact us at help@karmacircles.comKarmaFeed - KarmaFeed allows you to see who is helping who on the KarmaCircles platform. If you don't know who can help you with your needs, you can post a query on KarmaCircles. Each query goes into KarmaFeed and anyone can offer help. You can then schedule a KarmaMeeting with them.KarmaIntro - If you wish to ask someone (who you already know) to help a KarmaReceiver, you can introduce a KarmaReceiver to a KarmaGiver. You can then track the status of KarmaMeeting between the two of them.KarmaPoint- Karma points are the way to measure someone‚Äôs reputation on the KarmaCircles platform. The higher the score, the better it is. You get 10 points when you receive a KarmaNote for a KarmaMeeting. You also get two points when you send a KarmaNote to someone.Privacy - The messages that you send to a KarmaGiver requesting a KarmaMeeting is visible only to two of you. The responses that you receive from the KarmaGiver are visible only to two of you. The KarmaNote that you send to a KarmaGiver is visible on your profile as well as the KarmaGiver‚Äôs profile. You can always hide it from your profile at any point of time.   ', u'description': u'Give & receive professional help for free. Help others & build your reputation.', u'title': u'KarmaCircles - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': u'KarmaCircles is a platform to search for skilled people, request a meeting (online/phone/in-person) and then thank them for the time & help given by them. People give their time out of the goodness of their heart and to build their online reputation around various skills. We believe that "Karma Circles" i.e. if you do good karma, it circles back to you. KarmaMeeting - You can search for professionals by name, skills, groups & location. We call them KarmaGivers. If you need help from them, you can request a KarmaMeeting from these KarmaGivers. KarmaNote - After a KarmaMeeting, you are supposed to send a KarmaNote to your KarmaGiver. KarmaNote is a form of thank-you note for taking the time to help you with something. PLEASE NOTE THAT IT IS NOT FEEDBACK. One should be thankful to the KarmaGiver for the time that they gave you. It doesn‚Äôt matter whether their advice was useful or not. You also get the opportunity to endorse the KarmaGiver for up to three skills. You could thank KarmaGivers for a KarmaMeeting in the past. You can also thank one of your contacts for a KarmaMeeting in the past. The contact may not be registered on KarmaCircles platform yet. KarmaGroup - You can join a KarmaGroup to be part of your company's network or your schools's alumni network. One can send you a KarmaMeeting request only if you share at least one group with them. To create KarmaGroup for your company or school, please contact us at help@karmacircles.com KarmaFeed - KarmaFeed allows you to see who is helping who on the KarmaCircles platform. If you don't know who can help you with your needs, you can post a query on KarmaCircles. Each query goes into KarmaFeed and anyone can offer help. You can then schedule a KarmaMeeting with them. KarmaPoint- Karma points are the way to measure someone‚Äôs reputation on the KarmaCircles platform. The higher the score, the better it is. You get 10 points when you receive a KarmaNote for a KarmaMeeting. You also get two points when you send a KarmaNote to someone. Privacy - The messages that you send to a KarmaGiver requesting a KarmaMeeting is visible only to two of you. The responses that you receive from the KarmaGiver are visible only to two of you. The KarmaNote that you send to a KarmaGiver is visible on your profile as well as the KarmaGiver‚Äôs profile. You can always hide it from your profile at any point of time. KarmaCircles terms of use: http://www.karmacircles.com/terms', u'title': u'KarmaCircles'}]

tagline: IFTTT for the stock market
text_content: [{u'description': u'Trigger watches the stock market so that you don‚Äôt have you. With Trigger, you can create simple ‚ÄúIf this, then that‚Äù statements that monitor the market in real-time and notify you when their conditions are met. For example, you can create ‚Äútriggers‚Äù related to: - How rising interest rates affects the S&P - Notifications when your favorite stock reaches a new all-time high (or low) - Real-time intraday price drops and falls - When a stock you own has halted trading - Real-time earnings announcements results and how they affect your portfolio - US Inflation and GDP reports - Corporate fundamentals like P/E ratios and market cap Link your online brokerage account to see all your positions and set triggers on your returns.', u'title': u'Trigger - Create Rules to Track the Market'}, {u'description': u'Trigger helps you manage your portfolio by simplifying your investment ideas into "If THIS, then THAT" statements. Sign up to be notified when it becomes available.', u'title': u'Trigger Finance - Create Rules that Track the Market'}]

tagline: Discover where to travel
text_content: [{u'description': u'LAUNCH SALE: 80% off for a limited time! Modern Atlas lets you discover and bookmark places to explore. Make the most of your next adventure. Browse through 21,000 practical travel guides, uncover 1.5 million hidden gems and landmarks, and create your own custom trip maps. Modern Atlas is the most comprehensive tool to explore the world and plan your dream trips. == Practical Travel Guides == Reference over 21,000 travel guides created by independent travelers from Wikivoyage / Wikitravel featuring the best places to see, eat, and sleep. They cover virtually every place in the world a traveler would look to visit, from the largest cities in Europe, to the national parks of North America, to remote villages in the mountains and deserts of Asia and Africa. == Comprehensive Place Guides == Learn about the history of a place with detailed articles for over 1.5 million landmarks, historic sites, and hidden gems from Wikipedia. Never leave yourself wondering about a place again. == Visual Inspiration == Unfamiliar with a destination? Search for visual inspiration from photographers all over the world. Discover new places, see where photos are taken, and plan your future visits around them. == Custom Trip Maps == Create your own custom trip maps by bookmarking places that interest you. Plan an itinerary, remember places you've visited, keep note of your favorite museums and restaurants, or map out all of the mountains and campsites for an upcoming hiking trip. The possibilities are endless. == Beautiful Base Maps == Custom, offline-ready* topographic maps with worldwide coverage. Nearly everything in the world is mapped and at your fingertips for when you hit the ground. *Any maps you've already viewed in the app are available offline, just put your device into airplane mode to test it out == Virtual Tours == Scope out a city and its landmarks in 3D with Apple Flyover. See the full list of supported places at flyovercities.com Modern Atlas was created for the modern adventurer: the travelers, outdoorsmen, and explorers of the world. Be curious and venture outward. For any issues or suggestions, feel free to contact us at support@modernatlas.co!', u'title': u'Modern Atlas Travel Guide & City Maps ‚Äî nearby places in Wikipedia & Wikivoyage'}, {u'description': u'Discover & bookmark places to explore on your next adventure. 21,000 travel guides and 1.5 million places to discover. Create your own trip maps & start planning your next adventure. For iPhone and iPad.', u'title': u'Modern Atlas // Map-based travel guide app'}]

tagline: An all-In-One Calendar
text_content: [{u'description': u'Simpliday brings together your meetings, reminders and email into one calendar. Work with meetings and reminders side-by-side. Drag-‚Äòn-drop your day. Convert emails to reminders with a swipe. Share reminders and meetings. Simply see everything and miss nothing. USERS REVIEWS ‚ÄùThis app is very very nice and easy to use! Very helpful to keep organized.‚Äù /Lnemurph ‚ÄùQuickly after downloading the app I fell in love with its design and functionality. Highly recommend it for people like me who want to use meetings, todos and emails in one app.‚Äù /BossKh85 ‚ÄùI have been looking for an integrated todo app for a long time. Simpliday‚Äôs workflow is intuitive. It is a joy to use and a lot of thought has gone into what the user needs to do next‚Ä¶‚Äù /Rafhere The five principles we base our work on are; 1. EVERYTHING AT A GLANCE What matters is the people you meet and the things you need to get done, that's why we've put meetings and reminders side-by-side. - All your daily commitments at a glance ‚Äì meetings and reminders in the same view - See your Simpliday reminders in your Mac desktop/laptop calendar - Add documents to meetings so that every participants have them 2. EVERYTHING CHANGES ALL THE TIME Since your schedule and commitments are constantly being changed, we've made it real easy to move meetings and reminders around to match your ever-changing day. - Drag-'n-drop any meeting or reminder to where you want it - Set a reminder in time or simply move it to the side of the screen to save it for later 3. EMAIL IS NOT EMAIL - IT'S ACTUALLY COMMITMENTS (AND SPAM...) Your typical inbox is a mix of meetings, reminders, information and spam - that's why we've invented the action-swipe. The action-swipe enables you to turn an email into a meeting or reminder in two seconds - just by swiping it. - Turn any email into a meeting or reminder in seconds - Add multiple email accounts to one inbox ‚Äì workmail along side your private Gmail - Attach any email to an existing meeting or reminder 4. FAMILY, WORK AND FRIENDS ‚Äì ALL IN THE SAME PLACE As you already know, your life is not compartmentalized. Your kids call you at work, you send work-emails from family gatherings, your friends tend fill up your work inbox with ‚Äùlet‚Äôs find a time to meet‚Äù-emails at times. Some would call it a mess, we would say that all of your life is integrated. - One interface to all of your day ‚Äì family, work and friends AND meetings, reminders and email. - See family calendars next to work calendars 5. IT'S YOUR DAY - MAKE IT YOURS We may have developed the app, but it's your day sitting inside it. That‚Äôs why it is possible to change the background to the image of your choice - a beach, a family photo, your pet, vacation photos - whatever makes your day. - Set the background of your day by choosing any image from your own camera roll - If you prefer, you can choose between a number of beautiful backgrounds we have picked out that works perfectly --- The details --- Meetings Simpliday is connected through CalDav - tech language meaning that every meeting you have in your iPhone can also be found in Simpliday. When you create a new meeting in Simpliday, we will send it to your other calendars as well ‚Äì so you have all your meetings in all your calendars. Reminders Create and assign reminders. Add files and descriptions so that the person carrying out the reminder has everything he/she needs to get the job done - be it a colleague at work, a neighbour or your partner. Email Connect your Gmail, Outlook, Hotmail, Yahoo, iCloud, Exchange(EWS) or any IMAP account to Simpliday to make sure that you have all the email accounts you need in the same inbox. Files Connect Simpliday to Dropbox, Google Drive, iCloud and OneDrive in order to add the files you want to your meetings & reminders. Contacts Simpliday uses the contacts already stored in your iPhone, to make sure you can easily schedule meetings and assign reminders within your network. /The Simpliday Team', u'title': u'Simpliday - All-In-One Calendar'}]

tagline: See current drive times in your Mac menu bar üöô üïë
text_content: [{u'description': u'Chop Commute - see current drive times and traffic information on OS X menu bar as a status icon', u'title': u'Chop Commute - see current drive times on OS X menu bar'}, {u'description': u'Take the guess work out of your daily commute by seeing real-time traffic and drive times specific to your route right on your Mac menu bar (system status tray). Beat the traffic - save time and money by leaving for work or home at the right time. No need to manually check the traffic on your phone to figure out the best time to get out of work - Chop commute does the work for you and always shows you the best time right on the OS X menu bar. Chop commute is like Google Now for macOS, only better since it is designed specifically to help you get home quicker. Key features: + Live traffic information for almost all countries (using traffic data from Google Maps) + Status icon displaying color coded commute information + Save time and money by leaving at the right time + Optimized for macOS (10.12+) and OS X (10.10+)', u'title': u'Chop Commute - see current drive times on menu bar on the Mac App Store'}]

tagline: Content broadcast from the NYSE floor daily
text_content:
[{u'body': u' A unique and often wacky approach to news in technology, media, and entertainment, Cheddar is broadcast daily from the floor of the New York Stock Exchange, with exclusive CEO and founder interviews and the best of technology and media coverage.Subscribe to get access to Cheddar videos, right on your device!
‚Ä¢ Pay $6.99 a month with a 30-day free trial, renewing monthly.
‚Ä¢ Pay $59.99 a year with a 30-day free trial, renewing annually.With this Cheddar subscription, you will receive: ‚Ä¢ Daily weekday updates from the stock exchange floor
‚Ä¢ Exclusive interviews with top tier CEO's 
‚Ä¢ The company profiles you care about 
‚Ä¢ Business advice straight from the experts
‚Ä¢ Beautiful, HD streaming videos
‚Ä¢ Automatically send videos from your phone to your Chromecast enabled devices
‚Ä¢ No Internet required! Sync videos to watch offline, or connect with WiFi, 3G and 4G
‚Ä¢ Pick up where you left off, no problem
‚Ä¢ Comment on videos with the rest of the community
‚Ä¢ Tell your friends about your favorite videos with Twitter, Facebook, texts, and email, right in the app
‚Ä¢ For existing subscribers, you can simply sign in to your account to get access. No need to resubscribe.Terms of Service: https://cheddar.vhx.tv/tos
Privacy Policy: https://cheddar.vhx.tv/privacy   ', u'description': u'News coverage on tech, innovative products and transformative technologies.', u'title': u'Cheddar - Android Apps on Google Play'}]

tagline: Create polished video ads right from your phone
text_content:
[{u'description': None, u'title': u'
      Make video ads - YouTube
    '}, {u'description': u'YouTube Director provides shot-by-shot guidance‚Äîso you can create a high-quality video ad and upload it right from the app. No video editing experience required. Now, sharing your unique story with customers on YouTube is easy. CHOOSE A READY-TO-GO TEMPLATE Browse from 100+ video templates designed for businesses just like yours. Whether you‚Äôre a restaurant, service, retail shop or anything in-between, YouTube Director has a template that lets you tell your story, showcase your products, and highlight your mission. STEP-BY-STEP INSTRUCTIONS First-time making a video? No problem. YouTube Director provides shot-by-shot guidance to help you create a polished video for your business. YouTube Director helps you with everything from how to frame your video to what to say, and when. NO EDITING SKILLS REQUIRED Easy-to-use features like voiceover and custom text animations give your video a professional look. Add the perfect soundtrack to your video with music from YouTube‚Äôs extensive library. PROMOTE YOUR VIDEO ON YOUTUBE Upload your finished video to YouTube and start promoting your business to customers. An AdWords expert will reach out to help you run your new video ad on YouTube.', u'title': u'YouTube Director for Business'}]

tagline: Send locked messages that eventually... unlock
text_content: [{u'description': u'Sealed lets you send locked messages that will eventually unlock on a date that you choose. Recipients immediately receive the sealed messages but cannot open them... until they are set to unlock. As Andy Warhol once said, "the idea of waiting for something makes it more exciting." Sealed makes you wait, bringing anticipation and curiosity into the messaging experience. How you use Sealed is totally up to you, but here are a few ideas to get you started: * Send a message to a friend or loved one for the end of their long workday. They'll receive it in the morning and wait all day to see what it is. * Send a birthday or holiday message weeks in advance to unlock at exactly the right moment. * Use Sealed as a time capsule. Capture moments and send them to yourself or to friends for years into the future. FEATURES * Send photos, videos, or just text in your message. * Unlimited time delay, minimum of 1 hour. * Disappearing option: choose whether you want your message to disappear or not after opening. * Coming soon: send time-delayed gift cards. The message will look exactly the same until it unlocks to reveal your gift inside! FREE *Sealed is totally free.', u'title': u'Sealed Messenger'}, {u'description': u'Sealed is an app that sends time-delayed photos, videos, and gifts.', u'title': u'Sealed Messenger'}]

tagline: Event messaging app for WWDC attendees
text_content: [{u'description': u'Avenue is a group messaging app for everyone. Users can join public chat rooms focused on trending topics or start private chats with members they invite. We are always updating our global rooms based on popular events, trending topics, etc. You can also create your own rooms that are private by default. Only people you invite will be able to join the room. Sharing your room is as easy as posting a link to it from the room screen. Currently rooms don't have a limit on number of people that can participate. Features: [+] Easy sign up with Twitter [+] Global chat rooms [+] Private chat rooms [+] Direct messaging [+] Push notification settings per room (look at that bell icon) [+] Live typing indicators inside chats [+] Delete personal messages [+] Flag inappropriate content We hope you are enjoying using the app as much as we did making it.', u'title': u'Avenue - Group Communication'}]

tagline: iOS keyboard and social network for gifs and emoji packs
text_content: [{u'description': u'Hi-Art is a social network for emoji, gifs, memes and stickers. You can make, find, and share stickers, memes, emoji and GIFs with family, fans and friends from your keyboard. Hi-Art transforms your SMS conversations with an infinite library of images and GIFs (from Giphy) right inside your keyboard. You can now quickly create emoji, gifs or cut out photos, add words, drawings, stickers, stamps, overlays, filters, and other images. Explore and share via SMS text, iMessage, chat, Twitter, Instagram, Facebook, WhatsApp, WeChat, Tango, and more! Hi-Art's sticker library includes influential artists, celebrities, and musicians like Lil Bub, Cam‚Äôron, The Fat Jew, the Misfits, Ghostface Killah, Kid Ink, Todd James, Steve Powers, Dan Santoro, Ron English, Claw Money, Love Me, Seventh Letter, Grotesk, Fadeproof, and Vizie. Hi-Art makes contemporary art a part of everyday conversation. Have feedback or need help? Email us at info@hi-art.me. Please Note: *The Hi-Art Keyboard requests full access so you can access our stickers. We don‚Äôt store your typing information or compromise your privacy.', u'title': u'Hi-Art - Stickers, Emoji, Gifs, Memes, and Keyboard'}, {u'description': None, u'title': u'Hi-Art - Make Sticker and Gifs '}]

tagline: Spotify recommendations based on your songs
text_content: [{u'description': u'Soundtrack is fully integrated with Spotify and allows you to browse your existing Spotify library and expand it while listening to your own songs! First, scroll through your playlists. Once you find one you like, play a preview of any song. While listening a card will show up that suggests 20 curated songs that are related to the specific song you chose. It also shows you related artists based on the artist you are listening to. Soundtrack conveniently allows you to discover songs while listening to your music. If you find a song that you like, you can add it to any playlist, save it to your music library, or create your own playlist all within the app! Looking for a song that's not in your existing library? Use the search feature to search for any song and then get recommendations based on that song! Feedback or suggestions? Email me at zachary.cmiel@gmail.com', u'title': u'Soundtrack - Discover The Best Music on Spotify'}]

tagline: Discover movies without spoilers and damn fast
text_content: [{u'description': u'No idea what to watch on Netflix, Amazon or iTunes? Find better movies faster with Popflake App! Your keyword based movie search engine', u'title': u'Popflake App'}, {u'description': u'Popflake is your go to app when you want to watch a movie. Whether you want to go to the cinema, stream a movie, rent or buy one. We provide an easy to use keyword search for you. Simply press the keywords that describe your mood, a country the movie should play in, a type of plot or a general movie type. A great example would be; horror + students + forest! Every movie in our database is "hand-tagged". This is why the database contains not so many movies yet. If you love movies like we do, contact us and we can set you up with an beta account and access to the online movie tagging platform! Features or "How to use Popflake": 1) Click on a keyword that sounds compelling 2) Repeat step 1 until movies appear or you think the keywords describe what you want to watch 3) Click on a compelling movie cover 4) A movie details view appears which currently includes a movie rating (top right corner), a way to share that movie with friends (chat bubble in the middle of the screen under the movie title), the movie title, the year of the release, the movie age rating, ~8 actors and links to legally stream / buy the movie (via iTunes, Netflix..) Questions? Our FAQs: https://popflakeapp.com/faq/ Love: - You love the app? Rate us, we read every rating! - Tell them about Popflake Yours truly The Popflake Team #xoxo', u'title': u'Popflake'}]

tagline: Found a product but not at the price you are willing to pay?
text_content: [{u'description': u'Found a product but not at the price you are willing to pay? Save the product and Wait For Savings! Put products from pretty much any website into your Wait For Savings List. When that product goes down in price, Wait For Savings will alert you!', u'title': u'Wait For Savings'}, {u'body': u' Wait For Savings Lists are universal. You can add anything from any website to Wait For Savings making it easier than ever to keep track of all the products you want to buy at the price you are willing to pay.Once you download the Wait For Savings App -- start shopping. When you see something you want on any website, just share to Wait For Savings. Then from the app, you can view your list of products as well as those that you marked as bought and even those you decided to pass on. Whether you‚Äôre browsing online or on-the-go, Wait For Savings lets you save products wherever you find them.   ', u'description': u'When you find something you want but not at the right price, Wait For Savings!', u'title': u'Wait For Savings - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': u'Wait For Savings Lists are universal. Once you download the Wait For Savings App -- start shopping. When you see something you want on any website, just share to Wait For Savings. Then from the app, you can view your list of products as well as those that you marked as bought and even those you decided to pass on. Whether you‚Äôre browsing online or on-the-go, Wait For Savings lets you save products wherever you find them. tagline: World class indoor cycling experience wherever you are
text_content: [{u'description': u'Indoor cycling at your fingertips: Ride now ‚Äì anytime, anywhere. With the Peloton app, stream live and on-demand Peloton cycling classes to your iPhone or iPad. ‚Ä¢ Experience a range of group rides led by top indoor cycling coaches. ‚Ä¢ Take effective, full body cycling classes on your schedule ‚Ä¢ Ride at home. At the gym. Anywhere. PELOTON RIDES ‚Ä¢ 10+ daily live rides and 3,000+ on-demand rides ‚Ä¢ Classes suited to all riders, varying in length (10-90 minutes) and difficulty. ‚Ä¢ Rides coached by inspiring, motivational instructors ‚Ä¢ Real classes filmed at the Peloton studio in NYC ‚Ä¢ A variety of exciting, innovative ride types including Rhythm, Metrics, Theme, Live DJ, and Pro Cyclist rides TAKE PELOTON ANYWHERE Use the Peloton app at home or the gym to take indoor cycling rides. Attach your iOS device to any stationary bike and plug in a pair of headphones before launching a ride of your choice OR stream rides from your iOS device to any Apple TV using AirPlay. CHOOSE AN ACCESS PLAN THAT WORKS FOR YOU The Peloton app offers several access plans. ‚Ä¢ 14-Day Trial ‚Äì 14 days of free, unlimited access to live-streaming and on-demand Peloton classes on your iOS device. This plan can only be used one time. You will not be charged and the plan will not not auto-renew. ‚Ä¢ 1-Week Pass ($5.99) ‚Äì 1 week of unlimited access to live-streaming and on-demand Peloton classes on your iOS device for $5.99. This plan will not auto-renew. ‚Ä¢ Monthly Membership ($12.99/Month) ‚Äì 1 month of unlimited access to live-streaming and on-demand Peloton classes on your iOS device for $12.99. This plan automatically renews on a monthly basis.. ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- Additional Information on our 14 Day Free Trial access plan: Access to the Peloton app can be initially gained through a 14 day free trial access plan, which can be obtained at no cost. The 14 day free trial can only be used once per device. The free trial access plan will not auto-renew or charge you automatically. Additional Information on our Monthly Membership access plan: Access to the Peloton app can be gained through a monthly subscription (Monthly Membership), which can be purchased for $12.99 (plus tax, where applicable.) The Monthly Membership auto-renews on a monthly basis. The monthly subscription will be charged to your iTunes account at confirmation of purchase. By completing your purchase, you certify that that you are at least 18 years old and that you understand and agree to the Terms of Service (https://www.pelotoncycle.com/terms-of-services) and Privacy Policy (https://www.pelotoncycle.com/privacy-policy).Your Peloton subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours prior to the end of the current period. Your account will be charged the monthly subscription of $12.99 (plus tax, where applicable) for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period. Auto-renewal may be turned off in your Account Setting in iTunes after purchase. No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during an active subscription period. A user that cancels during a subscription month will not be charged for the following month.', u'title': u'Peloton Cycle ‚Äì Live Streaming Indoor Cycling Classes'}, {u'description': u'Peloton is changing the way people get fit by delivering live-streaming instructional exercise content to the most technologically advanced indoor cycle.', u'title': u'Peloton | iOS App'}]

text_content: [{u'body': u' 2016 Labor Statistics uses the statistics provided by the Bureau of Labor Statistics (http://www.bls.gov/) to provide insight into to the employment landscape.Know what you kind of job you want? - 2016 Labor Statistics can show you what industries pay the best and employ the more workers in that field and for U.S. states and cities as well.Know what industry you want to work in? - 2016 Labor Statistics can show you what occupations are employed the most highly in that industry and what U.S. states and cities employ the most worker for that industry as well.Know where you want to live? - 2016 Labor Statistics can show you what occupations are paid the best in that area and what occupations have the highest employment in that area.Already employed and want to compare your salary against the market? - 2016 Labor Statistics can compare and graph entered salaries against the market based on occupation, industry, and geographic location. tagline: Make money by selling your personal data to marketing firms.
text_content: [{u'description': None, u'title': u'DataWallet'}, {u'description': u'Your time spent online is money, and your data from Facebook, Instagram, and Twitter is gold just sitting in your pocket. Instead of big data brokerage firms selling this data behind your back, DataWallet allows you to take control and reclaim the profits made with your data for yourself. Using DataWallet is free and involves three easy steps: 1. Connect your platforms. This can be data from Facebook, Twitter, Instagram and Pinterest, with more platforms to be added in the coming months. 2. Choose which companies can access analyses based on your data. You can choose from more than 19 types of Data Buyers to make analyses based on your data available to-- from marketing agencies to producers of household appliances to banks. 3. All set! We‚Äôll take care it from there and whenever a company uses an analysis that involves your data, you‚Äôll get paid. When you use DataWallet, no data will ever be shared directly with any third parties. We take the data you connect and generate high-level analyses about it. Whenever a company accesses an analysis that your data helped generate, you will get paid. This way, we can guarantee that all data is 100% anonymized, 100% secure, and never leaves our servers. Follow us on Twitter @DataWalletHQ', u'title': u'DataWallet - Reclaim The Profits Made With Your Data'}]

tagline: Assessment scanning and grading with iPhone
text_content: [{u'description': u'With the Akindi mobile app, you can quickly grade assessments with your iPhone‚Äôs camera and get immediate results, insights, and analysis. Since 2012, we‚Äôve been helping educators manage, grade and provide feedback on multiple choice assessments using any paper and scanner. We‚Äôre now excited to bring our proven experience to your classroom so you can do all that and more with just your iPhone. Our platform is trusted and used by teachers across the world in schools like Harvard, USC, Duke and many more. BUILT FOR EDUCATORS Akindi makes it easy to carry out assessments with tools to help you handle errors, scan results, manage class roster and store answer sheets. CUSTOM ANSWER SHEETS Choose from different templates and customize them with your assessment information for a better testing experience. PERFORMANCE INSIGHTS Spend less time pushing numbers around and more time seeing what went well and what requires more of your attention. WEB PLATFORM Access your assessments and results on your phone, or continue the Akindi experience on the web! SUPPORT If you run into any issues, have feature ideas, or just want to say hello, shoot us a note at support@akindi.com ‚ñ∏ www.akindi.com', u'title': u'Akindi - Assessment scanning and grading'}, {u'description': u'Create assessments effortlessly. Grade multiple choice assessments using regular paper and any scanner! A free Scantron alternative you're sure to love.', u'title': u'Akindi - Effortless Grading (Scantron Alternative)'}]
