Get the free app and discover family-friendly places to play, eat, shop and more.', u'title': u'Winnie - Find Great Places for Kids'}, {u'description': u'Winnie helps parents navigate the world with their children. We give moms, dads, and people who care for children the information they need to find great activities and destinations for families. With data on over 100,000 locations, here are some of the things you can do with Winnie: * Find hidden gems and new places to play like the best parks, playgrounds and libraries nearby. * Search for family-friendly restaurants with changing tables, kids menus, highchairs and whatever else you need for a stress-free outing. * Locate the closest place to nurse a baby, change a diaper, or use a potty. * Add stories about the places you visit and keep track of where you travel with your kids. Winnie currently works best in the San Francisco Bay Area and early access is available for other parts of the country.', u'title': u'Winnie ‚Äî Find Great Places for Kids'}]

tagline: We instantly match you to the perfect home üè°
text_content: [{u'description': u'Get instantly matched to your perfect home. "Casamatic is like having a best friend/real estate agent combo in my pocket!" Casamatic's home matching algorithm looks at what matters most to you when buying a home and does all of the work for you. Homes are shown based on criteria like proximity to work (and all the ways you can get there), highly-rated public schools, and being close to the people and activities you love. And once you've found that perfect home, Casamatic will get you matched up with a great local real estate agent for a tour in under 10 minutes. KEY FEATURES: - See homes based on what matters most to you - Listing data refreshed regularly, always stay up to date - Get instantly notified when new, matched homes become available - "Favorite" homes to see if the price drops or more photos are added - Schedule a tour for a home in under 10 minutes with a real estate agent that we've vetted and matched to you - Stay up to date on your iPhone or on the web, your account is completely synced to Casamatic.com With Casamatic, stop wasting time on home search apps. It's free and we'll instantly find your perfect home. NOTE: Casamatic is currently available in Charlotte, Chicago, Cincinnati, Columbus, Nashville, Phoenix, and Raleigh. If that's not you, don't sweat it...we're adding new cities all the time!', u'title': u'Real Estate App by Casamatic - Search Homes, Condos & Townhouses'}]

tagline: The world's most advanced camera for your pocket computer
text_content: [{u'description': u'We are dedicated to the seemingly nonexistent art of creating software for your mini pocket computer that actually looks good.', u'title': u'BitCam : The World's Most Advanced Camera For Your Mini Pocket Computer'}, {u'description': u'A blast from the past! BitCam is the digital camera you would have used on your mini pocket computer back in 1996. We made it to celebrate the Iconfactory's 20th anniversary of making cool things with pixels! The design brief for this app was simple: ‚ÄúWhat would we design today given the constraints of the past?‚Äù What we ended up with shows how much technology has improved since we first started writing software for Apple‚Äôs products. We stuck to a black & white interface because color graphics support back then was hit-or-miss. Some folks had it, some didn‚Äôt. A mini pocket computer would certainly need a color graphics card upgrade, and that hardware would cost you hundreds of dollars! There‚Äôs also none of the typical animation we see in today‚Äôs apps. Zoom rects were used for view transitions, scrolling in credits was jerky, and chunky controls were par for the course. (And boy, were they hard to implement on today‚Äôs devices that do asynchronous layout and high resolution drawing without an XOR operation!) We did notice one thing that hasn‚Äôt changed over the years: the importance of clarity and simplicity in a user interface. BitCam‚Äôs graphics are blockier, but have many of the same traits we strive for in today‚Äôs client work. (We kinda wish buttons still had borders, too.) Retina displays, selfies and social networks weren't around in 1996. Coming up with terminology in BitCam was a blast: we tried as hard as we could to guess the future wrong! The only reason we got FatBits right was because Bill Atkinson had already invented it. He also came up with the dithering algorithm used in the app. :thumbsup: Another big difference is today‚Äôs 64-bit processor: it can easily process the video signal at 30 frames/second. We throttled the speed to simulate the 16-bit processor in the mini pocket computer. Higher resolution settings are slower for a reason! We even thought about the past while making the app‚Äôs promotional website. If you‚Äôre a web developer, take a moment to view the source at www.iconfactory.com/bc.html (even that URL is old skool!) Native apps aren‚Äôt the only thing that‚Äôs improved remarkably since we first started out! And then there‚Äôs the price. BitCam is free to download and try out, just like the shareware we first sold at the Iconfactory. The difference now is that BitCam‚Äôs in-app purchase is 1/10th of what we charged in 1996. Your kind support will help keep us in business for another 20 years. Finally, make sure to check out the credits screen: it‚Äôs our tribute to the folks that have helped us be a success over the years. There's also a fun, and retro, surprise!', u'title': u'BitCam'}]

text_content:
[{u'body': u' Gogobot helps you discover the best events, restaurants, attractions and hotels, near you or far away. * Find great restaurants and attractions wherever you are, or wherever you're planning to go
 * Book hotels recommended by Gogobot members and get the best prices
 * Create postcards using our postcard filters tool and share with friends
 * Use member reviews and Tribes to decide which places are perfect for you.
Gogobot is your go to place for places to go, with over 800,000 reviews and 4M photos.***Google Play Store Top Developer Award Winner***
* Winner "Best Travel Apps"  - Time Magazine, Mashable, Travel & Leisure
* Featured in USA Today, Business Insider, Mashable, TechCrunch, BGR, PC Mag, and more...
* "Your secret weapon for having fun in your hometown" - Business Insider
* Featured as ‚ÄúBest New App‚Äù 
* Named ‚ÄúNew & Noteworthy‚Äù in more than 20 countries
Permissions description:- Location permissions: We're all about helping you find the best places near you (or near where you're going). 
- Photos/Media permissions: Gogobot allows you to create postcards of the places you've been, to commemorate and share your adventures with friends. 
- Call information permissions: We can connect you directly to your favorite restaurants and things to do by phone.
- Contacts permissions: At your request (and only at your request), we can help connect you with your friends and add them to your Gogobot network.   ', u'description': u'Discover great restaurants, activities, hotels & bars nearby.', u'title': u'Gogobot - City & Travel Guide - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': u'***The award winning Gogobot App is your guide to discovering the best places to Play, Eat and Stay that are perfect for you, at home or while traveling*** Gogobot uses your interests, the time of day, the local weather, and your location to help you discover the best attractions, events, restaurants and hotels: * Get recommendations whether you‚Äôre a foodie, a nightlife lover, a family traveler or more * Get timely suggestions to grab dinner, brunch, coffee, dessert and more based on the time & day of the week * Get ideas for things to do based on the weather for those sunny, rainy or even cloudy days * Discover local gems and fresh places to go while at home, and see the most popular places when visiting or exploring a new city * Explore ideas for a weekend getaway nearby or get inspired by exploring one of Gogobot‚Äôs 60,000 destinations across the globe * Book & save on hotels recommended by the Gogobot community - compare prices across Expedia, Hotels.com, Booking.com, Priceline, Hotwire and more * Read from over +1M Gogobot member reviews so you never miss out on insider tips * Give back & share your experiences by creating postcards & reviews of your adventures with fun, custom photo filters * Join the Gogobot community to participate in local and global leaderboards, show off your travel expertise, collect badges & more TOP APP * Featured as ‚ÄúBest New App by Apple‚Äù * Named ‚ÄúNew & Noteworthy‚Äù in more than 20 countries * Named in the ‚ÄúBest of‚Äù Apple App collection as best travel applications along with Airbnb, Expedia, Yelp and more... * Featured in USA Today, Business Insider, Mashable, TechCrunch, BGR, PC Mag, and more... * Winner "Best Travel Apps" - Time Magazine, Mashable, Travel & Leisure * "Your secret weapon for having fun in your hometown" - Business Insider Note: Continued use of GPS running the background can dramatically decrease battery life.', u'title': u'Gogobot - City & Travel Guide: Activities, Restaurants, Events, Hotel Reviews'}, {u'description': u'Sync your Gogobot Lists with your mobile. tagline: A music studio in your pocket
text_content: [{u'description': u'One track can change music. What will you make? "What makes Auxy stand out from the scores of other music-making apps is a smarter and simpler design that makes building a song not only easier, but more beautiful too." ‚Äî WIRED ‚óÜ ‚óÜ ‚óÜ We believe better music will be made if music making becomes more about music and less about cables. That‚Äôs why Auxy gets rid of the mess and lets you focus on what matters: making melodies, creating beats, tweaking sounds, and arranging your track to get it just right. ‚óÜ ‚óÜ ‚óÜ STATE-OF-THE-ART SOUND Behind the minimalist interface runs a powerful sound engine with effects by Sonic Charge and FXpansion. ABLETON LINK Auxy supports Ableton Link, which makes it possible to play in sync with any music app that supports the standard. Connect to the same wifi and enable Link to jam with other Auxy users. ABOUT AUXY Auxy builds music instruments for the future. By putting a studio in everyone‚Äôs pocket, we aim to push music forward as an artform. Engineered in Stockholm, Sweden since 2014. Connect on social media and send your love and feedback. You can also reach us via feedback@auxy.co.', u'title': u'Auxy Music Studio'}, {u'description': u'A studio in your pocket. Engineered in Stockholm, Sweden since 2014.', u'title': u'AuxyLogo'}]

text_content:
[{u'body': u' Tap on Dango to find the best emojis, GIFs and stickers while messaging in any app.
 
‚òÖ On point emoji. Dango is powered by artificial intelligence that has been trained to understand how you're feeling based on what you or your friends say. You can trust Dango to recommend some exceptional emoticons üëå
 
‚òÖ Quick GIFs. With just a few short taps, you can search through MILLIONS of funny images free of charge courtesy of Giphy to make your friends laugh. üòÇüòπüòù (Note: Dango will only give the option to share Giphy GIFs in apps that properly support the GIF format)
 
‚òÖ Original Stickers. üòéüëç Don't be afraid to shoot us your sticker pack requests. Messaging has never been this expressive! üòÜüéâ
 
‚òÖ Emoji combos.  Make your own emoji stories! Emoji art, emoji combos, or emoji stories are made easy and quickly with Dango üèÅüöóüí®üöôüí®
 
‚òÖ Dango is üÜì Dango is a FREE app! Eventually we might make some features available as in-app purchase, but for now everything is absolutely free. üí∏üëÄ

tagline: Explore medical cannabis treatment together
text_content: [{u'description': u'Mindfully manage your medical cannabis treatment with Releaf. Designed to be your companion in your personal journey to feeling better through medical cannabis, Releaf helps you chart a personal pathway to feeling better, faster, and with greater confidence and comfort in your medical cannabis treatment plan. Please note that this first version of Releaf is primary aimed at patients who smoke or use vaporizers for their treatment. Support for tinctures and edibles is coming soon! BENEFITS OF MINDFUL MANAGEMENT Cannabis isn‚Äôt a ‚Äútake two and call me in the morning‚Äù type of medicine. It affects everyone differently so to get the most out of it you need to track your experiences and examine what‚Äôs working for you. But it‚Äôs hard to know what to write down. It‚Äôs even harder to turn whatever you write down into actionable information. Releaf helps you do all of that and more. Releaf makes it simple to record information about your cannabis treatment sessions in real time. You can easily enter each puff you take and each change in your symptoms. Besides your primary symptom, you can also record your ‚Äúfeels‚Äù - all of the common side effects that come with cannabis. By tracking what strains and dosages make you hungry, talkative, anxious, etc. you can better shape your treatment to your needs. When you‚Äôre done with a session you can then rate it and view easy to understand infographics about how your session went. This data is all processed and fed back to you so you can quickly learn what‚Äôs working for you and make more informed choices about your cannabis purchases and treatment plan. HELPING US ALL ‚ÄúGuess and check‚Äù is a lot of work. One of the goals of Releaf is to bring us together to learn from each other by sharing 100% anonymous session data. We are working on features that will provide insight to you as to what other patients with similar ailments are having success with on specific strains or equipment. This will result in less work for everyone on the path to feeling better, faster, and with more comfort and confidence. FEATURES Simple to use, real-time recording of your cannabis sessions Record your symptoms, notes, and feelings easily Beautiful infographics help you figure out what works for you Track your cannabis purchases Easily enter testing data from THC and CBD to all major cannabinoids and terpenes Record personal notes about your strains Help the world better understand the benefits of medical cannabis!', u'title': u'releaf - a thoughtful approach to cannabis treatment'}, {u'description': u'', u'title': u'releaf.'}]

tagline: Instantly transform your photos into professional collages!
text_content: [{u'description': u'"The app promises an easy way for smaller businesses to quickly create and design content" - TechCrunch "Sprightly‚Ä¶ helps small businesses design snazzy promotional materials without needing a PC or complicated tools" - PCWorld Sprightly, a Microsoft Garage App, lets you instantly create detailed catalogs, beautiful fliers, multiple price lists, E-cards and discount coupons on the go. No need to hire expensive designers to make professional designer quality content for your business or personal uses. Designing and sharing your content has never been so easier or faster: ‚Ä¢ Click ‚Äì Take photos, or import images ‚Ä¢ Make ‚Äì Choose from multiple template options ‚Ä¢ Share‚Äì Export to Facebook, WhatsApp, email and more The graphic design experts at Sprightly have tackled all your design problems so you don‚Äôt have to. Without any previous experience you can easily create professional looking designs. Choose from a number of pre-designed templates, add one image or 20 and each time the app will re-size and arrange the images in the most beautiful way possible. Once created, easily share your content across digital platforms for your social media and content marketing needs or send print ready PDF‚Äôs to your customers. To save time you only have to import your images once into your ‚Äòcollections‚Äô. Once imported you can quickly access the images letting you create once and use many times. Sprightly comes in handy for retailers who regularly engage with their customers on social channels. Create on-the-go awesome business collages for new product launches or special occasions such as 1st Anniversary or Spring Collection and share them on Messenger or WhatsApp to attract new customers. A simple and easy to use photo editor for your digital marketing campaigns, Sprightly enables you acquire new customers without spending any money on creating content. It's completely FREE! We value your feedback. Please join the discussion here - http://aka.ms/discuss The Microsoft Garage is an outlet for experimental projects for you to try. Learn more at http://garage.microsoft.com. By installing the app, you agree to these terms and conditions: http://aka.ms/sprightlyios/eula', u'title': u'Microsoft Sprightly ‚Äì Instantly transform your photos into professional collages!'}]

text_content: [{u'description': u'Laundry and Dry Cleaning delivered to your door, at the tap of a button. Cleanly is changing how we think about laundry and dry cleaning. Choose a 1-hour window that works for you, let us know if you‚Äôre sending out laundry, dry cleaning, or both, and boom - you‚Äôre done. Clean clothes delivered in 24 hours, 7 days a week. With early morning pickups to late at night deliveries, we‚Äôre there when you need us with convenient Cleanly branded laundry and garment bags so you know your clothes are in good hands. There are lots of apps out there, but not many that will do your laundry for you. That‚Äôs where Cleanly comes in. Now this is what we call the age of convenience. ‚ÄúThe YC-backed startup that handles all of your laundry needs with the push of a button‚Äù - TechCrunch ‚ÄúShouldn‚Äôt getting a shirt cleaned be as easy as downloading a song?‚Äù - Wall Street Journal ‚ÄúJust think of it as the UBER of laundry‚Äù - NY Daily News --- See if Cleanly is available in your city at https://cleanly.com Follow us on Twitter at https://twitter.com/cleanly Like us on Facebook at https://www.facebook.com/getcleanly Have a question? text_content: [{u'description': None, u'title': u'Walter - Where things are'}, {u'description': u'The best way to explore a new city is to walk it. You wander around with just a general idea of where things are. If that's how you roll, Walter is the travel app for you! Walter is your smart travel compass. Instead of pointing you north, south, east or west, Walter points you towards sights, shops, restaurants and bars. Simply hold your phone in the direction you want to go and Walter will show you the hotspots nearby. With Walter you‚Äôll always know where things are. Why you need Walter Walter works everywhere you go. Walter works without an internet connection. Walter points you in the right direction for sightseeing, shopping, eating and going out. No signup, no settings, just launch and go! Happy Waltering!', u'title': u'Walter - Your Smart Travel Compass'}]

tagline: Create cinematic scenes on your iPhone
text_content: [{u'description': u'Want to get more likes on Instagram and Facebook? VUE is the most fashionable tip. Use hash tag #madebyVUE to highlight and find out more. VUE is a video camera empowering users to capture memorable moments, edit them through adding filters, stickers or montage, and most importantly, share them with the world. VUE offers you an excellent opportunity to create cinematic videos as easy as to take photos. The only thing you need do is tap. -Montage is never this easy --Choose one to four scenes, tap for each scene, and make a 6 second masterpiece --Get the montage effect via juxtaposition -Enhance your video with stickers --More than 30 designer stickers for you to choose - from weather conditions to emoticons --The stickers can appear at the entrance, at the finale, or throughout the video -Cinematic filters --12 carefully-selected filters from film professionals to cater to all your needs no matter you're looking for documentary effects or artistic expression --Create flawless selfie videos with our killer filter when switched to the front camera -Ultra wide picture Wide and ultra wide aspect ratio supported, complies with the standard of film Besides, VUE is optimized specifically for iPhone 6s and iPhone 6s Plus. Come and try. Sharing is loving - share your incredible VUE videos with your friends on Facebook, Instagram, Twitter, Vine etc. If you have any questionsÔºåplease contact us via feedback@vue.video or tweet us @VueVideo. We will contact you as soon as possible and your feedback will be highly appreciated.', u'title': u'VUE - Video camera with artistic tools, filters and stickers'}, {u'description': u'VUE Video is a video camera app empowering users to capture memorable moments, edit them through adding filters, stickers or montage, and most importantly, share them with the world. tagline: Search and read Wikipedia from your Mac menu bar
text_content: [{u'description': u'Quickly and easily search Wikipedia, without even leaving your menu bar! You can read articles inside Qwiki, or you can opt to have it open in your default browser, it‚Äôs up to you. You can also generate links, you can choose from a plain URL, Markdown, or even generate HTML link code. If you want to use the native OS X Share Sheet, then that‚Äôs supported as well! Once you've typed your search query, just use your arrow keys to navigate the results, and press enter to open it up! It gives you the power of Wikipedia, and puts it under the single icon in your Menu Bar. There‚Äôs so many occasions where just a little reference is needed, or you need to copy a URL to insert into a document. There is a URL Scheme available for Qwiki, and also an Alfred workflow. You can find these on the Qwiki website (getQwiki.co).', u'title': u'Qwiki - Search Bar and Article Viewer for Wikipedia! on the Mac App Store'}, {u'description': u'Search Bar and Article Viewer for Wikipedia!', u'title': u'Qwiki'}]

tagline: A parent-to-parent carpooling for kids
text_content:
[{u'body': u' Carpooling Made SimpleKidCarPool is a parent-helping-parent network that simplifies the carpool experience. Families with kids who attend the same school or after-school activities share a ride, save time & gas and make the ride a fun, social experience for the kids.- Get Matched - don‚Äôt know where to start? get matched with families from your community that share similar schedules. Connect directly and start a pool!
- Organize the chaos: start a pool by adding your child, activity name & time and inviting other parents who may want to join the pool. 
- See what‚Äôs coming: an easy-view dashboard shows your complete child activity schedule and upcoming pools
- Plan / view route: each scheduled drive includes efficient pick-up drop off route and carpool status updates
- Stay informed: Notifications remind carpool participants of upcoming pool and notifies of estimated time of departure / arrival
- Save time & money and watch your kids enjoy a social, fun ride!   ', u'description': u'Carpooling Made Simple', u'title': u'Kid CarPool - Android Apps on Google Play'}, {u'description': u'Carpooling Made Simple KidCarPool is a parent-helping-parent network that simplifies the carpool experience. tagline: Alerts and information in the case of a major crisis üá´üá∑
text_content: [{u'description': u'Alerts and information in the case of a major event or crisis using geolocation. SAIP, meaning "syst√®me d‚Äôalerte et d‚Äôinformation des populations" (system to alert and inform populations) is the official government mobile alert application from the Ministry of the Interior for smartphones running iOS. This free application allows users to receive alerts in the case of exceptional events (nuclear, hazardous materials, and hydraulic structure failure alerts, etc.) that may result from an attack within a specified geographical zone, providing that the user‚Äôs geolocation settings are activated and that the application is active. The SAIP mobile application is available in French and English, and adds to the existing system for alerting and informing populations (sirens, pre-formatted radio messages, etc.). The alert activates when the user is in, or enters, an at-risk zone, without any user information being sent, even when geolocation settings are activated. The user can record up to 8 geographical zones (postcodes, cities) and receive notifications if an event occurs in one of these locations. The application also provides advice on how to act and instructions to follow depending on the type of alert ("how to react"). It also allows users to relay current alerts on social networks via their personal accounts.', u'title': u'SAIP'}]

text_content: [{u'description': u'Akku ‚Äî simple mobile application to help you eat healthy. You can define your desired outcome, choose nutrition plan, cook by yourself or order diet delivery. All nutrition plans are standardized and consist of healthy and easy-to-cook recipes. Akku is ideal for you whether you‚Äôre just curious on how to eat healthy, looking for yummy recipes, or looking for effective diets and nutrition plans. Key Akku Features: ‚Ä¢ Define your desired outcome: Become healthy, lose weight, gain muscle weight, become vegetarian. ‚Ä¢ Choose between effective and healthy nutrition plans. ‚Ä¢ Akku can choose a nutrition plan for you based on your desired outcome and metrics. ‚Ä¢ Share favorite meals ‚Ä¢ Receive timely reminders ‚Ä¢ All meals include detailed directions and ingredients list. ‚Ä¢ Only easy-to-cook meals of everyday products. Akku is free to download and use. We are working hard on developing key function of the App - delivery of the chosen nutrition plan. The global mission of Akku is to help you solve all your problems with healthy nutrition. Looking forward to hear what you think.', u'title': u'Akku ‚Äì Personal Diets and Nutrition Plans'}, {u'description': None, u'title': u'Your personal nutrition programs'}]

tagline: Text and talk with Alexa on the go
text_content: [{u'description': u'Ava gives you the ability to interact with Alexa on your iPhone. Ava is powered by Alexa Voice Service. HOW TO USE (Text and Talk!) -Login with your Amazon account to get started (required) -Tap anywhere to begin speaking -Tap again when you are done speaking -Wait for response -Repeat for additional requests -Click the pen icon to begin texting (only one text allowed at a time) -Receive text or audio responses from texting interface -Configure your preferences in the free Amazon Alexa app (see configuration details below) SOME FEATURES (Text and Talk!) -Interact with Alexa using your iPhone -Text a request instead for better quality in busy and crowded areas -Text with privacy -Jump into texting mode using the 3D touch shortcut! -Control your smart home devices -Check your order status for purchases made on Amazon -Enable Alexa skills from the free Amazon Alexa App -Get your daily news update -Check your morning commute -Build your shopping list -Developers can test out their Alexa skills as they create them LIMITATIONS (currently not available) -Playing music -Reading audio books -Setting timers and alarms CONFIGURATION -Download the free Amazon Alexa App -Set your current location -Set your morning commute -Enable all the skills you want! **Text responses from Ava will not always be 100% accurate. **This app is not storing any data.', u'title': u'Ava - Alexa Voice Service edition with text and talk'}]

tagline: Turn your phone into a breathalyzer
text_content: [{u'description': u'A personal breathalyzer that connects to your cell phone with and lets you know your alcohol level and how long to wait before being sober again.', u'title': u' Cautoh Breathalyzer, find your alcohol level '}, {u'description': u'Find out your blood alcohol content (BAC) to see if you are within the blood alcohol limit or how much time you have to wait before being within limits again. You can use the alcohol calculator Cautoh. It uses an algorithm to give you an aproximation of your BAC based on your physiology and ingested drinks. Make smart choices when drinking and enjoy again the tranquility of driving without fear of an accident or getting a fine.', u'title': u'Cautoh'}, {u'body': u' Find out your blood alcohol content (BAC) to see if you are within the blood alcohol limit or how much time you have to wait before being within limits again. You can use the calculator or test it yourself with our smart breathalyzer Cautoh.To use the calculator you will select the drink you are having for a list in the app, so based on your weight, gender and some studied formulas you can get an approximation of your blood alcohol content. The drink list is filled with most popular drinks around the world, but you can create your own drinks if you want. Discover nearby restaurants where you can  wait until you are within legal limits to drive. you can also use this app to book a cab, get a designated driver or call a friend.Make smart choices when drinking and enjoy again the tranquility of driving  without fear of an accident or getting a fine.   ', u'description': u'Find your BAC, track your drinks in the calculator and get your alcohol level.', u'title': u'Breathalyzer Cautoh - Android Apps on Google Play'}]

tagline: The best way to coordinate with friends
text_content: [{u'description': u'Featured recently as a ‚ÄúNew App We Love‚Äù Firefly is the new best way to get together with friends. See who is around and then quickly plan hangouts. Unlock powerful coordination with Firefly groups! We want to hear your feedback! Email feedback@firefly.cool Use Firefly to: ‚Ä¢ See who is nearby to grab coffee ‚Ä¢ Plan a fun night out ‚Ä¢ Check who is in town this weekend ‚Ä¢ Get a pickup bball game going ‚Ä¢ Any and all things spontaneous and social! Features: ‚Ä¢ Create a group to stay close with your best friends near and far ‚Ä¢ Control your location sharing by turning your light on/off ‚Ä¢ No content is permanent: all posts delete after a few days ‚Ä¢ Use a power tag to supercharge your posts (#hangout, #party, #event, #glow, #getlit) ‚Ä¢ Posting will automatically notify nearby friends Note: Continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life. However, we have worked hard in order for Firefly to use less battery than your favorite apps and to use almost no battery when your light is off.', u'title': u'Firefly - Coordinate with Friends'}, {u'description': u'', u'title': u' Firefly'}]

tagline: Connected smart toys that learn and grow with a child.
text_content: [{u'description': u'Default Description', u'title': u'Connected Smart Toys that Grow CogniToys are the next generation of internet connected smart toys that learn and grow with your child. Preorders are available now!'}, {u'description': u'The CogniToys Dino is cloud-based and Wi-Fi enabled, which allows the toy to explore different topics and answer questions in real-time. CogniToys are built for personalization! The toy can remember information a child shares such as their name, favorite things, stories, jokes and more to help enrich learning and future conversations. Educational topics CogniToys cover include, but are not limited to: storytelling, math, science, geography, rhyming and vocabulary. Key Features: Initiates and Engages in Real Conversations Speech recognition allows the toys to sustain engaging conversations using intelligent, age-appropriate content. Uniquely Personalized Adapts by remembering individual attributes (e.g. a child's favorite color), even telling knock-knock jokes and providing answers to "who," "what," "why," "where" and "when" questions. Integrated Parent Panel A web-based dashboard that allows parents to monitor their child's progress in real time, providing unique insights into learning skills and suggestions for improvement. The Parent Panel also allows for content moderation. Internet-Connected CogniToys are internet-connected devices which automatically update with new content. Toy Specs: iOS & Android compatible Durable ABS body (can be cleaned with mild soap and warm water) Batteries: 4AA included, 6 week battery life with moderate use Multi-color indicator lights Dimensions: 5.5" L, 4" W, 7.5" H Cloud updates to introduce new features and content What's Inside The Box: The CogniToys Dino 4AA batteries Quick start guide.', u'title': u'CogniToys Dino Green'}]

tagline: A better way to understand text - across multiple documents
text_content: [{u'description': u'** NAMED "MOST INNOVATIVE APP" OF 2015 BY THE APPLE APP STORE! ** ** One of Mashable's Ten Best iPad Apps of 2015! ** ** One of Time Magazine's Ten Best apps for iPad Pro! ** ** Named "Best App of September" by Apple App Store! ** ** Named One of the Top Ten Products of 2015 by TechnoLawyer ** Featured in TechCrunch, Xconomy, Technolawyer, Macworld, and Brooks Review. LiquidText offers gesture based reading and annotation for documents (PDF, DOC, PPT, web pages). Read in ways not possible on paper. LiquidText gives you the tools to pull out the key facts from all your sources and integrate them together, focus on what matters, compare different pages or documents, take notes, and build upon thoughts. Improve the way you read on the iPad with LiquidText. Here‚Äôs how: ‚ñ∫ MULTIDOCUMENT USERS RECEIVE (requires one-time in-app purchase): Work with multiple documents and webpages in a single workspace ‚Ä¢ Pull together excerpts from different documents. ‚Ä¢ Search across all the documents in a LiquidText workspace. ‚Ä¢ Compare documents in parallel. ‚Ä¢ Make comments that refer to multiple documents. ‚ñ∫ ALL USERS RECEIVE: View ‚Ä¢ Read and interact with text in a flexible environment ‚Ä¢ Compatible with PDF, Word, and PowerPoint documents and web pages ‚Ä¢ Import from Dropbox, iCloud Drive, Box, email, and more ‚Ä¢ Import content from webpage or send to LiquidText directly from Safari Interact ‚Ä¢ Workspace area for writing notes and pulling out excerpts ‚Ä¢ Organize and group excerpts and notes ‚Ä¢ Tap comments and excerpts to find original source ‚Ä¢ Pinch document to compare different sections ‚Ä¢ Collapse text to see annotated parts side-by-side ‚Ä¢ Collapse text to view search term(s) side-by-side ‚Ä¢ Scroll to navigate through pages ‚Ä¢ Scrollbar shows where highlights, comments, excerpts, and search results are located Annotate ‚Ä¢ Highlight text, images, comments, excerpts, and notes ‚Ä¢ Add margin notes/comments to text, images, notes, and excerpts ‚Ä¢ Comment on two or more selections simultaneously Share ‚Ä¢ Export file as notes only, highlights only, notes and highlights, or entire document with annotations ‚Ä¢ Export as LiquidText file, PDF, or DOCX (supported by most word processors) ‚Ä¢ Send files by email or to Dropbox, iCloud, Box, and more Learn more at LiquidText.net | Comprehend More.', u'title': u'LiquidText - PDF and Document Reader'}, {u'description': u'LiquidText improves upon the reading experience by allowing users to better understand, synthesize, visualize and collaborate over digital text.', u'title': u'Comprehend More with LiquidText'}]

tagline: You don't need a personal assistant to manage ur appointment
text_content:
[{u'description': u'Scibler Smart Scheduler is the fastest way for you to track and respond to meeting requests in email conversations. Our new AI-powered one-touch scheduling technology is designed to help busy people schedule effortlessly even when on-the-go. This how Scibler's smart scheduling technology works: - Automatically intercepts meeting requests sent or received via email - Prepares responses or followups, on your behalf, based on your availability and scheduling preferences - Allows you to review and send out the prepared responses with just one-tap! So now you don't need an assistant to manage your schedule. tagline: Forecast the weather with geolocation
text_content: [{u'description': u'Check the weather using the free Meteo app by iNVASIVECODE, the world leading company for advanced iOS training. Weather forecast and alerts in real time.', u'title': u'Meteo Weather iOS App'}, {u'description': u'Meteo integrates innovative mapping and meteorological technologies, allowing users to pinpoint and share the current temperature, daily high and low temperatures, cloud cover, and type of precipitation for exact locations anywhere in the world. By cultivating precise, easily-understandable weather data, Meteo mitigates uncertainty and confusion, and ultimately creates the sleekest meteorological experience possible. Features 1. Pinpointing Weather changes drastically from one location to the next, and locations that are close, geographically, can have extremely different weather. Meteo confronts ambiguous weather predictions and the geographical diversity of microclimates, by allowing users to access weather data from exact locations. 2. Favorites When users want to observe a specific location, they simply flag it. Once a location is flagged, it‚Äôs fluidly added to a favorites list, which displays, concisely, the weather at relevant locations. 3. 5-Day Forecast Accurate, long-range weather prediction is invaluable. Meteo, therefore, automatically generates an interactive, updated 5-day weather overview. 4. Sharing Weather is communal, which is why Meteo facilitates the open exchange of pertinent meteorological information through modern platforms.', u'title': u'Meteo - Local Weather Forecasts and Hazard Alerts on an Interactive Map'}]

text_content: [{u'description': u'Access over 10,000 emoji and manage over 100 emoji keyboards all from one app. Moji Keyboard is the #1 emoji keyboard app delivering fresh new emoji content all the time. Browse from the world's largest emoji library or search through thousands of amazing icons. With 100% original content, these aren't your typical stock images. Choose from hundreds of keyboards for celebs, trending, memes and more. Every say "I wish there was an emoji for that" ? Problem solved. We've created an emoji for literally anything you can think of. From new animated emojis to age 18+ ones, the possibilities are endless. NEW verified accounts give you access to hand-picked emojis from your favorite celebs. Everything is made in stunning high resolution and optimized for iMessage. Combine multiple emojis together and send directly from the app or install the optional keyboard. Forget installing multiple apps to get the emojis you want by getting them all in one place. FEATURES- ‚Ä¢Combine multiple icons together in messages. ‚Ä¢Assign Favorites to access the ones you use most in one place. ‚Ä¢Arrange & Delete icons from your keyboard and keep the ones you want. ‚Ä¢Organize Tabs to sort the order on your keyboard from left to right. ‚Ä¢Customize Tab Icon to quickly identify a pack by changing the main icon. ‚Ä¢Search using words or phrases to find just what you're looking for. ‚Ä¢Animated Icons bring your favorite emojis to life with hilarious animation. NOTE: It is IMPOSSIBLE for any app developer to create new emojis that work like the ones installed on your phone. If it were possible, we would do it. The process to create more emoji is highly restricted and takes years. Until those rules change, we've come up with the next best thing by creating an unlimited language of dynamic emoji. DISCLAIMER: Moji Keyboard, its designs, all static and animated icons, all other assets & artwork are the sole property of AppMoji, Inc. unless otherwise designated. All of the work contained within this app is copyrighted or falls under Fair Use Act Guidelines. Images depicted do not reflect the beliefs of Appmoji Inc. or it's partners. ‚óÜ Notice ‚óÜ Please rest assured that Moji will NEVER collect any personal information or transmit what you type over any network. Turning on ‚ÄúAllow Full Access‚Äù is simply an iOS requirement for third party keyboards. We take your privacy very serious. ‚Äª Go to iOS System Settings and add "Moji Keyboard" from third-party keyboards after download. Instagram.com/MojiKeyboard Facebook.com/MojiKeyboard Twitter.com/MojiKeyboard Biz - WeMakeMoji.com Press - MojiKeyboard@gmail.com', u'title': u'Moji Keyboard'}]

text_content:
[{u'body': u' Presenting the best and powerful material design music player, MP3 player and music video player with Equalizer, Virtualizer, Bassboost, Lyrics and Tag editor and Album art downloader.The audio player supports mp3, m4a, flacc, wav and lots more. Equalizer - 5 bands, Edit tags, Download Album art, Browse and EDIT LYRICS. Search music videos. Create, edit and delete playlists. Play by genre, artists, albums and folders. Stream hundreds latest and most trending music videos from all over the world, Pop, Rock, R&B, EDM, Bollywood and lots more..KEY FEATURES
# 5 band Equalizer with Virtualizer and Bass Boost to enhance music playback
# Material design
# Album art downloader
# Organize and play your music/audio files by Albums, Genres, Artists and Music Folders. 
# Watch and play hundreds of HOTTEST & most TRENDING Music videos from all over the world 
# Edit TAGS, browse and edit LYRICS, and ALBUM Covers
# Create, edit and manage Playlists. 
# Search for music videos of your favorite songs directly with this app. 
# Download artist images and biography from LAST.FM
# Mark songs, albums and artists as your Favorites
# Flexibility to users to enable or disable features, choose among several gorgeous skins and themes
# Smooth and unmatched design
# Gapless music playback
# Auto playlists based on your most played and recently played songs and music albums
# Artist Biographies along with social media profiles. No other music player out there offers this feature# Stay tuned for more...The music Player supports all popular audio formats like mp3, wav, ogg, flacc, m4a, etc. As its in Beta, We shall continue to add more features to the audio player on the run. Planned features include widgets, better lockscreen control, improved tag-editor, better album art downloader, cross-fading and many more. Please support our efforts as we tirelessly continue to improve and add new features. We are constantly monitoring crashes or bugs with inbuilt analytics packages as well as through manual testing. In case of any crash or glitch, please allow us a chance to fix them before uninstalling or giving us a poor review. Please understand that we are entirely dependent on your support to continue with the development of this awesome Music Player application.We can guarantee you this shall prove to be the best free music player that you might have come acrossPlease contact the developers in case of any issue or complaints or suggestion
